"Kutenga bitcoin kuri nyore kupfuura makare ose. Kuchengeta bitcoin yako kwenguva refu uye zvakachengeteka kunoda hushoma hwekunzwisisa kwehunyanzvi uye kwehupfumi. Bhuku rino rinopa hwaro hunodiwa kuti urambe uchidzora mari yako. Kwose uko rwendo rweBitcoin runotitora, kuisa mari. mubhuku rino mune chokwadi kukunda." - **Johannes Grill, Mutungamiri Bitcoin Austria**

003-preface

Chikwereti
Kutenda kwakakosha kuna Sovryn nekubatsira mukusikwa kwebhuku rino (kugadzirisa, kurongedza, kugadzira, shanduro).
Ndinodawo kutenda vanhu vanotevera nekupa nguva yavo nehunyanzvi: Exiledsurfer, Jameson Lopp, Nic Carter, Andreas M. Antonopoulos, Caitlin Long, Maya Zehavi, Lyn Alden, Alena Vranova, Thomas Voegtlin, Max Hillebrand, Hass McCook, Ryan Gentry, kunyara OK, Erik24020105, Chris Chester, Johannes Grill, Daniel Pichler, Stephanie Jagl-Posch.
Pira
Ini ndiri mukadzi mumwe akazvimirira mubhizinesi, handina vashandi, handina mubatsiri, dzimwe nguva ndinohaya ma freelancers kuti andibatsire. Kana iwe uchida kutsigira basa rangu rinounza dzidzo nezveBitcoin kuvanhu vakawanda sezvinobvira, unogona kubatsira pa https://anita.link/donate

006-introduction

Nhanganyaya
"Kunyora tsananguro yechinhu ichi kune vateereri vese kune ropa rakaoma. Hapana chekuita nazvo." -Satoshi Nakamoto
(L) earn Bitcoin ndiyo gwara rakanakisa rekusarudza kuti sei uye sei uchifanira kupinda munyika yeBitcoin. Inopa Bitcoin mumativi ayo ese, kubva kune ayo ehunyanzvi, ehupfumi, ezvematongerwo enyika uye emagariro kune mafambisirwo ari kuita mamiriro emari aripo. Inopa nhanho-ne-nhanho nzira yekufambisa ino nyika itsva yezvemari uye inomisa iwe nekongiri kurudziro yekuti ungawana sei zvakachengeteka, kuwana uye kuchengeta bitcoin. Kukwira masitepisi ehutongi hwemari kuchakupa rusununguko uye kutonga pamusoro pemari yako.
Mubhuku rino, iwe uchawana mhinduro kumibvunzo yekuti chii mari, kwainobva, budiriro yayo yenhoroondo, blockchain tekinoroji uye Bitcoin chaizvo. Inopa mhinduro kumibvunzo kuti sei uye sei kushandisa Bitcoin, uku uchibvisa ngano dzakakurumbira uye kusanzwisisana kwakapoteredza cryptocurrencies. Ini ndinonyura zvakadzama mukusimukira kweBitcoin kubva payakavambwa muna 2008 uye ndinopa tarisiro yemangwana mashandisirwo emari anoenderana neBitcoin.
Kunyange zvazvo vezvenhau vakuru uye nyanzvi dzezvehupfumi munyika dzekumadokero vachifunga kuti chinhu ichi chingori chekutengesa, chinangwa changu ndechekuparadzira shoko nezveBitcoin sechinhu chinokwanisa kuunza kuenzana kwehupfumi uye shanduko yemagariro. Zvinhu zvisingataurwi ndezvekuti Bitcoin, iyo isingade mvumo, isingadzivisiki, isina divi, uye ine huwandu hwakatarwa, inopa mikana yakanaka munyika chaiyo.
Mune rimwe bhuku, ndichatarisa pakushandisa kwakanyanya kwebitcoin (BTC) uye maitiro aungaita kuti uwane uye uichengetedze zvakachengeteka. Uchadzidza maitiro ekuzvivimba nekutanga nemari shoma, maitiro ekuderedza njodzi dziripo uye kufambira mberi nenzira yakarongeka uye inoshanda mukuchengetedza hupfumi hwako kwenguva refu.
Iri harisi zano rezvemari kana gwara rekutengesa kune zviuru zveAltcoins zviripo. Kana iwe uchingofarira kuwana kwenguva pfupi, kubata mari sekunge uri kubhejera mukhasino, bhuku rino harisi rako. Izvo ndezvevanhu vanoda kudzidza uye kunzwisisa zvakakosha zveBitcoin uye kudzora mari yavo nenzira yekuzvimiririra.

100-evolution-money

Kushanduka Kwemari
Musi waNdira 3, 2009, Bitcoin yakazvarwa. Kubva pakusikwa kwayo, iyo Bitcoin P2P network Internet Protocol (IP) yakanamatirana ne mabhuraki matsva edata kune chetani yekutengeserana anenge maminetsi gumi ega ega. Iyo Bitcoin blockchain inochengetedza kutengeserana mune nzira kwayo kurongeka kwenguva iyo isingagone kuchinjwa mushure, yakagadziriswa senguva pachayo. Sezvo kurova kwemoyo yedu kunochengetedza miviri yedu, maitiro aya anochengetedzwa nehurongwa hunokwevera hwaro hwayo kubva kumutambo wecryptography, neIT, uye decentralized network inozvichengeta pachiyero.
Iyi yekuzvitonga sisitimu ine maitiro anoteera:
Kuchinjana mari mu Bitcoin akuna mitemo yakawanda.
Bitcoin haichinjike
Bitcoin haina manyepo
Kuchinjana mari kuBitcoin kwakachengeteka zvakanyanya pasina vamiriri, sebhangi.
Kuchinjana mari kuBitcoin kuri pachena, kunoonekwa pachena uye kunogona kuongororwa nemunhu wese
![Mubhadharo wePayPal uchipikisana neBitcoin](zvishandiso/_paypal-bitcoin-intermediaries.PNG) [^1] Mukubhadhara kwechivanhu kune vamiriri vanosvika vanomwe kusvika muripo wasvika kune anenge apihwa. Bitcoin haina.
Bitcoin haina tsika kana kusiyanisa pakati pe "zvakanaka" uye "zvakaipa" mukubhadhara.
Bitcoin haina mvumo: hapana vachengeti vemagedhi vanogona kudzivirira kushandiswa kway
Bitcoin inosvika kwese kwese
Bitcoin, iyo Internet Protocol, chinhu chakajairika: ndeyemunhu wese, kwete sangano rimwechete sekambani.
Mitemo yeBitcoin inosimbiswa nekubvumirana kwakachengeteka kwehurongwa hwevose vanobatanidzwa.
Bitcoin imari yevanhu. Bitcoin ndiko kushanduka kwemari. Iko kuenderera mberi kwemaitiro asingagumi ekutsvaga mari itsva yakagara iri chikamu chenhoroondo yevanhu. Kwezviuru zvemakore, nzira itsva dzakasiyana siyana dzemari dzakawanikwa uye dzakashandiswa, kubva pakuchinjana kwakananga pakati pevanhu kuenda kune kiredhiti sisitimu mune yegoridhe mwero, kune mari ye fiat kune yanhasi isina zvekukwira kwemitengo. Mabhangi uye hurongwa hwemari sezvatinoziva nhasi hwave huripo uye hwakashanduka kweanenge makore mazana matatu. Zvinongoitika kuti, nekubuda kwenzira itsva yekukurukurirana kuburikidza neinternet, nzira itsva yehupfumi uye rudzi rutsva rwemari, iyo mari yepa internet, inofanira kusimuka.
Nhoroondo yemari
Mari inogoneka yekriptografiki kana kuti "Internet yeMari" - sezvinotaurwa naAndreas M. Antonopoulos - haigone kumiswa. Tiri pakutanga kwenguva itsva munhoroondo yevanhu.
Mabwe eRai eYap
Kana Bitcoin ichinzwika kushamisa pfungwa uye iwe usingakwanise kubata pfungwa ye blockchain seyakagovaniswa pachokwadi, iyo Rai yeIsle yeYap muenzaniso wakanaka kuunza mamwe anopindirana pfungwa.
Rai madhisiki makuru ematombo anoshandiswa pachitsuwa cheYap muWestern Pacific (Micronesia). Ayo "akagadzirwa" kubva kumarara emarara echitsuwa chePalau uye vakashandiswa semari kusvika muzana ramakore rechi20.
 ![Rai matombo ane matanda ekutakura, 1903](zviwanikwa/_Stone_Money_of_Uap_1903_Jayne,_String_Figures_p160.jpg) [^3
Matombo eRai akaunzwa kuYap nechikepe uye, nekuda kwehukuru uye huremu hwawo, haana kufambiswa kana ashandiswa, asi kungochinja varidzi. Kutengeserana kwega kwega "kwainyorwa" nemuromo mukati menharaunda diki, nenhoroondo yemuridzi wedombo ichiva ruzivo rwakawanda. Pakupedzisira, kutengeserana "nhoroondo"/"ledger" yakava iyo chete chikamu chakakosha. Dombo rakambodonhedzwa neigwa richiriendesa kuYap rikanyura. Iro dombo rainzi richiri mari sezvo richiripo, kunyangwe pasina akamboriona kana kuwana mari kubva ipapo.
Izvi zvinonyanya kukosha nekuti zvinoratidza mashandisirwo anongoitika ega redhisheni yekutengeserana. Ledger yakagovewa nemuromo pakati pevagari uye ichinzi ndeyamuridzi uye midziyo yakagoverwa pasina dombo rimwe chete rinofamba; munhu wose akabvumirana nazvo uye kubvumirana kwakaumbwa. Iyi ndiyo nzira yatingaita nayo kuenzanisa nemabasa eBitcoin blockchain; ibhuku rakagovaniswa rekutengeserana kwese, rakachengetwa panguva imwe chete pazviuru zvemakomputa (node) pasi rose. [^4
Imwe yakafanana neBitcoin ndiko kusikwa kweRai dombo, iro raive basa rakasimba uye chimiro chehumbowo-hwe-basa. Matombo akavezwa nemidziyo yemaoko, akacherwa mhiri kwemakungwa uye akaunzwa kuchitsuwa kuburikidza neigwa. Kamwe matombo eRai akave nyore kugadzira nehunyanzvi hwemazuva ano, akave mashoma anobatsira semari, nekuti akange asisiri chiratidzo chakavimbika chesimba rakashandiswa.
Matombo eRai akaonekwa nenyanzvi dzezvehupfumi dzemazuva ano semari yechinyakare, uye anowanzoshandiswa semuenzaniso kutsigira pfungwa yekuti kukosha kwemamwe marudzi emari kunogona kugoverwa chete kuburikidza nekutenda kwakagovana muukoshi hwataurwa.[^5] Mari yanhasi haina kutsigirwa nechero chinhu futi. Muchokwadi, inongogadzikwa uye kuziviswa zviri pamutemo tenda nemutemo wehurumende. Nekuda kweizvozvo, ndiyo nzira yeakaunti yatinoshandisa uye nekudaro inoonekwa seinokosha
Magadzirirwo Emari
Bhangi repakati rinofanira kuvimbwa kuti risadzikisire mari, asi nhoroondo yemari dze fiat izere nekutyorwa kwekuvimba ikoko." - Satoshi Nakamoto
Kudzidza nezveBitcoin kwakavhura ziso kwandiri. Pane nguva mbiri dzakasiyana dzehupenyu hwangu, imwe isati yasvika Bitcoin uye imwe mushure meBitcoin. Ndiri kuona zvinhu nenzira yakasiyana zvachose nhasi. Muchinangwa changu chekunzwisisa Bitcoin, ini ndaifanira kutanga ndanzwisisa iyo sisitimu yemari iripo. Ndeupi musiyano uripo pakati pemasisitimu emari akaita seUSD kana Euro neBitcoin? Chii chinonzi inflation (kukwira kwemitengo)? Nderipi basa riri kuitwa nemabhanga makuru, zvichingodaro? Zvinokatyamadza kuti isu hatidzidze pfungwa idzi muchikoro, asi uku kushomeka kwedzidzo kunogona, zvinosiririsa, kuve nemaune.
180 mari inoshandiswa munyika zana nemakumi mapfumbamwe neshanu pasirese. Mari ndiyo hurongwa hwemari inoshandiswa zvakajairika, inotsanangurwa nehurumende. Mazhinji masimba anotsanangura mari yavo yenyika setenderi yepamutemo; imari inoziviswa nemutemo kuti inoshanda pakubhadhara zvikwereti zvisingagoni kurambwa senzira yekubhadhara.
Mari dzese zana nemakumi masere - US Dollar, Euro, Yen uye Pound Sterling, semuenzaniso - inogona kutsanangurwa seiri mukati mechikamu chinonzi 'fiat money'. Kubva 1971, hapana kana imwe yeiyi mari yefiat yakatsigirwa negoridhe kana neimwewo chinhu chinobatika. Mari ine kukosha nekuti tinotenda mairi. Mari mutauro wekuratidza kukosha kwechinhu, mumagariro. Izwi rokuti fiat rinobva muchiLatin uye rinoreva kuti "ngazviitwe". Mari yazvino inogadzirwa kuburikidza nekupinda mudhijitari ledger uye ingori nhamba mumasisitimu eakaunzi. Iko hakuna kusikwa kweiyo chaiyo-yenyika kubereka shure kwayo.
Ndiani anotarisira kusikwa kwemari? Musanganiswa wehurumende nemabhanga epakati, pamwe nemabhangi ekutengesa. Iyo yepakati, ine hierarchical system ine vachengeti vemagedhi. Iko hakuna chibvumirano pamutengo wekupa kana chiyero chekuburitsa.
Fiat ndiyo "mari nechirevo"; inotungamirirwa nechisimba kuburikidza nekutyisidzira kwehurumende kwemhirizhonga. Kukosha kuri kuchengetedzwa nekugadzirwa kwemutero usingaperi waunogona kungogutsa nemari yefiat uye nemisika inotungamirwa nehurumende, pamwe chete nemitemo yepamutemo yematende uye mutemo wemitero.
Mari inogadzirwa nemabhanga makuru nenzira yemari yemapepa nemari.
Mabhangi epakati anotenga zvinhu uye zvisungo kubva pamusika wakavhurika, mari inoyerera ichipinda muhurongwa.
Mari inogadzirwa kuburikidza nekukurudzira kwehurumende, kuburikidza nemabhenefiti, ma grants uye bail out.
Mari inogadzirwa nemabhanga ekutengesa kuburikidza nezvikwereti.
Mari Inogadzirwa Nechikwereti
Pfungwa yekupedzisira ndiyo yatinoziva tese. Ndiwo matorero atinoita chikwereti kutenga imba, kutanga bhizinesi kana kutenga mota. Nzira yacho iri nyore, asi kune avo vakatova neropafadzo. Kana usingakwanise kuisa pamberi sechibatiso sechibatiso, uri muridzi webhizinesi diki, hauna basa raunowana rinogara rakagadziriswa, kana kuti uri mukadzi munyika umo vakadzi vachiri kurambidzwa kuva nemidziyo chero ipi zvayo, saka haungadaro. kodzera kuwana chikwereti kubhangi rako. Kana iwe ukawana chikwereti, bhangi rinogadzirisa dhijitari redhijitari uye rinowedzera mari yechikwereti kuakaundi yaro. Iwe wobva wavakwereta chikwereti pamwe nechiyero chekukwereta. Iwe zvino unofanirwa kubuda uye kushanda kana kutengesa chimwe chinhu kuti ukwanise kubhadhara chikwereti pamwe nemubereko. Izvo zvakanyanya kune mabhanga. Hapana chavano wedzera, asi tora mari yechibvumirano chako chechikwereti uye mubereko pakubhadhara kwako.
Pamusoro pazvo, pane chimwe chinonzi fractional-reserve banking. Izvi zvinoita kuti mabhanga akwanise kukweretesa mari yakawanda kudarika yavanobata mumatura kana masaramusi muakaundi yavo kubhanga guru renyika. Mari shoma iyo mabhanga anofanira kubata mumidziyo inobatika, inonzi "reserve ratio", inotarwa nebhanga guru. Mwero uyu unosiyana munyika nenyika. Munharaunda yeEuro, mabhanga anofanirwa kubata isingasviki 1% panguva yekunyora. Muna Kurume 2020 iyo FED yakabvisa nzira diki yekuchengetera zvinodiwa nekuda kweCOVID-19 denda. Canada, UK, New Zealand, Australia, Sweden neHong Kong zvese hazvina kuchengetwa zvinodiwa. Dai mumwe nemumwe wedu aizoenda kubhanga nhasi kunokumbira kubvisa mari yedu, hurongwa hwekubhanga hwaizoparara. Nekuda kwekuti mabhanga akweretesa mari yakawanda kudarika yavanayo, havangakwanise kukudzosera mari yako.
Muna 2020 chikwereti chepasi rose chakakwira neinoshamisa 24 tiririyoni kusvika 281 tiririyoni USD, kana 355% yeGDP yepasirese. [^6]
![Chikwereti-ku-GDP ratios](zviwanikwa/_Debt-to-GDP-ratio-2020.jpg)
Mabahanga Makuru seVakweretesi veLast Resort
Mabhanga ekugadzira upfumi anogona uye akadaidzira rubatsiro rwebhanga guru sevakweretesi vekupedzisira. Muna 2008/2009 mabhanga, aikonzera dambudziko remari pasi rose, akawana mari yechibatiso. Vakanunurwa nekuti "vakange vakanyanya kukundikana". Uye vakaita sei nemari yacho? Vakatengazve mashares mumakambani avo. Hapana "chakadonha" pasi muhupfumi. Mukaha uri pakati pevapfumi nevarombo wakaramba uchikura.
Mabhanga epakati anonzi vakweretesi vekupedzisira. Chinangwa ndechekudzivirira kusagadzikana kwehupfumi nekuda kwekunetseka kwemari, uye mabhanga anomhanya achipararira kubva kune rimwe bhanga kuenda kune rinotevera nekuda kwekushaikwa kwemari. Vashandi vezvemari vakaita semabhanga vanoziva kuti mabhanga epakati anozofanira kuvabvisa, izvo zvinotungamira kunjodzi yehunhu - kutora njodzi zvakanyanya nevabhengi nevaisiri mari.
Kugadzirwa kwemari yefeki kuburikidza nemabhanga makuru kwakavhara kukanganisa mumusika. Nekuda kwemafashama uye kushandiswa kwehurongwa hwemari nemari yakachipa, hapasisina nzira yekuwana mutengo inonzwisisika. Kazhinji, kupa uye kudiwa kunotarisisa kukosha kwezvinhu uye zvigadzirwa asi, mumusika wakakanganiswa uye wakashandiswa, hapana nzvimbo yekuwanikwa kwemutengo wakanaka. Vepasi rose vepakati vari kubhadhara makaro evakuru vezvemari ayo, zvakare, ari kudyiswa nehurongwa hwakaora hwekusika mari.
Iwe, semunhu, wakambobvisiswa mari yechibatiso here? Uye kana iwe uine, iwe ungaita chinhu chimwe chete kakawanda, kubiridzira hurongwa uchiziva kuti pane sarudzo yekupedzisira, iyo ichagara ichikubvisa? Izvi ndizvo chaizvo zvinoitwa nemabhanga, Wall Street, Hedge Funds uye magweta avo ekutsvaga rutsigiro nguva dzose, achibatsirwa nemabhanga makuru pasi rese.
Kazhinji, mabhanga makuru anobata matura kana paine njodzi, anoisa mitero yemitengo, uye kugovera mari yekukurudzira kana kunonoka hupfumi mushure mezviitiko zvinokanganisa senge kuvhunduka kana hondo. mamiriro ezveupfumi enyika dzine hutongi hwejekerere. Uku ndiko kupokana kwehutongi hwegutsaruzhinji. Utongi hwemari hwakadaro hunoshanda zvinopfuura tsika nemiganhu yedhemokirasi. [^7]
Bhuku raNaomi Prins rakapinda mundangariro yeWall Street, richiratidza kuti chimiro chemari chemari chakamira sei kune vatengesi vanodirana kubheji hombe rinotevera, zvisinei nemateki. Pamusoro pezvo, _vanhu vakafanana_ nemhuri vakaramba vachiuya, vachichovha bhasikoro nemuWall Street neWashington. Vakapesvedzera hupfumi hwaive pasi pavo kubva pakakwirira pakakwirira pazvinzvimbo, mari dzepachivande nezvinzvimbo zvehurumende, vachibvisa mitemo yakamira munzira yavo nekutsvaga maburi kuburikidza nevamwe. Mabhanga ega ega akajairisa kushandiswa kwemusika. Mabhanga epakati akaiita hunyanzvi, isina miganhu." [^8]
Kuwedzera Kwemari
Ngatitorei US Dollar semuenzaniso kune ese mafiat currencies. Nekuda kweiyo mari inopa inflation, iyo yakawanda USD inowanikwa, iyo shoma kukosha ine imwe chete. Fungidzira mari yepepa sechinhu chinotengeswa semhangura. Kana mhangura ikawanda pamusika, kupfuura pakudikamwa, mutengo wendarira unoderera; kukosha kwayo kuri kuderera. Zvimwe chetezvo kune banknote yako. Kukosha kwefiat mari kunotarwa nekupa uye kudiwa zvakare. Kana iwe ukawedzera kugovera uye kudiwa kunoramba kwakafanana, kukosha kwechimwe chikwata kunoderera.
Mari inopihwa nemhando dzakasiyana siyana dzemari dzinowanzo kurondedzerwa seMs, senge M0 (base money), M1, M2 neM3. Tsanangudzo dzinogona kusiyana zvishoma munyika dzakasiyana.
Huwandu hwemari (M0) ndiyo huwandu hwemari iri mubepa chairo uye koini iri kutenderera mumaoko everuzhinji kana muchimiro chemari yekubhanga yekutengeserana inochengetwa mumatura ebhanga guru renyika. [^9]
Chero bedzi iwe uchibata mari, chinhu chakaita se bitcoin, chivakwa chaunacho. Kana iwe ukatora mari yako woichengeta kubhangi, une chikumbiro, asi iwe hausisina mari yacho. Zvakafanana ne bitcoin pakutsinhana.
Chero imwe fiat mari yekupihwa (M1, M2, M3) inoumbwa nezvikumbiro pamari yekutanga. [^10]
M1 inosanganisira M0, madhipoziti anodiwa, cheki dzevafambi, uye mamwe madhipoziti anotarisika, anoshandurwa nyore kuita mari.
M2 inosanganisira M0, M1, kuchengetedzwa kwemusika wemari, mutual funds uye mamwe madhipoziti nguva. Iyi midziyo haina mvura shoma pane M1 uye haina kukodzera semasvikiro ekuchinjana, asi inogona kukurumidza kushandurwa kuita mari kana kutarisa madhipoziti. M2 inotariswa zvakanyanya sechiratidzo chekupa mari uye inflation yeramangwana, uye sechinangwa chepakati pebhangi rezvemari.
Huwandu hweM2 mari iri kutenderera muUS yaive ** 19.7 trillion USD ** muna Kukadzi 2021. [^ 11] Tarisa kukura mu2020.
![M2 Kukura kwemari yakachengetedzeka USA, 2021 ](zviwanikwa/_M2-money-stock-US-2021.png)
Isu tinozvigamuchira sechinhu chakajairika nekuti isu tinofungidzira kuti hachizombopera. Sisitimu yamabhanga yekuchengetedza mari muzvikamu yakashanda pasi rose kwemazana emakore (kutanga goridhe-backed, uyezve zvachose fiat-based), kunyange zvazvo pane dzimwe nguva inflation zviitiko munzira. kugadzirisa zvishoma zvinhu.
Imwe neimwe unit yefiat currency yakaderera inosvika 99% mukukosha kana kupfuura pamusoro pemakumi emakore akawanda. Izvi zvinoreva kuti vatengesi vangangoda kuwana chiyero chemubereko chinodarika marates ekukwira kwemitengo (iyo isiri kuitika parizvino), kana kuti ivo vanofanirwa kutenga mainvestimenti pachinzvimbo, izvo zvinowedzera kukosha kwemasheya uye zvinoverengeka se real estate zvichienzaniswa nekuyerera kwavo kwemari uye kusunda. kukwidza mitengo yezvinhu zvinoshomeka senge art yakanaka." [^12]
Chinowedzera kukwira kwemari inyaya yekuti huwandu hwevanhu muUS nedzimwe nyika dzekumavirira hahusi kukura pamwero wakafanana nekuwanikwa kwemari. "Vanhu veUnited States vaiwanzokura pamwe ne1.5% pagore, uye ikozvino inokura pedyo ne0.5% pagore. Izvi zvakakosha zvikuru. Zvichakadaro, mari yakawanda inokwira 25% gore negore, uye iri munzira yekukwira 75% + mumakore mashanu mune ramangwana. " [^13]
Kutaura chokwadi, kukwira kwemari kunoitika apo mari inotengeswa inodarika GDP yezita, iyo inosanganisira kukura kwevanhu uye kubudirira. Consumer Price Index yekuUSA inoratidza kuti mitengo yezvinhu yakakwira kubva kukosha kwemari kwakaderera. ![Consumer Price Index US 2020](zvishandiso/_Consumer-Price-index-US-2021.png) [^14]
Chirongwa chePonzi
Ponzi scheme: "Chimiro chekubiridzira umo kutenda mukubudirira kwebhizimisi rekunyepedzera kunosimudzirwa nekubhadhara kwekukurumidza kudzoka kune vekutanga vanoisa mari kubva pamari inoiswa nevamwe." - **Oxford English Dictionary**
Vavengi veBitcoin vanozvidaidza kuti Ponzi scheme. Ini ndinoti, ivo vangave vasinganzwisise Bitcoin kana kuti chaiyo Ponzi system chii, kana vane chido cheBitcoin chisingabudiriri. Charles Ponzi akasungwa muUS muna 1920 nekutora mamiriyoni makumi maviri emadhora kubva kumakumi ezviuru zvevakabatwa. Chivimbiso chake chaive chekuwedzera mari yavo nekaviri mukati memwedzi mitatu. Mukudzorera mari, vatengesi vakagamuchira zvinyorwa zvevimbiso izvo zvakavimbisa mari yepakutanga pamwe ne50 muzana mubereko. Aya manotsi akanga aine siginicha yeinki yaPonzi. Vazhinji vaidaidza kwavari se "Ponzi notes".
Bhizimisi rangu rakanga riri nyore. Wakanga uri mutambo wekare wokubira Peter kuti abhadhare Paul. Waizondipa zana remadhora uye ndaizokupa tsamba yekukubhadhara madhora zana nemakumi mashanu mumwedzi mitatu… inokosha kupfuura mari yeAmerica…Ipapo dambudziko rakauya. Chinhu chose chakaparara. - **Charles Ponzi**
Kana iwe uchida kuziva zvakawanda, [teerera kuchikamu changu chepodcast nezve hupenyu uye nyaya yaCharles Ponzi akazvarwa muItaly](https://anita.link/ponzi). Unogona kuzviwana pa https://anita.link/ponzi.
Mamiriro ePonzi Scheme
Chirongwa chePonzi chine mutambi wepakati, mutungamiri kana sangano rinounganidza mari uye rinomhanya kumagumo.
Ponzi zvirongwa hazvitaridzike kana kujeka. Hapana mumwe kunze kwemusiki anoziva zvinoitika kumari.
Chirongwa chePonzi chinoburitsa mari kusvika yatyoka - hapana muganho wekupa.
Kuoma mukubhadhara vatengesi: iyo mari yakawanda inoyerera muchirongwa, mari yakawanda inofanirwa kubhadharwa, uye zvakanyanya kuoma kuti musiki amise muchina.
Iyo system inofanirwa kutyora rimwe zuva, hapana nzira yekubuda nayo.
Matsotsi anowana mari yekukweretesa mari pasina mupiro chaiwo mukuita kwehupfumi hwenyika.
Makaro ari kufambisa chirongwa chePonzi. Retail vatengesi vanokurumidza kupinda, vanowana mubereko uye vanoudza vamwe, vanodawo kupfuma nekukurumidza.
Ngatienzanisei maitiro aya nehurongwa hwanhasi hwekugadzira mari.
** Hunhu hweFiat Mari Kusikwa **
Vatambi vepakati vakaita sehurumende, mabhanga makuru uye mabhanga ekutengesa vanogadzira mari.
Iyo sisitimu yemari haitaridzike kana kujeka.
Hapana muganhu wekupa mari.
Kuomerwa mukudzorera vatengesi: nekuda kweiyo fractional-reserve banking system, kana chete 20% yevatengi vemabhangi uko kukumbira kubhadhara panguva imwe chete iyo bhangi inopinda mumatambudziko uye ichati "kwete" kuti ubvise. Izvi zvinoitika nguva nenguva pasirese uye zvakaitika kune mamwe mabhanga eUS kutanga kwa2020 panguva yekuvharwa kwedenda.
Iyo system inofanirwa kutyora rimwe zuva, hapana nzira yekubuda nayo.
Mabhanga anowana mari yekukweretesa mari pasina mupiro chaiwo mukuita kwehupfumi hwenyika.
Makaro ari kutyaira fiat system. Vemari vepamusoro vanogashira zvikwereti zvakachipa nekuti vane zvibatiso zvekutenga zvimwe zvibatiso uye kukura hupfumi hwavo nesimba.
Iyo Chaiyo Ponzi Scheme
Iyo chete yakafanana pakati peBitcoin nePonzi chirongwa ndeye netiweki mhedzisiro yekukara. Asi kusiyana nePonzi, unogona kubata makiyi e bitcoin yako pachako. Iko hakuna bhangi kana centralized mutambi anodzora bitcoin yako.
Iyo chete yakafanana pakati peBitcoin nePonzi chirongwa ndeye network mhedzisiro yekukara. Asi kusiyana nePonzi, unogona kubata makiyi e bitcoin yako pachako. Iko hakuna bhangi kana centralized mutambi anodzora bitcoin yako.
Kuburitswa kweBitcoin kunofanotemerwa nealgorithm iyo vese vatambi muBitcoin vakabvumirana uye vakachengeteka kuburikidza neanoshanda node. Haikwanise kuchinjwa pasina mvumo yepasi rose yeBitcoin nharaunda. Sezvo 21 mamiriyoni bitcoin muganhu ndeimwe yezvinhu zvakakosha zveBitcoin, chibvumirano chekuchinja chichave chakaoma zvikuru kana kunyange chisingagoneki kubudirira.
Mabhangi epakati ari kutarisa mamiriro ezvemari enyika dzese pasirese. Havana kusarudzwa, asi vanoita sehurumende dziri kuedza kudzora misika yose yemari.
Chiitiko cheCantillon chakatsanangurwa neIrish-French economist Richard Cantillon munenge muna 1730. Akataura kuti inflation inoitika zvishoma nezvishoma uye kuti kutsva kwemari yakagadzirwa nemabhangi kune maitiro emunharaunda pamusoro pekukwira kwemitengo, kupa mubayiro vabhengi nevatambi vepedyo kuburikidza nekugadzira mari nemaoko. kubatsira vari pedyo nekwakabva mari.
Dambudziko reFed uye mushure mematambudziko emari mitemo, yakagamuchirwa nemamwe mabhanga makuru epakati, yaifanirwa kudonha" kune vanhu vazhinji. Izvo hazvina kuitika. Vakuru vepasi rose vaiziva izvi panguva iyoyo, uye ivo vanozviziva zvakanyanya iye zvino. . Muna Ndira 2017, World Economic Forum yakabvuma kuti kukwira kwekusaenzana kuri kutyisidzira hupfumi hwenyika. Vadyidzani ava vanonyandura kusaenzana nokuti zvinobatsira ivo uye kuchengetedzwa kwemasimba avo epasi rose anokuvadza zvinhu zvose uye munhu wose. - **Nomi Prins** [^15]
Kuguma kweKukura Kwerudzi Urwu
Kusaenzana kwehupfumi kuri kuwedzera mumazana emakore apfuura pamwe chete nekutengesa uye kuita mari kwezviwanikwa. Hapana chinosara kuti chipedzwe. Tiri kurarama kuburikidza nekurwira zviwanikwa, kumikana yakaenzana kurwisa kugadzwa uye vepamusoro vanozvipfumisa kuburikidza nehuwori uye kuwana mari.
Zvimwe zvakakonzerwa nedambudziko rezvemari uye kubatana kwebhangi guru kwaiva kuwedzera kwekunetseka kwehupfumi uko kwakakonzera kushanduka kune nyika, kubva kuBrazil kuenda kuGreat Britain kusvika kuUnited States. Kuvhundutsa kweBrexit muUnited Kingdom kwakadzokorora pasi rose sevavhoti. vakasiya hutungamiri hwange huripo nematongerwo ahwo ehupfumi akakundikana.MuUnited States, kukunda kwesarudzo kwaDonald Trump, bhiriyoniya mutungamiri we'antiestablishment', kwakava kumwe kuratidzwa kwemaitiro aya.Mavhoti makuru aya haana kukonzerwa nemutemo wemabhanga epakati asi zvakanangana aiva maeffects. [^16]
Kuparadzana kuri kukura pakati pevapfumi nevarombo kunobva pane yedu yemazuva ano hurongwa hwemari, iyo ndiyo chaiyo Ponzi chirongwa. Mabhengi epakati haana kusarudzwa nedemocracy, asi ivo vanosarudza mamiriro ezvemari enyika. Vemabhangi neshamwari dzavo vari kuita purofiti kubva kune ino system. Yave nguva yeimwe nzira: yakasarudzika, yakavhurika, isina kwayakarerekera, yakajeka, isingachinjiki, isiri-inflatable uye yekubatana fomu yemari yevanhu: Bitcoin.
Nhasi Petrodollar System
Zvino zvatakurukura kuti mari inogadzirwa sei, ngatinyure tichipinda munyika yehondo dzemari uye kuti hurongwa uhu hwemari yenyika hwakasarudzika sei uye, munhoroondo, hwakatongwa nehumambo hwakasiyana.
Nhoroondo yehondo dzemari yakareba. "Mukati mezana remakore rapfuura nyika yakabva kune yegoridhe standard system, kuenda kuBretton Woods system, kuenda kuPetrodollar system. Imwe neimwe system yainyanya kudzururwa kubva mukati pane kuburutswa kunze, uye nguva imwe neimwe nzira ichichinjirwa kune imwe, yakakosha uye kudzikisira kwemari kwakaitika."[^17]
Ukuru hwemari hweBritain hwakatangira muna 1871 kusvika kuHondo Yenyika I. Kare ikako mari yenyika yakanga yakanamirwa kundarama. Mushure menguva yehondo, apo simba remari rakatanga kudzikisira, United States yakabuda semuzinda wesimba remari mushure mekukunda kwemubatanidzwa muHondo Yenyika yechipiri. Iyo Bretton Woods system, yakavambwa muna 1944, yaive muenzaniso wekutanga wehurongwa hwemari hwakakurukurwa zvizere, hwakagadzirirwa kutonga hukama hwemari pakati penyika dzakazvimirira. Yakaisa hurongwa hwemitemo, masangano, uye maitiro ekugadzirisa hurongwa hwemari hwepasi rose, seInternational Monetary Fund (IMF). United States, iyo yaitonga zvikamu zviviri muzvitatu zvegoridhe repasi rose, yakaramba ichiti hurongwa hweBretton Woods huri pagoridhe nedhora rekuAmerica. Vamiriri veSoviet vakapinda musangano uyu asi vakazoramba kubvumidza zvibvumirano zvekupedzisira, vachisimbirira kuti masangano avakagadzira aive "mapazi eWall Street". Izvi zvinogona kududzirwa sepamavambo eCold War.
Musi wa15 Nyamavhuvhu 1971, United States, inotungamirwa naMutungamiriri Richard Nixon, yakamisa kuchinjika kwedhora rekuAmerica kuenda kugoridhe, zvichiunza hurongwa hweBretton Woods kumagumo uye kupa dhora mari yefiat. Panguva imwecheteyo, mari zhinji dzakagadziriswa (senge pondo sterling) dzakavawo dzakasununguka-inoyerera.
Mazuva ano hurongwa hwemari hwakavakirwa paPetrodollar. Lyn Alden anotsanangura izvi muchinyorwa chake "The Structure of the Global Monetary System":
Kutanga muna 1971 mushure mekuparara kweBretton Woods system, mari pasi rose yakava fiat currencies, uye hurongwa hwemari hwepasi rose hwakava husina kurongeka. Iyi yakanga iri nguva yokutanga munhoroondo yevanhu kuti izvi zvakaitika, apo mari yose munyika panguva imwe chete iyo yakashandurwa mumapepa asina kutsigirwa.
Fiat currency inzira yemari umo pasina chinhu chinokosha mumari yacho pachayo; ingori bepa, simbi dzesimbi dzakachipa, kana zvidimbu zvedhijitari zveruzivo. Iine kukosha nekuti hurumende inozivisa kuti ine kukosha uye kuti zviri pamutemo tenda kubhadhara zvinhu zvese zvinosanganisira mitero.
Nyika inogona kumanikidza kushandiswa kwemari yefiat senzira yekutsinhana uye chikamu cheakaundi mukati menyika yavo nekuita kuti mutero wese ubhadharwe chete nemari iyoyo, kana nekudzika mimwe mitemo yekuwedzera kukakavara, kana mune dzimwe nguva kurambidzwa zvachose, zvimwe. nzira dzekuchinjana uye mayunitsi eakaundi. Kana mari yavo iine dambudziko rakakura zvakakwana, zvakadaro, sezvakangoita kune misika zhinji iri kusimukira, musika mutema uchakura kune dzimwe nzira dzekutsinhana, dzakadai semari yekunze kana midziyo yakaoma.
Mari yefiat inogona kutarisana nezvinetso zvakanyanya kana ichiedza kushandiswa kunze kwenyika yayo. Neiko mabhizimisi nehurumende mune dzimwe nyika vachifanira kugamuchira zvidimbu zvamapepa, zvinogona kudhindwa nokusingaperi nehurumende yokumwe uye vasina tsigiro yakasimba, senzira yokubhadhara zvinhu zvavo zvinokosha namabasa? Pasina tsigiro chaiyo, chii chakakodzera? Sei muchitengesera mafuta kune vatorwa nebepa?
Mukutanga kwema1970, pakanga paine makakatanwa akasiyana ezvematongerwo enyika anosanganisira Yom Kippur War uye OPEC oiri embargo. Muna 1974, zvisinei, United States neSaudi Arabia dzakasvika chibvumirano, uye kubva ipapo, nyika yakanga yaiswa pagadziriro yepetrodollar; nzira yakachenjera yekuita kuti pasi rose fiat currency system ishande zvakanaka zvakakwana ....Ne petrodollar system, Saudi Arabia (nedzimwe nyika dziri muOPEC) vanotengesa mafuta avo chete mumadhora mukuchinjana nekuchengetedzwa kweU. Kunyange kana France ichida kutenga mafuta kubva kuSaudi Arabia, semuenzaniso, vanozviita mumadhora .... Mukudzoka, United States inoshandisa iyo isingaenzaniswi yemvura yebhuruu-navy kuchengetedza nzira dzekutakura pasi rose, uye kuchengetedza geopolitical status quo nemauto. kuita kana kutyisidzira kwazvinoita sezvinodiwa....Vamwe vedu, kunyanya padyo nepamusoro pemanera emari, tinobatsirwa zvakananga kana zvisina kunanga kubva kune ino. Vanhu vekuAmerica vanoshanda zvakatenderedza mari, hurumende, hutano, uye tekinoroji vanowana akawanda mabhenefiti ekugara musimba rehegemonic, pasina zvinokanganisa. Nekune rimwe divi, vanhu vekuAmerica vanogadzira zvigadzirwa zvemuviri havawanzo batsiri, nekuti vakarasikirwa nemabasa kana kudzvinyirirwa mari yavo, uye nekudaro havana kubatsirwa kubva pane zvavakawana. Uye kunze kweUnited States, nyika dzinotengesa kunze kwenyika dzinobatsirwa nehurongwa, nepo nyika dzisingafarire magadzirirwo emari yepasi rose hadzina zvakawanda zvekuita nezvazvo, kunze kwekunge dzakura zvakakwana seRussia neChina. "[^18]
Tave muhondo dzemari kwemakumi emakore akawanda. Ndeipi mari yakasimba? Inyika ipi inogona kuwana zvikomborero zvakawanda kubva mukushandisa mari yayo? Iyo Euro, iyo US Dollar, iyo Chinese Yuan? Kana kunyange Facebook's Diem? Mari yemubatanidzwa ndiye mutambi mutsva, akasimba pamusika. Kuti vachengetedze masimba avo mabhanga epakati akatanga kushanda pamari yavo yedhijitari (CBDCs).
![Nzira itsva dzemari dziri kubuda](zvishandiso/_new-forms-money.png) [^19]
Bitcoin ndiyo nzira yedu kune ino system. Kuchengetedza kuvanzika kwedu munguva ino yedhijitari, kuvhota kusabatwa zvisina kunaka kwesimba rekutonga muhurongwa hwazvino, uye kupa vanhu vanogara mumatunhu ane hutongi ane vatongi vane huwori mikana yakafanana yekutora chikamu muhurongwa hwehupfumi. Bitcoin inzira yekudzivirira, chishandiso chatinogona kuchengetedza nacho kodzero yevanhu yekusununguka kwekutengeserana uye kuvanzika.

103-bitcoin-money-for-the-digital-age

Bitcoin - Mari yeDigital Age
Kana vanhu vakabvunza kuti Bitcoin chii, mhinduro yangu yekutanga uye pfupi ndeye: Bitcoin idhijitari mari. Zvakafanana nemabhengi nemari dziri muhomwe yako. Ndezvako, hapana anogona kukukonesa kuzvishandisa. Kana ukashandisa mari kutenga bhasikoro, unopa mutengesi mabhengi ako nemari. Haufanire kuvimba nemutengesi, nekuti watora bhasikoro rako uye chitoro chakawana mari yayo. Chibvumirano chinovharwa pasina bhangi, chitupa kana kadhi rechikwereti.
Izvo zvakafanana ndezvechokwadi kune bitcoin. Paunotenga chimwe chinhu, paInternet kana muchitoro uye uchibhadhara ne bitcoin, kukosha kwauri kutumira kunofamba zvakananga kubva kwauri kuenda kune mumwe munhu. Pasina bhangi, pasina PayPal uye pasina makadhi echikwereti, kutengeserana kunoramba kwakachengeteka, kusingavimbike uye kusingakanganwike - iyi ishanduko.
Iyo Bitcoin network ndeye yakavhurika sosi software uye haisi yemunhu. Chinhu chakanaka. Iko hakuna kambani kuseri kweBitcoin. Chero ani zvake anogona kudhawunirodha, kumhanya uye kuona kodhi, uye kuita mazano ekuvandudza pasina kukumbira mvumo. Chero sarudzo yekuti uye sei kuita shanduko kumitemo inofanira kuitwa nekubvumirana kwevose vanobatanidzwa. Iko hakuna hierarchy. Bitcoin inogadzira kuvimba kuburikidza nekubatanidza maitiro kubva munzvimbo dzakasiyana dzesainzi: cryptography, network yakagoverwa pasi rose komputa, isingachinjike dhatabhesi yezvese matransaction (blockchain) uye mutambo-theory incentive system yekuchengetedza network uye kuburitsa mari (migodhi).
Kusiyana nemari yefiat seEuro kana USD, iyo inodzorwa nemabhangi avo epakati, iyi ihurongwa hutsva zvachose. Kuvimbika hakubvi pahuerarchical, yezvematongerwo enyika asi yakavakirwa pamasvomhu, cryptography, uye inozvitonga yekubvumirana system.
Bitcoin yakavakirwa pamitemo yakatarwa. Iyo inozvitonga yega system, yakavakirwa pamasvomhu uye cryptography iri kumanikidza kuburitswa kwemari ichangobva kuumbwa pahwaro hweprotocol pasina kupindira kwevanhu. Censorship yetransaction kana mibairo yakaipa haigoneki, saka inzira yakavimbika yekuchengetedza kukosha uye midziyo.

104-the-history-of-bitcoin

Nhoroondo yeBitcoin
Dambudziko remari remuUS ra2007-2008 raive mhedzisiro yehurongwa hwekubhanga hwakasununguka umo masimba akaiswa mumaoko evafungidziri vashoma. [^20]
Dambudziko rezvemari ra2007-2008 iro rakaparadza hupfumi hwepasi rose rakabatidzwa nehurongwa hwekubhanga hwakashata muUnited States. Mukupindura, vachifudzwa neFed, mabhanga epakati enyika dzeG7 akafunga nezve nzira isingaperi yekugadzira mari - muhupamhi. chiedza chezuva. [^21]
Musi waOctober 31 2008, pakuuya kwematambudziko makuru emari pasi rose akamboona, mumwe munhu achienda nezita remanyepo Satoshi Nakamoto akabudisa bepa chena rainzi "Bitcoin: Peer-to-Peer Electronic Cash System" pane domain bitcoin.org uye akakurudzira nzira itsva yedhijitari yemari.
Musi waNdira 3 2009, nzvimbo yekutanga yeruzhinji yeBitcoin, inonzi Genesis Block, yakacherwa. Satoshi akasiya meseji mairi: "Chancellor ari kumucheto kwechipiri chekubhadhara mari kumabhangi", wanga uri musoro wepepanhau remazuva ese, The Times, kuUK pazuva rimwe chetero. Ndiyo timestamp inoratidza kutanga kweBitcoin uye inoratidza chinangwa chekuti inofanira kunge iri imwe nzira kune yazvino yebhangi uye hurongwa hwemari, iyo yaunoda kuvimba nevamiriri kana iwe uchida kugadzirisa kubhadhara kwemagetsi.
Musi waChikumi 9 2021, bitcoin yakave yepamutemo nyoro muEl Salvador.
Kubva kuma1990, nyanzvi dzemakomputa, nyanzvi dzemasvomhu uye ma cryptographer - kusanganisira vamwe vakadzi - vanga vachishanda pane pfungwa dzekugadzira mari yedhijitari. Bitcoin inogona kugadzirwa nekuti yakavakirwa pane akakosha matekinoroji evakaitangira.
Mapurojekiti ecryto curency Pamberi peBitcoin
Zvikamu zvemashoko anotevera zvakabatanidzwa muSatoshi Nakamoto's Bitcoin white paper.
![Cryptocurrency mapurojekiti pamberi peBitcoin](zviwanikwa/_History-of-Bitcoin.png)[^22]
**Paruzhinji uye Akazvimiririra Makiyi maviri** Muna 1990 David Chaum aive nehanya nehunhu hweveruzhinji uye kuvhura mukana wekubhadhara online uye ruzivo rwemunhu. Akavamba "Digicash", mubatanidzwa uye mari yemagetsi yezita rimwe chete, iyo yakashandisa nzira yecryptographic pamwe nemakiyi epachivande uye eruzhinji kuti asazivikanwe kutengeserana. Kushandiswa kwemasiginecha - eruzhinji neakavanzika makiyi maviri - kwakava kwakakosha mukusimudzira mari yemagetsi neBitcoin. 
**Umbowo-hwe-Basa**
Mapiramidhi eEgypt chiratidzo chebasa. Ivo chiratidzo cheEgypt tsika, hupfumi uye sangano.
Nekuuya kweinternet uye email kwakauya dambudziko rekutumirwa mameseji nevanhu vausingazive iwe usina kuzvitendera. Kurwisa dambudziko iri, mubepa ravo ra1992 "Pricing via Processing or Combatting Junk Mail", Cynthia Dwork naMoni Naor vakaronga zano "...kuda kuti mushandisi averenge zvine mwero zvakaoma, asi zvisingaite basa. ." vasati vakwanisa kutumira maemail. Zvaireva kuti, kana mumwe munhu achida kutumira maemail akawanda panguva imwe chete, komputa yaizoda kugadzirisa dambudziko remasvomhu. Izvi zvinotora nguva uye kushanda nesimba uye zvakachengetedza spammers kubva pakutumira mameseji mukukurumidza kutevedzana.
Muna 1997 Adam Back akapa zano rakafanana rinonzi "Hashcash". Satoshi Nakamoto akaisa Hashcash sehumbowo-hwe-basa system inoshandiswa muBitcoin. Basa raAdam Back rinotaurwa muBitcoin chena bepa. Teerera kubvunzurudzo yangu naAdam Kudzoka kubva ku2019 kwatinokurukura zano rake reHashcash uye shanduko yebasa rake kusvika kuBitcoin. Zviwane pa https://anita.link/12
Izwi rekuti "uchapupu-hwe-basa" rakatanga kuumbwa uye kunyoreswa mubepa ra1999 naMarkus Jakobsson naAri Juels.
 Hashcash yakateverwa ne "B-Money" naWei Dai muna 1998. Pfungwa yake ndiyo yekutanga kuve yakavakirwa pane network decentralized yemakomputa. Izvi zvakabikwa muBitcoin's peer-to-peer network ine makomputa anomhanyisa Bitcoin software seazere node kana miners. Peer-to-peer zvinoreva hurongwa hwevatori vechikamu vane ropafadzo dzakaenzana pasina hutongi hwemambure.
Nguva pfupi gare gare, Nick Szabo akaburitsa bepa pa "BitGold", yekutanga dhijitari mari system yakakwanisa kumhanya pasina chepakati sangano rinopa mari. Ndiye zvakare munhu wekutanga kupa bepa pa "Smart Contracts".
Kugadzirisa Dambudziko reKushandisa Kaviri
Aya matekinoroji emari akatangira aive nedambudziko guru risina kugadziriswa. Dambudziko re "kushandisa kaviri" zvinoreva kuti yakatoshandiswa mari yedhijitari inogona kushandiswa kechipiri. Fungidzira faira rePDF raunogona kukopa, kushandura uye kutumira zvachose nemutengo we zero, uchiti kopi yega yega ndiyo yekutanga. Yakadaro faira yedhijitari ingadai isina kukosha semari.
Satoshi Nakamoto's pfungwa yehungwaru yaive yekuwedzera ledger kune system nemabhuroko ane matransaction. Aya mabhuroki akasungwa pamwe chete kuburikidza ne "uchapupu-hwe-basa" migodhi, saka izwi rekuti blockchain. Uku kusungirirwa kwekutengeserana mune chaiyo nguva yekurongeka kunoita kuti bitcoin isakanganiswe uye isingachinjike.
Pakarepo kana mutambi ari muBitcoin netiweki achibiridzira, network ichaona uye kuirambidza kwechinguva. Izvi zvinoreva kuti haufanirwe kuvimba nemunhu, hapana chikonzero chemurevereri sebhangi kana PayPal. Izvi hazvireve kuti hapana scammers kunze uko kana kuti unogona kumira kuona kuti ichokwadi kana nhema, kana kurega kudzidza nezve mashandisiro eBitcoin. Zivo isimba.
Chirevo cheBitcoin ndechekuti "Usavimbe, simbisa." Izvi zvakandivhiringa zvishoma pakutanga. Kune rimwe divi, unodzidza kuti haufanirwe kuvimba nemuridziri, kune rimwe divi, unogona kuona kutengeserana kwako. Zvazvinoreva ndezvekuti: kana iwe uchida kuonesa bitcoin transaction iwe pachako, unogona kuzviita. Iwe unotofanirwa, kana iwe uine ruzivo rwehunyanzvi kumisikidza yako yega node yakazara.
Iyi ishanduko - paunongotanga kuona yako bitcoin yako ichipinda, unotoita bhangi. Izvi ndizvo zvinoitwa nemabhanga - vanosimbisa mabatiro ako mumaredhi avo. Zvisinei, unofanira kuvimba navo kuti vaite basa rakanaka. Izvi zvinogona kunge zviri kushanda zvakanaka munyika dzakabudirira, asi ruzivo rwekubhanga rwakatoipa kumatunhu mazhinji epasi. Zvino fungidzira iwe usina yakavimbika kubhengi mamiriro kana ID, asi une mbozhanhare uye kuwana internet. Pane imwe chete sarudzo yekuti iwe uchengetedze uye ushandise mari. Ingave mari yenharembozha seM-Pesa kana EcoCash muAfrica kana cryptocurrencies, kwausingade kuzvizivisa.
Vanhu vese pasi rese vane nharembozha inogonesa internet vanogona kuwana Bitcoin. Mabhangi sezvatinoaziva haadiwe kushandiswa kweBitcoin. Haufanire kukumbira chero munhu mvumo yekuve yako kana kushandisa Bitcoin. Zvese zvaunoda kuti utange i foni, internet yekubatanidza uye app yezvikwama zveBitcoin.
[^20]: Collusion, by Nomi Prins, Bold Type Books, 2019, p. 1.   [^21]: Collusion, by Nomi Prins, Bold Type Books, 2019, p. 247.   [^22]: Anita Posch, Source [The Merkle](https://themerkle.com/top-4-cryptocurrency-projects-created-ahead-of-bitcoin/), [Hashcash.org](http://www.hashcash.org/bitcoin/)

131-what-is-blockchain

Chii chinonzi Blockchain?
Iyo Bitcoin blockchain inzvimbo yeruzhinji, isingachinjike iyo inochengeterwa zvese zveBitcoin transaction. Nekudaro, "iyo blockchain" pachayo haisi iyo shanduko yetekinoroji kubudirira sezvainowanzo kutsanangurwa munhau. Sezvawakadzidza muchitsauko 1.4 "Nhoroondo yeBitcoin", kuwedzera blockchain ndicho chinhu chakazogadzirisa dambudziko rekushandisa kaviri uye kugonesa kuburitswa kwemari pane network yakachengetedzwa yakachengetedzwa. Bitcoin ine yakawanda yakapfuura tekinoroji mairi.
Muchokwadi, Satoshi Nakamoto haana kumbotaura izwi rekuti blockchain. Panzvimbo iyoyo, Nakamoto akashandisa izwi rekuti cheni yenguva, nekuti iyo ledger inonyanya kushandiswa ndeyekuchengeta zvese zvekutengesa muhurongwa hwenguva.
Sezvo izwi rekuti blockchain rave izwi rinowanzoshandiswa, ini ndichatevera mukushandisa pano. Kubva payakagadzirwa muna 2009, iyo Bitcoin blockchain haina kumbobvira yabiwa. Kubva 2009, yega yega yekutengesa yakachengetwa pa blockchain. Kuchinjisa kwese kwakaitwa muBitcoin kubva payakatanga kunochengetwa zvine hukasha pamakomputa anofungidzirwa kuti anosvika gumi kusvika zviuru zana pasi rose. Aya makomputa anofambiswa nevanhu, mayunivhesiti, kuchinjana uye zvichingodaro. Uku kubvisa wepakati kunoita kuti zviome kurwisa Bitcoin nekuti, kana ukarwisa komputa imwe uye blockchain, kuchine zviuru zvemadhatabheti akafanana anoita seyakabvumiranwa-yakavakirwa backup. Kuedza kuunza kutengeserana kwenhema kune ledger kunozoguma nekukundikana nekuti mamwe manodhi pasi rese angatadza kusvika pakubvumirana neanodhivha, achiramba rekodhi yayo yekutengeserana.
Data mukati meBitcoin blockchain iri pachena uye pachena. Kana iwe ukaita kutengeserana iwe unogona kuzvitarisa muBitcoin muongorori, iyo yakafanana nejini yekutsvaga iyo inochera dhatabhesi yekutengeserana inopesana nemapeji ewebhu. Iwe unogona kuona kukosha pane bitcoin kero yakanyorwa pane blockchain. Nemakiyi ako epachivande - blockchain yakaenzana nepassword yako - unokwanisa kuwana kero yako yeruzhinji uye unogona kufambisa kukosha kweblockchain kune imwe kero.
Iyo Bitcoin blockchain haina muridzi, chero munhu anogona kuidhawunirodha uye kuichengeta pakombuta yavo. Neiyi "node yakazara", iwe unogona zvakare kubatsira mukusimbiswa kweBitcoin network. Sei? Nekusimbisa yako kopi ye blockchain, hausi kuvimba nemumwe munhu kuti ave akatendeseka kwauri. Kuwanda kwevanhu vanoita izvi, ndiko kuwedzera kuparadzirwa uye kusimba kweBitcoin network inova.
Yakavhurika uye Inobvumidzwa Blockchains
Ndokumbira utarise musiyano uripo pakati peBitcoin, inova blockchain yakavhurika uye semuenzaniso "Diem" ( Facebook's money project token) kana yehurumende yeChina E-Yuan CBDC, iyo yakavharwa uye nechepakati blockchains.
Iyo yakavhurika blockchain inowanikwa kune vese vanhu, inogadzikiswa, yakajeka, isingadzoreki uye isina kwayakarerekera, zvichiita kuti ive mari yechimurenga iri: yepasirese, internet-yekuzvarwa sisitimu yakavhurika kune wese munhu zvisinei nezera, ruvara, rombo, murume kana nyika. . Bitcoin inogona kutoshandiswa nemichina. Hapana anogona kukutadzisa kuitumira kubva kuumwe kuenda kuumwe kutenderera pasirese.
Iyo mvumo-yakavakirwa, yakavanzika blockchain, yakavharwa, isina-pachena, zvakateedza zvakarongeka uye zvakachengetwa nechepakati. Iyo kambani kana hurumende inomhanyisa sisitimu inogona kusabvisa uye kuongorora kutengeserana kwako. Vanogona kuvhara account yako nekukutadzisa kushandisa mari yako. Iwe unotoziva nehurongwa uhu nekuti ndiwo mashandiro echinyakare emabhangi system anoshanda.

132-bitcoin-internet-protocol-values

Bitcoin iyo Internet yeuremu
Bitcoin inopfuura mari yedhijitari kana mari yemuno painternet. Iyo inzvimbo yeruzhinji internet. Iyo i inzira yekushandisa internet kuburikidza iyo hunhu hunotsinhaniswa pakati pemakomputa anoshanda nevanhu, asiwo nemichina inozvimiririra pachayo. Semuyenzaniso, mota hadzingofambi dzakazvimirira chete mune ramangwana, asi dzinozofambawo dzichienda kuchiteshi chekuchaja dziri dzega kuti dzichajise. Mune mamiriro ezvinhu aya, kubhadhara kunoitwa otomatiki kuburikidza neBitcoin pasina chero munhu anofanirwa kupindira nemaoko.
Mitemo inotonga kuchinjana kwemashoko kana maitiro. Mutauro iprotocol. Pandinotaura ndombozorora zvishoma, mumwe wangu anoziva kuti ava kugona kutaura. Shoko rimwe nerimwe muhurukuro rine zvarinoreva, kutaura kwose kunochinja matauriro ehurukuro. Mutauro wemutauro wevanhu unoronga kutaurirana pakati pevanhu vaviri kana kupfuura. Makombiyuta anotauriranawo. Semuyenzaniso, maprotocol avo iSMTP yekutumira email, FTP yekutumira mafaera, kana HTTPS yekushanyira mapeji ewebhu. Iyo yakasarudzika protocol inosarudza kuti data rinotsinhaniswa sei kune mumwe nemumwe kuitira kuti komputa imwe inzwisise imwe.
Mitmo ye internet
Iyo Bitcoin protocol inogona kuenzaniswa nechimiro cheinternet protocol stack.
[Bitcoin chinhu chakajairika](zviwanikwa/_Bitcoin-protocol.png) [^23]
Iyo Bitcoin blockchain ndiwo mutemo mutsva inofananidzwa neTCP/IP protocol, inova hwaro hweinternet. Pamusoro peBitcoin blockchain, iyo mitemo yeBitcoin inotamisa bitcoin maitiro akafanana neSMTP yekutumira maemail. Pamusoro peizvozvo, kune bitcoin sechishandiso chinofananidzwa neemail software seGmail kana Outlook. Iyi inonzi base layer yeBitcoin.
Netiweki yeLightinig
Pamusoro penheyo yenheyo yeprotocol, mamwe mazamu anogona kuvakwa, akadai seMheni Network, iyo yave ichishanda kubva muna 2018. Ndokusaka inonzi nhungamiro yepiri kana mutemo wenhungamiro. Iyo netiweki yelightining inogonesa diki asi inokurumidza kubhadhara uye panguva imwechete isingaverengeki huwandu hwekubhadhara pasekondi. Chimwe chinhu chisingagoneke nehunyanzvi paBitcoin base layer nekuda kweiyo yakavharirwa block size. Inounzawo kuvanzika kwakawanda paunenge uchishandisa bitcoin, sezvo iri kushanda kuburikidza neakavanzika nzira dzekubhadhara pakati pezviuru zvenode. Kubhadhara kwemheni kunobva kune imwe node kuenda kune imwe, zvichiita kuti zvisave nyore kuziva kuti ndiani anotumira mubhadharo. Zvikumbiro zvakaita sewallet, masevhisi ekukweretesa uye nezvimwe zviri kuvakwa pamusoro peMheni protocol, zvichiunza Bitcoin kuchengetedza zvivakwa nazvo.

133-How-are-Bitcoin-created

Bitcoin Yakagadzirwa Sei?
Isu taitaura nezve nzira nemitemo yemasvomhu inoronga kuti Bitcoin inoshanda sei. Seti yemitemo inotsanangura kuti bitcoin inogadzirwa uye inotenderedzwa sei. Iyi mitemo inogona kuchinjwa chete kuburikidza nekubvumirana kubva kune vose vanobatanidzwa munetiweki yeBitcoin. Vanhu, masangano kana hurumende havagone kushandura mitemo yeBitcoin.
Mune yedu yazvino sisitimu yemari dzefiat, kusikwa kwemari kuri mumaoko emabhanga epakati. Ivo vari kutungamira nekudzora kuburitswa kwemari yemabhangi nemari, pamwe chete nehuwandu hwechikwereti icho mabhanga ekutengeserana anogona kukweretesa, vachiona mubereko uye nokudaro vachipesvedzera kukosha kwechikamu chimwe nechimwe chemari.
Bitcoin inogadzirwa nenzira inodaidzwa kunzi migodhi nenzira yakasarudzika, kubva mumaoko evanhu vane hurongwa hwezvematongerwo enyika. Izwi rokuti "migodhi" rakasarudzwa nokuti, zvakafanana nekutorwa kwegoridhe, kushanda uye simba rekuisa rinodiwa pakusikwa kwe bitcoin.

134-What-happens-bitcoin-mining

Chii chinonzi Bitcoin Mining?
Iwe haufanire kunzwisisa kuti kuchengetedzwa Bitcoin kunoshanda sei uye kushandisa Bitcoin, asi kana iwe uchifarira ruzivo, zvinoitwa nevashandi vemumigodhi uye kuti bitcoin inowanikwa sei, verenga.
Kuchera muMazwi Ari Nyore
Fungidzira iwe unoda kuzadza museum nemifananidzo yakagadzirwa nejigsaw puzzles, apo yega yega puzzle inobatsira kune ruzivo rwemuenzi. Pane mitemo yakajeka: mapuzzle chete akaunganidzwa zvakanaka uye akakunda mukwikwi anogona kuiswa mekuchengetera zvekare. Iwe uchasarudza nekupa mubairo kumwana anopedza iyo yakanyanya kuoma pikicha yekutanga. Iwe haudi kuti mwana agone kubiridzira kune vamwe kana kuziva pachine nguva kuti ndeipi puzzle ichakunda. Iye zvino unotumira vana zviuru gumi pasi rose jigsaw puzzle yakafanana uye vanotanga kuibatanidza chidimbu nechidimbu panguva imwe chete. Mwana anopedza kubatanidza zvidimbu zvinotanga ahwina mubairo. Varatidza kuti vakaisa basa mukati uye dambanemazwi rakapedzwa ndiyo humbowo.
Iyo nzira yekuvaka iyo puzzle haigone kushatiswa, zvisizvo zvidimbu zvepuzzle hazvigone kuiswa uye mwana anohwina haagone kusarudzwa zvisirizvo. Mwana anokurumidza kuhwina mubairo. Iyi ndiyo mitemo. Iwe unogona chete kushandura mitemo kana vabereki, vana, mugadziri wepuzzle uye museum - vese vatori vechikamu munetiweki yepuzzle - vakafunga pamwe chete kuzviita. Pano, kana tichitaura nezvemubairo, tiri kutaura nenzira yedimikira nezve kusikwa kwe bitcoin.
Izvo zvakanyanya kana zvishoma izvo humbowo-hwe-basa huri pamusoro. Zviuru zvemakomputa pasi rese achigadzirisa zvirahwe zvemasvomhu panguva imwe chete, zvichiratidza kuti vanoisa huwandu hwekuedza mukati uye, panguva imwecheteyo, kuendesa mibairo mibairo kuitira kuti pasave nemunhu anogona kupindirana kana kufanotaura kuti ndeupi mugodhi achazotevera kuwedzera block. kucheni. Kuedza kwakaitwa nevacheri kuti kusimbise kutengeserana uye kuumba mabhuroko hakungoratidzi basa ravo chete asiwo kunochengetedza blockchain. Iwe haugone kushandura zvakapfuura - zvezvakaitika kare - muBitcoin blockchain pasina kushandisa mari yakawanda pazvivakwa uye magetsi kunyora zvakare blockchain. Ndosaka kurwiswa kweBitcoin network kuchigoneka mune dzidziso asi zvakanyanya, zvinodhura muchokwadi.
Kuchengeta Muudzamu
Fungidzira iwe uri kutoshandisa Bitcoin uye uine Bitcoin wallet yakaiswa pane smart foni yako. Iwe unoraira chigadzirwa painternet, uchisarudza bitcoin sekubhadhara. Iyo saiti inokuratidza kero yayo yeBitcoin uye iwe uchashandisa chikwama chako mbozha kutumira mari inodiwa. Zvino zvinotevera zvinoitika:
Chikwama chako chinosaina kutengeserana. Inobva yatepfenyurwa muBitcoin netiweki uye inopinda mudziva rekumwe kuchinjana mari kusina kusimbiswa, inonzi Mempool. Iye anobhadhara anogamuchira kutengeserana kwako uye node yavo yakazara inosimbisa kutengeserana. Ichiri kumirira, zvisinei, kuti isimbiswe kuti kutengeserana kwacho kwakanyatso kuwedzerwa kune block isati yaona yekupedzisira. Ndiyo nguva yaunoona kuti mari yako yatumirwa muchikwama chako asi yakamirira, zvichireva kuti haisati yagadziriswa pa blockchain. Iwe une zero zvisimbiso panguva ino.
Panguva imwecheteyo, vashandi vemigodhi vanogashira kutengeserana kwako muNode yavo yeMempool zvakare. A Bitcoin mugodhi mudziyo wakasarudzika unonzi ASIC. Basa rayo chete nderekumhanyisa hashing algorithm uye kugadzirisa iyo migodhi puzzle nekukurumidza sezvinobvira. Kune mazana ezviuru azvo, akaiswa pasi rose.
Vashandi vemigodhi vanewo yakazara node software inoshanda iyo inosimbisa kutengeserana kwako, kutarisa kuti mitemo yose yenzira yakateverwa uye kuti iwe, semubhadhari, une bitcoin yakakwana yekubhadhara kutengeserana. Kana mhinduro kune idzi cheki iri hongu, ivo vanowedzera kutengeserana kune yavo block template. Asi kutanga kwezvose, pavanogadzira template itsva ye block, mucheri anoisa iyo inonzi coinbase transaction iyo, kana vakakunda nhangemutange yemigodhi, vachavabhadhara 6,25 bitcoin semubairo. Mushure mekugadzira iyo coinbase transaction, makomputa anosarudza kutengeserana kubva kuMempool uye oawedzera mune yakambogadzirwa.
Panguva imwecheteyo, iyo hashing makomputa (ASICs) ari kutanga kugadzirisa iwo masvomhu akaoma. Vanokwikwidza nemamwe makomputa ese emigodhi pasi rese. Iyo hasher inogadzirisa puzzle inotanga kutepfenyura block kune avo vezera, vanoisimbisa uye voidzosera kune vezera ravo, uye zvichingodaro kusvikira node yega yega pane network yaona uye yakachengeta block. Mushure mekunge mamwe mabhuraki makumi mapfumbamwe nemapfumbamwe awedzerwa ku blockchain, mugodhi anokunda anobvumidzwa kushandisa iyo yakambogadzirwa rubatsiro ye6.25 bitcoin.
Iye mubhadhari, kutaura zvazviri, node yavo yakazara, anogamuchira bhuloku uye anoisimbisa zvakare uye pakupedzisira anosimbisa kutengeserana kwako. Kubhadhara kwako ikozvino kwakasungirirwa kune cheni mune bhuloku redata uye kunopedzwa. Iwe unogamuchira simbiso mune chikwama chako cheBitcoin kuti mubhadharo wasvika kune anogamuchira. Iwe unoona muchikwama chako kuti kutengeserana kwako kune 1 simbiso. Angangoita maminetsi gumi ega ega block nyowani inogadzirwa uye inowedzerwa mushure me block ine transaction yako. Mushure mezvivharo zvitanhatu kutengeserana kunoonekwa kunge kusinga gadziriswe.
Nguva iyo dhizaini yako inoda kugadziriswa zvinoenderana nemari yekutengeserana yauri kusarudza uye kubhadhara. Iyo yakakwira mubhadharo, ivo vanokurumidza vabati vemigodhi vanopinza kutengeserana kwako mubhuroko, nekuti vanowana mari idzi mukuwedzera kune block mubairo we6.25 bitcoin.
Nei iyi dambanemazwi remasvomhu? Humbowo-hwe-basa hwakasimba-hwekushandisa sezvo makomputa anoda huwandu hwakawanda hwesimba. Chokwadi ichi chinotungamira kushoropodzwa kweBitcoin muchiedza chekuchinja kwemamiriro ekunze uko isu vanhu takagadzira mumakumi emakore achangopfuura. Chitsauko "Bitcoin's Ecological Footprint" inobata nemubvunzo uyu zvakadzama.
Nei tichifanira kushandisa magetsi akawanda kudaro? Mhinduro ndeyekuchengetedza uye kuendesa matunhu. Iko kudikanwa kwekuisa simba uye simba mumigodhi inodzivirira iyo data mu blockchain kubva mukugadzirisa uye inoita kuti isachinjike uye isingaverengeki. Hapana nyika kana sangano rinogona kuchinja blockchain.
Kubva pakusikwa kwayo muna 2009, iyo Bitcoin blockchain haina kumbobvira yabiwa. Around 18.74 miriyoni bitcoin vagadzira kusvika pari zvino, parizvino vanodarika mazana matanhatu emabhiriyoni emadhora (Chikumi 2021). Nepo kubira kwakabudirira kweBitcoin network kunganetsa uye nekuparadza kuvimba kwakawanda, zvinoda inokwana 51% yesimba remigodhi yeBitcoin kuti ive pasi pemuridzi mumwechete kana conglomerate. Izvi zvinogona kubvumira bato rine hutsinye kuti rigadzire mabhuroko matsva nekukurumidza kupfuura mamwe 49% yevashandi vemumigodhi, zvichireva kuti vanogona kukanganisa kubvumirana. Asi kurwiswa kwakadaro hakugone kuba, kutungamira kana kushandisa bitcoin pasina kusaina. Vanorwisa vanogona kungoedza kushandisa kaviri-yavo bitcoin mumabhuroki achangopfuura uye kukonzera kukanganisa-kwe-sevhisi kukanganisa pakugadzirwa kwezvivharo zveramangwana.
Pamusoro pezvo, kana kurwiswa kweBitcoin kwakambobudirira, ipapo iyo Bitcoin blockchain yaizotsemuka sezvayakamboita kakawanda zvisati zvaitika. Vatori vechikamu muBitcoin blockchain vanogona kusarudza kuchinja kuti vatsigire cheni 'itsva' kana kuramba vachitsigira 'yekare' ketani shanduro. Iyi kupatsanurwa kweshanduro nekuda kwemitemo yekuzvarwa inozivikanwa seforogo yakaoma. Iyo 2017 Bitcoin / Bitcoin Cash hard fork yakaratidza kuti izvi zvaisazokanganisa kuve pamutemo kwe blockchain.
Chechipiri basa guru remigodhi ndere kuona kuendesa matunhu. Kune rimwe divi, kuita kugadzirwa kwemari kwakazvimiririra kubva kune epakati masangano uye masimba emunhu-anobata akadai sepakati mabhangi, uye kune rumwe rutivi kuve nechokwadi chekuti hapana mugodhi anogona kuwana mukana uye kushandisa iyo blockchain. Basa rekuverenga rakaoma uye panguva imwe chete, sekunge raffle, inyaya yerombo kuti komputa inowana mhinduro inoshanda kutanga. Nekuda kweizvozvo, hazvibviri kufanotaura kuti ndiani komputa inokunda ichave, izvo zvinoita kuti zvibvirire kupesvedzera blockchain. Kana iwe usingazivi kuti ndiani achave wekutanga, haugone kuzvibata uye kuwana mubairo.
Kana iwe uri kufunga nezve kutanga kushandisa bitcoin, iva nechokwadi chekuti blockchain inochengetedzwa nemigodhi uye yakagoverwa zvakafanana pazviuru zvemakomputa akasiyana. Yakachengeteka zvikuru. Basa rako rakakosha nderekuzvichengeta wega bitcoin yako uye chengetedza makiyi akavanzika (password yako) akachengeteka.

135-21-million

21 Mamiriyoni eBitcoin
Bitcoin inogadzirwa, sezvakatsanangurwa mumapeji apfuura, apo komputa yemugodhi inogadzirisa basa remakomputa uye ndiyo yekutanga kubudirira kubatanidza ichangoburwa bhuloku kune cheni.
Vashandi vepamigodhi parizvino vanowana mibairo ye6.25 bitcoin yebasa iri. Mubairo uyu ndiwo unokurudzira vashandi vemumigodhi kuzvibata zvakanaka kune network yeBitcoin uye kuvadzivirira kushamwaridzana nevamwe uye kurwisa netiweki.
Kuhafura
Mitemo yeBitcoin inotaura kuti mubairo wevacheri uchaderedzwa nepakati pese 210,000 mabhuroko, angangoita makore mana ega ega. Pakutanga mubairo uyu waiva 50 bitcoin. Kubva muna Chivabvu 2020 i6.25 bitcoin. Muna 2024 mubairo uyu uchaiswa nepakati kuita 3.125 bitcoin pabhuroka. Chiitiko ichi chinowanzonzi Halving.
Satoshi Nakamoto akaisa mahafu aya muBitcoin Core software. Huwandu hwekubuda hunodzikira nekufamba kwenguva, zvichiita kuti pave ne kevi yekuwanisa iri flat.
[Kodhi yepakati yepakati muBitcoin Core software muC++](zvishandiso/_halving-interval.jpg)
[Tsanangudzo naAndreas M. Antonopoulos](zviwanikwa/_aantonop-21-million.png) [^24]
Iyi algorithm inosvika zero zvekuti kuchave nepamusoro pe21 miriyoni bitcoin. Parizvino pane anosvika 18.7 miriyoni ari kutenderera. Muna 2140 ese 21 miriyoni bitcoin achange agadzirwa. Migodhi ichaenderera mberi uye vashandi vemigodhi vachapihwa mibairo chete yetransaction fees. Nenguva iyo, zvinotarisirwa kuti Bitcoin semumbure ichava nekugamuchirwa kwakakwirira zvokuti mari yekutengeserana chete inofambisa zvakakwana mubayiro kune vashandi vemigodhi.
[Total bitcoin inopihwa nekufamba kwenguva](zviwanikwa/_Total_bitcoins_over_time.png) [^25]
Sei mamiriyoni 21?
Sei Satoshi Nakamoto akasarudza mamirioni makumi maviri nerimwe evhavha yekugovera? Kune akawanda dzidziso, asi heino mhinduro yaSatoshi:
[Tsananguro yaSatoshi Nakamoto ye21 miriyoni yekupihwa chivharo](zviwanikwa/_Why-21-million.png) [^26]
MaUnitsi eBitcoin
Iyo diki yedhinomination unit ye ​​bitcoin is satoshi. 1 bitcoin inoumbwa ne100,000,000 satoshis; 1 satoshi izana remamiriyoni e1 bitcoin (0.00000001).
Iwe haufanirwe kutenga kana kutengesa 1 bitcoin panguva, unogona kutanga diki uye shandura chidimbu cheminuscule yayo.
Bitcoin kana bitcoin, asi Usambofa BitCoin
Bitcoin ine capital B inoshandiswa kana ichitaura nezveBitcoin network, iyo blockchain, nharaunda uye pfungwa yacho yese, nepo bitcoin ine diki b inoshandiswa kureva mari, iyo bitcoin tokeni.
Muchokwadi, koini ndiro izwi risiri iro rekutsanangura iyo dhijitari asset, iri kurasika zvishoma. Mukutaura kwehunyanzvi inonzi UTXO - unspent transaction output. UTXO inotsanangura huwandu hwekukosha hunochengetwa pa blockchain pane imwe kero yeBitcoin. Naizvozvo kune maonero akasiyana ekuti kune yakawandisa bitcoin, iyo uniti, nekuti imvura uye hapana yakatarwa yega mari. Asi sezvo Satoshi Nakamoto akataura nezve bitcoins, isu senharaunda tinozvitumidza nenzira iyoyo zvakare. Iko hakuna kuwanda kweBitcoin, sezvo paine chete blockchain uye network.
Scams seBitClub network yakaidaidza seBitCoin uye izvi zvinowanzo shandiswa zvisizvo neBitcoin vanotanga zvakare.
[^24]: [Source Andreas M. Antonopoulos](https://twitter.com/aantonop/status/1257366095515848716?s=20)   [^25]: [Source: Insti](https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Total_bitcoins_over_time.png)   [^26]: [Source plan99.net](https://plan99.net/~mike/satoshi-emails/thread1.html)

136-satoshi-nakamoto

Ndiani Satoshi Nakamoto?
Iyi inyaya inogona kusambogadziriswa nekuti hapana Satoshi Nakamoto. Zita izita remanyepo. Inogona kunge iri munhu kana boka rekriptographers, programmers uye masayendisiti. Musi waAugust 18 2008, munhu asingazivikanwe akanyoresa domain bitcoin.org. Nekunyoresa domain nerubatsiro rwekambani muPanama, kusazivikanwa kwemunhu wacho kunodzivirirwa kusvika nhasi.
Musi waOctober 1 2008, Satoshi Nakamoto akaonekwa pa "Cryptography Mailing List" uye akatsanangura mumharidzo kuti vakanga vachishanda pamagetsi emari yemari uye vakatumira chinongedzo cheBitcoin white paper pa [https://bitcoin.org/bitcoin. .pdf](https://bitcoin.org/bitcoin.pdf).
Hal Finney, American cryptography uye nyanzvi yekombuta, akange ave nenguva achibatanidzwa mune pfungwa yemari yedhijitari. Nekudaro, hapana kana imwe yemhinduro dzakapfuura yaive tekinoroji kana kuti pfungwa yakakura zvakakwana kuti ishandiswe zvakanyanya. Nhau dzakabva kuna Satoshi Nakamoto dzakanzwika kunakidza zvekuti Hal Finney akatanga kutaurirana naNakamoto. Musi waNdira 3, 2009, Nakamoto akachera yekutanga yeruzhinji Bitcoin block, iyo inonzi "Genesis Block". Kubva ipapo, muna Ndira 3, zuva rekuzvarwa kweBitcoin rakapembererwa.
Musi waNdira 8, 2009, Nakamoto akaburitsa vhezheni yekutanga yeButcoin software.
Hal Finney aive wekutanga mushure meNakamoto kuisa software pakombuta yake, akataura zvine mukurumbira tweeted "Running Bitcoin" muna Ndira 11, 2009 uye akagamuchira kutengeserana. Hal Finney akafa nechirwere chetsinga imwe nguva gare gare. Aiziva here kuti ndiani akanga akavanda kuseri kwezita remanyepo, Satoshi Nakamoto?
Kusvikira Kubvumbi 26 2011, Nakamoto akabatanidzwa muhurukuro pamusoro peBitcoin network - vakapindura mibvunzo kubva kune vamwe vanogadzira, vakatsanangura zvitsva zvepurogiramu, uye vakatsanangura zvimwe zvinangwa shure kwayo. Mharidzo yekupedzisira (zvichida) yakasiiwa naSatoshi Nakamoto yaiva muna March 2014 apo mushumo pamusoro pekufungidzirwa kwekuzivikanwa kweBitcoin "muumbi" wakaenda kuburikidza nevezvenhau. MuSan Francisco, magazini yeNewsweek yakaronda Dorian Satoshi Nakamoto, muAmerica wedzinza reJapan. Zvainzi ndiye aive uropi kumashure kweBitcoin. Ne "Ini handisi Dorian Nakamoto", anonzi Satoshi Nakamoto akazivisa kuti Dorian haasi "iye" Satoshi Nakamoto.

200-invest-bitcoin

Isa mari muBitcoin?
Kana iwe wakaverenga kusvika ikozvino, iwe wakatoisa nguva uye simba mukudzidza nezveBitcoin. Sei uchifanira kana usingafaniri kutanga kushandisa Bitcoin iwe pachako? Zvakanaka, ndinokurayira kuti usadaro kusvikira wava nechokwadi chokuti unoda kuzviedza. Ingoisa mari yakawanda muBitcoin sezvaunonzwisisa uye wakasununguka kuita - chete sekuwanda kwaunenge uchida kurasikirwa mune yakaipisisa-mamiriro ezvinhu.
Paunowedzera kuziva nekushandisa Bitcoin, ndipo paunowedzera kuvimba kwauchaita. Ndakatsvaga nyaya yacho kwemwedzi mitatu ndisati ndaisa chikwama changu chekutanga bitcoin uye ndakachinjanisa yangu yekutanga 75 euros ye bitcoin. Ini ndoda kukubatsira kuti ugadzire pfungwa dzako saka zvino tichazokurukura zvinowanzoitika nharo uye zvinopesana neBitcoin.

201-Arguments-against-Bitcoin

Nharo Dzinopesana neBitcoin
Kusagadzikana
Bitcoin haina simba, haugone kuishandisa senzira yekuchinjana nayo.
Ehe, mutengo we bitcoin hauna kugadzikana, unogona kurasikirwa kana kuwana kukosha kwakawanda muzuva rimwe chete. Kana iwe uchida kubhadhara chimwe chinhu mu bitcoin, unogona kuzviita. Ingochinjana mari imwechete yawakashandisa kubva kufiat kudzokera ku bitcoin pazuva rimwe chete. No volatility, hapana kurasikirwa kana kuwana.
Kuvandudza Mutengo
Bitcoin haisi chitoro chemutengo nekuda kwekuchinja kwemitengo.
Wona bitcoin sekudyara kwenguva refu, yanga iri chitoro chiri kuita zvakanaka cheukoshi hwemakirasi ese ezviwanikwa mumakore gumi apfuura.
[Bitcoin chiwanika chirinani pamakore gumi apfuura 2021](resources/_best-asset-10years.png) [^27]
Iko hakuna chokwadi chekuti kuita uku kucharamba kuchienderera nekusingaperi.
Panguva yekunyora bitcoin yaiva mune nzombe inomhanya, iyo yakatanga muchikamu chekupedzisira che 2020. Izvi zvinoreva kuti mutengo wakakosheswa kwekanguva kwemavhiki nemwedzi uine zvipingamupinyi zvishoma pakati. Muna Chivabvu 2021 kudonha kwakakosha kwakaitika, uko vazhinji vakadudzira sehutano hwekudzokera shure mumusika wakapisa. Nzombe yekupedzisira yakatanga muna 2017 uye yakapera pakutanga kwe 2018. Kubva ipapo mutengo wakafamba zvishoma kumativi - sezvazvinodanwa mumashoko evatengesi - zvinoreva kuti hapana kunyanya kukuru kana kuderera mumutengo.
[Kukura kwemutengo weBitcoin](zviwanikwa/_Bitcoin-price.png)[^28]
Kuvandudzwa kwemutengo weBitcoin kunotevera kutenderera kwehafu. Anenge makore ose e4 huwandu hweminted bitcoin inoderedzwa ne50%. Izvi zvinoreva kuti kukura kwe bitcoin inowanikwa pamusika iri kuderera. Kunyangwe kana kudiwa kwe bitcoin kungoramba kuri padanho rimwe chete, mutengo uchawedzera.
Kuwanikwa mumhepo
Iyo yakazara bitcoin inopa inogumira kune 21 miriyoni, 18,7 miriyoni iyo yatove pamusika. Makore mana ega ega (chaizvoizvo 210,000 blocks), huwandu hwe bitcoin iyo inogadzirwa inoderedzwa nehafu. Parizvino, nzira yekuchera migodhi inogadzira 6.25 bitcoin maminitsi gumi ose, iyo 900 bitcoin pazuva uye 328,500 pagore. Kubva 2024, pachange paine 450 bitcoin yakaitwa pazuva, sezvo chete 3.125 bitcoin ichapihwa kune yega block inogadzirwa. Izvi zvinoreva kuti mari inowanikwa zuva rega rega inodzikira uye kugovera kunowedzera kushomeka. Kana kufarira kunowedzera panguva imwe chete, mutengo unokwira zvakanyanya.
Kubva muna Chivabvu 2021, inosvika 36 miriyoni USD (nhamba yemazuva ese minted bitcoin * mutengo) inofanira kuyerera ichipinda mumusika weBitcoin zuva rega rega kuchengetedza mutengo uripo we40,000 USD wakagadzikana. Pese painodonha mutengo, mashoma bitcoin akatsinhaniswa pane aivepo pazuva iro uye zvinopesana.
Mazuva ezvikamu izvi akanyorwa pachati iri pazasi. Mutengo unotevera mapatani akafanana pamberi uye mushure mehafu yega yega. Mune chati iyi, pamusoro pe bitcoin inofungidzirwa kuva munaSeptember 2021, mushure mokunge mutengo unotarisirwa kuwira zvakare sezvaunogona kuona pa "Low" yakanyorwa mitsetse yegridi. Zvechokwadi, uku kunongova kufanotaura kwakavakirwa pazviitiko zvishomanana zvenhoroondo nenhamba. Hatigone kutora izvi sechiitiko chakapihwa mune ramangwana.
[Kuderedza mutengo kutenderera](zvishandiso/_Halving-Price-cycles-by-Pladizow.png) [^29]
Kubva pakatangwa Bitcoin muna 2009, pave nekuputsika kwemitengo kwakati. Iva wakagadzirira kuti izvi zvichaitika zvakare. Mubvunzo ndewokuti huchadzika sei nokuti pane logarithmic scale unogona kuona kuti, nekufamba kwenguva, bitcoin yakangowana kukosha kwenguva refu.
[Chikero chemutengo weBitcoin](zviwanikwa/_Bitcoin-price-log.png) [^30]
Usaedze kukurira musika, usatengese. Ingobata bitcoin yako. Anenge makore mashanu.
Panyaya yemusika webheya, kana mutengo we bitcoin uchidzika pasi, iwe ucharasikirwa nekukosha mune fiat mari mazwi. Nekudaro, yako stack ye bitcoin inoramba yakafanana. Kana iwe wakabata 0.3 bitcoin mumusika wenzombe, iwe unobata 0.3 bitcoin mumusika webheya futi. Kurasikirwa kwako kuri mumaonero ako chete, zvichienderana nekuti ndeipi mari kana asset yaunoenzanisa bitcoin yako pazuva rakapihwa. Iva nemoyo murefu, mirira, usatengese - nhoroondo inoratidza kuti kubata kwenguva refu inzira yechokwadi yekudzivirira kukosha kwako.
Ingoisa mari yakawanda mu bitcoin sezvaunenge uchida kurasikirwa. Kana iwe usingakwanise kurara munguva dzekuderera, saka unogona kubata yakawandisa yengozi asset se bitcoin.
Hapana Nzira
Ukatumira bitcoin kukero isiriyo, vanorasika. Haukwanise kuvadzosa.
Katatu-tarisa kero usati watumira bitcoin. Iwe haugone kudzosera mubhadharo. Semari yefiat, kana iwe ukatenga chimwe chinhu pachitoro chendaneti uye wodzosera chigadzirwa, ibasa rebhizinesi rechitoro kubata bitcoin uye kuidzosera kwauri. Zvakadaro, kungonyora zvisizvo kero kunofanira kukonzera kukanganisa kwete kurasikirwa nemari, sezvo kero dzinosanganisira kuongororwa kwekuvimbika.
Hapana Chengetedzo Mambure
Munzvimbo dzakasimukira dzepasirese, madhipoziti eakaundi yebhangi (muEurope anosvika 100,000 euros) anopihwa inishuwarenzi. Izvi hazvisizvo ne bitcoin._
Ichokwadi. Kana iwe uchizvichengetera bitcoin yako, saka iwe ndiwe wega une mhosva. Hakuna inishuwarenzi. Asi ziva kuti, kana paine dambudziko rezvemari, aya mainishuwarenzi efiat anogona kusakwanisa kukubhadhara zvakadaro. Munguva yematambudziko emari muCyprus muna 2013, 47.5% yemabhengi ese ari pamusoro pe100,000 euros akabatwa. Kana iwe uchizvichengeta - hapana anogona kutora bitcoin yako.
Kana tikavhura maziso edu tofunga nezvepasirese, uko 2 bhiriyoni vanhu vasina kubhengi uye 80% yevagari vepasi vanogara munzvimbo dzine masimba, nyaya yemari isingaverengeki senge bitcoin, uko iwe uri kutonga uye kwete bhangi, zvine musoro zvakare. Munyika idzodzo, umo vanhu vasina mambure ekuchengetedza zvachose, Bitcoin network inogona kupa kuchengeteka.
Handikwanise Kuisa Mari
Handikwanise kutenga bitcoin imwe chete, inodhura zvakanyanya.
Zvakanaka, haufanirwe kudaro. Iko hakuna bhajeti shoma yaunoda kushandisa bitcoin. Bitcoin inokamurwa kuita zvidiki zvakanyanya, zvidiki pane cent. Unogona kutenga chidimbu che bitcoin uye wotanga kutamba uchitenderedza ne20 USD kana zvishoma.
Iwe unogona zvakare kuwana bitcoin, asi zvimwe pamusoro peiyo muchitsauko 9 "Imba Bitcoin".
Bitcoin Ichakundikana Sekutanga Makambani eInternet
Bitcoin inyanzvi itsva. Ndiyo yekutanga yerudzi rwayo. Kana tichienzanisa izvi nemakambani ekutanga emakombuta muma1980 kana mapuratifomu epainternet eiyo dot com boom, anenge hapana akapona. Bitcoin yaive yekutanga blockchain pamusika, inogona kuenda nenzira imwecheteyo._
Bitcoin yanga iri iyo cryptocurrency inonyanya kushandiswa pasi rose kubva payakavamba muna 2009. Ndinobvuma, hapana vimbiso yekuti zvicharamba zvakadaro. Kutonga kwemusika kweBitcoin kwakapfuura 80% kusvika 2017. Zvichireva kuti, pazviuru zvese zvekriptofity pamusika, pamusoro pe80% yezvese mari yakaitwa muBitcoin. Izvi zvakashanduka muna 2017-18 paive ne "hondo" pakati pemafungiro akasiyana-siyana akapoteredza kuti Bitcoin sei teknolojia inofanira kuenda mberi. Iyo gakava rehukuru hweblock rakapera neforogo yakaoma, apo iyo Bitcoin blockchain yakakamurwa kuita maforogo maviri: Bitcoin (BTC) uye Bitcoin Cash (BCH). Panguva iyoyo, mamwe mapurojekiti e crypto akaita seEthereum akawana kukosha. Makore mana gare gare, BCH yakaramba ichiderera kuva isingakoshi kana ichienzaniswa neBTC. Bitcoin yakabata hutongi hwayo nepamusoro pe60% kusvika nzombe yazvino ichimhanya, kwayakadonha kusvika ku40% panguva yekunyora. Kumhanya kwehando kunoguma nekutariswa kwakanyanya, izvo zvinotungamira kune zvakawanda zvisina ruzivo zvinyorwa zvenhau uye, kana mamwe mabhirioni akawedzera makuhwa uye fungidziro kumusanganiswa, Altcoins inosimudzwa mukutarisisa.
[Muzana wemari yese yemusika](zviwanikwa/_Market-dominance.png) [^31]
Kutangazve kwekutonga kweBitcoin mushure menguva yakaoma yeforogo yakaoma muna 2017 chaive chiratidzo chesimba kune nyanzvi dzakawanda semacro-economist Lyn Alden uye US investor Michael Saylor, izvo zvakaita kuti vatende mune ramangwana reBitcoin semukundi. -inotora-yose cryptocurrency. Uye kunyangwe paine hunyanzvi hwetekinoroji muAltcoins hwaizovafambisa pamberi peBitcoin, hapana kupokana kuti vanogadzira Bitcoin vaizozvishandisawo.
Bitcoin Yakundikana
Kune vashoma vashandisi veBitcoin. Mushure memakore gumi nemaviri ekuvapo, vanhu vazhinji vanofanirwa kushandisa Bitcoin. Bitcoin yakundikana.
Sezvo kushandiswa kweBitcoin kuri, musimboti, kusasungirirwa kune zvitupa, hazvigoneke nenhamba kuti uzive kuti vangani vanhu vanoshandisa Bitcoin. Zvakare, nhamba yeBitcoin kero inotipa isu kusaziva kuti vangani vanoishandisa. Munhu mumwe chete anogona kuva nemamiriyoni emakero, kana munyaya ye bitcoin pane imwe nzvimbo yekutsinhana, zviuru zvevanhu zvinogona kutungamirirwa nekero imwe huru yekuchengetedza chete.
Idzo dzekutsinhana dzepakati dzinofanirwa kuona chitupa chako usati wabvumidzwa kushandura fiat kuita bitcoin. Nhamba inotevera inoratidza kuti vanhu vanopfuura mamiriyoni zana pasi rose vane akaundi pakutsinhana kwakadaro. Vanhu vakakwanisa kuwana bitcoin mumazuva ekutanga, kana kushanda kunze kwemiganhu yekutsinhana kwepakati vanoenda vasingazivikanwe.
[Nhamba yevashandisi-vakasimbiswa crypto asset mumamiriyoni](zviwanikwa/_nhamba-vashandisi-2020.png) [^32]
Around 1.3% yevanhu venyika vaiva neakaundi panguva cryptocurrency exchange pakupera 2020, kukura anenge 190% pakati 2018 uye 2020. Kunyange zvakadaro, mumwe anogona kutaura kuti izvi hazvisi zvakawanda. Zvisinei, nokuda kwekirasi itsva yeasset uye mari yakatanga sechikwata chepasi pasina kambani kana kutengesa shure kwayo, Bitcoin yakazvigadzira pachayo kusvika pakuzivikanwa zvikuru, kukurukurwa uye kushandiswa nevanhu vanopfuura mamiriyoni 100 pasi rose.
[Vapinduri vakataura kuti vaimbove ne crytptocurrencies](resources/_users_around-world.png) [^33]
Uyu ndiwo mugumisiro weongororo munyika dzakasarudzwa inoratidza kuti 32% yevanhu vekuNigeria vakashandisa kana kuti vane cryptocurrency. Ramba uchifunga, huwandu hwevanhu vekuNigeria vane avhareji yemakore gumi nemapfumbamwe, zvichienzaniswa neUS nhamba yemakumi matatu nemasere uye yepakati yeGerman yemakore makumi mana nemana. Vachiri vadiki, vanoda kushanda, vari tech-savvy uye vanokoshesa cryptocurrencies, zvisinei nekusagadzikana kwavo nekuti yavo yenyika mari Naira iri kurasikirwa ne25% yeukoshi hwayo pagore.
Unoda kuziva zvakawanda nezveBitcoin yekuNigeria, vhura browser yako uende ku: anita.link/88, anita.link/66 and anita.link/63
Matransactions anotarisirwa paBitcoin 
Iyo Bitcoin network inongokwanisa kugadzirisa matransaction manomwe pasekondi. Izvo hazvina kukwana kuchengetedza network yekubhadhara yepasi rose. Dai vanhu vese vaishandisa Bitcoin, network yaizoremerwa._
The Lightning Network yave iri mukuvandudzwa kubva pakutanga kwe 2018. Iyi iprotocol inowanikwa imwe nhanho pamusoro peBitcoin blockchain. Iyo Mheni Network inotarisirwa kubata zviuru zve micro-kubhadhara pasekondi mumakore mashoma uye yakatoratidza dhigirii rakanaka rekubudirira kwekukurumidza kuyambuka-kondinendi kubhadhara. IBitcoin blockchain ichashandiswa sechigadziko chekugadzirisa kutengeserana kukuru, nepo mari shoma yekofi, semuenzaniso, ichaitika paMheni Network. Semushandisi, haufanirwe kuziva kuti izvi zvinoshanda sei. Vazhinji vedu hatizive kuti Netflix kana kutumira email inoshanda sei uye zvakadaro tinozviita mazuva ese.
Pool yeku miner Bitcoin
Dziva remigodhi inzvimbo iyo "madziva" pamwe chete nezviwanikwa zvema komputa zvinopihwa neakabatana hasher (pool contributors) kuwedzera mukana wekuwana bhuroko idzva, izvo zvinoguma mune yakawanda bitcoin mubairo kubhadhara-kubuda.
Kunyange chiri chokwadi kuti madziva emigodhi anogona kuve akazara munzvimbo dzakati kana matunhu, senge kuChina hurumende yavo yehutongi isati yarambidza migodhi yeBitcoin muna Chikumi 2021, vachiri nepesvedzero shoma pane yaungatanga kufunga. Chekutanga, madziva emigodhi ane zviuru zvevacheri vemigodhi. Kungoti dziva remigodhi riri muChina hazvireve kuti mugodhi wega wega anofanira kunge ari muChina. Hashers vanoda kuve nechokwadi chekuti dziva ravanopa mariri riri kuita maitiro anoenderana neBitcoin philosophy. Muchiitiko chekusawirirana, vashandi vemigodhi vakasununguka kuchinja madziva. Muna 2013, dziva remigodhi reBitcoin GHash.io rakasvika kupfuura 50% yehuwandu hweBitcoin hashrate kwenguva pfupi, izvo zvakaita kuti ma hashers anongedze hashpower yavo kune mamwe madziva kuitira kuti vadzivise kuisa pfungwa kunokanganisa. Mutengo wakaderera wekuchinjisa madziva unoshanda sehurongwa hwemacheki uye zviyero pane kuzvitonga kwemaitiro evacheri. [^^33a]
![Global Overview yeBitcoin Mining Regions. Matunhu Ane Matunhu Makuru Akakodzera Anoratidzwa muTeal, Sichuan muBlue uye Akasara Matunhu Madiki muBlack](resources/_mining-locations.png) [^34]
Iyo 2017 yakaoma-forogo yakakamurwa pakati peBitcoin neBitcoin Cash muenzaniso wechipiri wekuti Bitcoin iri kuzvitonga sei. Vashandi vemigodhi nekutsinhana kukuru vaida kuwedzera saizi yebhuroka yega yega Bitcoin block kuti vawane yakakwira transaction kubuda pabhuroka. Nharaunda yevashandisi ve node uye vashandisi veBitcoin havana kuda kushandura saizi yebhuroka nekuti vanhu vane bandwidth yakaderera vangadai vasina kuwana mukana. Pane kudaro, vakasarudza 2nd layer mhinduro semheni Network kugadzirisa dambudziko iri. Izvi zvakakonzera "Blocksize war", apo vashandi vemigodhi nemakambani makuru vakaedza kumanikidzira shanduko pane network. Izvi zvakakonzera kuoma-forogo: Bitcoin yakakamukana kuita Bitcoin uye Bitcoin Cash. Makore mana gare gare, Bitcoin Cash inenge yakanganwa, nepo Bitcoin ndiyo yakakura cryptocurrency. Zvinoratidza kuti miners havana simba rakawanda kupfuura vamwe vashandisi.
[^27]: [Source Charlie Bilello](https://twitter.com/charliebilello/status/1370722188739891202/photo/1)   [^28]: [Source CoinGecko](https://www.coingecko.com/en/coins/bitcoin/usd), June 7, 2021   [^29]: [Source Pladizow](https://twitter.com/Pladizow/status/1358545292782497792/photo/1)   [^30]: [Source CoinGecko](https://www.coingecko.com/en/coins/bitcoin/usd), June 7, 2021   [^31]: [Source CoinMarketCap](https://coinmarketcap.com/charts/) June 7, 2021   [^32]: [Source Cambridge Center for Alternative Finance, 3rd Global Cryptoasset Benchmarking Study, Fig. 34, Illustration: Anita Posch](https://www.jbs.cam.ac.uk/faculty-research/centres/alternative-finance/publications/3rd-global-cryptoasset-benchmarking-study)   [^33]: [Source Statista](https://www.statista.com/chart/18345/crypto-currency-adoption/)   [^33a]: [2nd global cryptoasset benchmarking study](https://www.jbs.cam.ac.uk/faculty-research/centres/alternative-finance/publications/2nd-global-cryptoasset-benchmark-study](https://www.jbs.cam.ac.uk/faculty-research/centres/alternative-finance/publications/2nd-global-cryptoasset-benchmark-study/)   [^34]: [Source CoinShares, Bitcoin Mining, Dec. 2019](https://coinshares.com/de/research/bitcoin-mining-network-december-2019)

202-Bitcoin-ecological-footprint

Bitcoin nemamiriro ekunze
_Bitcoin inoshandisa magetsi akawanda zvinozowedzera dambudziko remamiriro ekunze uye kusaita basa nazvo._
![Chinyorwa cheNewsweek kubva 2017](resources/_Newsweek-2020-energy.png) [^35]
Iyo skrini iri pamusoro inyaya kubva kuNewsweek pakati chaipo peiyo 2017-2018 bull run. Inobva pabasa raAlex de Vries (Digiconomist), aimbova muongorori wedata weDutch Central Bank. Mapepa mazhinji ekutsvagisa uye zvinyorwa zvemidhiya zvakabva pafungidziro dzake dzenhema sekuenzanisa mashandisirwo emagetsi eBitcoin kune VISA kubhadhara uye kuverenga kabhoni kubva pane izvi. Ini ndinopikisa kuti basa rakawanda iri rinoitwa kuparadzira zvirevo zvenhema kuitira dhimoni Bitcoin.
Nguva dzose patinenge tichiita rally muBitcoin tinoona zvose izvi zvisina kunaka kutarisa kune zvakatipoteredza zvinokonzerwa neBitcoin. Sezviri pachena zvinongokosha chete kana mutengo wakakwirira. - **Andreas M. Antonopoulos**
Ngatinyure mune izvi. Vatsoropodzi veBitcoin vanowanzotaura kuti Bitcoin inoshandisa simba rakawanda kupfuura mabhenefiti ayo anogadzira. Hazvirambike kuti kuchera kweBitcoin kunoda magetsi akawanda. Zvinofungidzirwa kuti pakati pe80 ne118 TWh pagore inoshandiswa pasi rose kumigodhi iyo yakaenzana nekushandiswa kwesimba rose kwenyika dzakaita seNetherlands.
![Chinzvimbo chenyika, Kurume 2021](resources/_electricity-consumption-btc.png) [^36]
Nyika inoparadza magetsi akawanda. Huwandu hwemagetsi anopedzwa gore rega rega neanogara-aripo asi asingashande emidziyo yemumba muUSA chete anogona kugonesa Bitcoin netiweki kwemakore 1.9. Izvi zvinoreva kuti huwandu hwesimba hwakaraswa muUSA hunogona kuita simba reBitcoin network kaviri, gore negore. [^37]
Panguva imwecheteyo, zvikamu zviviri muzvitatu zvemasimba ese anogadzirwa muUSA anorasika. Zvine musoro kufunga kuti izvi zviri kuitika mune mamwe mativi ose enyika zvakare.
![Estimated US Energy Consumption in 2017 - Rejected Energy](resources/_Energy_US_2020.png) [^38]
Ziva kuti akarambwa emagetsi maakaundi anosvika 62% yemagetsi ese ekugadzirwa. Simba rakarambwa isimba rinogadzirwa asi pakupedzisira hariende kubasa rinobatsira. Kuita kuti zvinhu zvitonyanya kuipa, nekufamba kwenguva, nhamba iyi yave ichiwedzera pane imwe nguva. Muna 1970 Lawrence Livermore National Laboratory akawana chikamu chedu chesimba rakarambwa chaive 48%. [^39]
Kuzvitaura neimwe nzira, Bitcoin inotora 0.54% yemagetsi ese anoshandiswa pasi rose. ![Magetsi epasi rose ekugadzirwa, kushandiswa uye mugove weBitcoin, Kurume 2021](zviwanikwa/_electricity-world-btc.png) [^40]
**Magetsi Ekushandisa Zviri Nyore Kuona kuti ashanda akawanda sei ** Kujeka kweBitcoin kunobvumira fungidziro yesimba rayo rekuda zvakanyanya mukupesana nemamwe maindasitiri mazhinji, uko aya mapoinzi edata akanyanya kujeka. Tichiyerwa nemitengo yemagetsi chete, tinogona kufunga kuti Bitcoin [yakanyanya kushanda zvakanaka](https://medium.com/@danhedl/pow-is-efficient-aa3d442754d3) kupfuura kubhenga kwechinyakare uye kuchera goridhe pasi rose.
Mutengo wemadhora ekumigodhi weBitcoin paGigajoule unoshanda zvakapetwa ka40 pane zvechinyakare kubhengi uye ka10 inoshanda zvakanyanya pane yekucherwa kwegoridhe.
![Kuenzanisa kushandiswa kwesimba mumari nemabhanga masisitimu](resources/_energy-efficiency-ARK.png) [^41]
** Sei Bitcoin Ichida Huwandu Uhu hweMagetsi ** Iyo yehumbowo-ye-basa yekuchera migodhi chinhu chakakosha chinochengetedza kusununguka, kusarerekera uye otomatiki kuvimbika kwetiweki. Ndiyo nzira yakachengeteka yekudzivirira kurwiswa kwezvinhu zvakakosha pamusoro pe600 bhiriyoni USD zvakavharirwa munetiweki. (BTC musika cap, Chikumi 2021)
Bitcoin inogona kugadzirisa kutengeserana pasina vamiriri nekuti nyanzvi, yakatsaurirwa hardware inoratidza pachena kuti komputa yakaita computation inodhura.
Humbowo-hwe-basa inosimbisa mari yedhijitari munyika chaiyo. Sezvo mugari weChaincode Labs, Hugo Nguyen anotsanangura, "Pasi pehodhi, uchapupu-hwe-kushanda migodhi inoshandura kinetic simba (magetsi) mubhokisi rebhuroki. Nokubatanidza simba kubhuroko, munhu anopa 'fomu', achibvumira kuti ive nehuremu chaihwo. nemigumisiro munyika yenyama." [^42]
Humbowo-hwe-basa ndiyo chete nzira inobvumira kugovaniswa zvakaenzana, kugadzirwa kwakasarudzika kwekupihwa kwemari, nepo dzimwe nzira dzinoda madonhwe ekutanga echiratidzo uye zviitiko zvechizvarwa zvinobvumira vatambi vepakati kutora mukana wemari isati yacherwa (Uchapupu-hwe-- stake).
**Kufungidzira #1: Zvinotora X Kilowatts Kuita Imwe Chete Transaction ** Iyi isvomhu dzakatadza. Kushandiswa kwesimba kwe bitcoin hakurevi kune nhamba yekutengeserana. Huwandu hwekutengeserana kunoitika pa-cheni uye nhamba yekutengeserana kunoitika kunze-cheni - semuenzaniso, patekinoroji yechipiri senge Mheni Network kana kuburikidza nekutsinhana kwekuchengetedza, iyo batch transaction - haina kuwirirana zvachose nemutengo we kuchera. 80-90% yemigodhi inotungamirirwa nemutengo we bitcoin, uye imwe 10-20% inotungamirirwa nemari. Kuwanda kwepurofiti inogoneka kuvacheri, ndipo panowedzera mukana wekuti vashandi vemumigodhi vatange nzvimbo itsva dzekuchera migodhi uye, kana mutengo waparara, vamwe vachafanira kumisa michina yavo. Mukufamba kwenguva, apo mamiriyoni e21 bitcoin akacherwa, mari yekutengeserana chete ichatyaira migodhi. Panguva iyoyo, kusimba kwekutengeserana kuchave kwakabatana nekushandiswa kwesimba. Asi kwete nhasi, satoshi yekupedzisira ichacherwa mu 2140. Migodhi inotungamirirwa nemakwikwi mumusika wakasununguka apo kuoma kwemigodhi kunogadzirisa dynamically. Hazvinei nekuti mangani matransaction arikugadziriswa. Kuchera inzira yekuchengetedza. Inoenderana nekuchengetedzeka kwakadini kwemusika kugovera kuhurongwa, saka simba rakawanda rinoenzana nekuchengetedza uye kana mutengo we bitcoin uchikwira huwandu hwemari yakagoverwa kudzivirira iyo inowedzerawo zvakasikwa. Naizvozvo kushandiswa uye kutorwa kwepamusoro kunosimudzira kukurudzira kwemari kune vashandi vemumigodhi kuti vagadzire kuchengetedzwa kwakawanda nekushandisa simba rakawanda. 
"**Kufungidzira 2: Linear Extrapolation ** Chechipiri fungidziro isiriyo ndeye extrapolate linearly uye kutaura kuti, kana zvichitora X kilowatts yesimba kuita imwe kutengeserana nhasi uye isu tine manomwe nehafu bhiriyoni vanhu vari panyika vanozoda kuita rimwe kutengeserana pazuva rimwe nerimwe, ipapo bitcoin simba. kushandiswa mune ramangwana kuchava Y. Iyi inhema. Bitcoin haigone kuyera mutsetse maererano nekutengeserana nekuda kweiyo block size zvipingaidzo pane base layer. Kudzikamisa izvo, yechipiri-layer protocol seMheni Network kana sidechains seLiquid inogadzirwa, iyo inobvumira zviuru zvekubhadhara pasina kudiwa kwekuwedzera simba. Kubudirira kwezvigadzirwa zvemigodhi kuri kuwedzera. Vashandi vemigodhi vanoda simba shoma rehuwandu hwakafanana hwekushanda kwekombuta nekufamba kwenguva. Pamusoro pezvo, vagadziri veBitcoin vari kuvandudza kodhi, vachidzikisa saizi yedhata yekutengeserana kuitira kuti mamwe matransaction anogona kucherwa mubhuroka rimwe.
** Kufungidzira 3: Kufananidza VISA neBitcoin ** A Bitcoin on-chain transaction haigone kufananidzwa nekubhadhara VISA. Hazvina kufanana. Mumabhengi echinyakare kune akasiyana akaturikidzana ekugadzirisa, zvichireva kuti anosiyana padanho ravo rekuchengetedza uye kupedzisa. Ngatitorei muenzaniso weUS system, inofananidzwa pasi rose. Iyo base layer iFedwire, CHIPS uye SWIFT network, nepo kiredhiti kadhi uye kubhadhara kadhi rechikwereti kunoshanda nhanho imwe kana maviri pamusoro nevarevereri vazhinji. Iyo base layer yeBitcoin inofanirwa kuenzaniswa neFedwire, CHIPS uye SWIFT. Chechipiri-layer mhinduro sekukurumidza, micropayments paMheni Network inogona kuenzaniswa neVISA.
![Kuenzanisa kwenhema pakati pekutengesa bitcoin neVISA](zviwanikwa/_VISA-BTC-comparison.png) [^43]
Ngatitarisei avhareji yekutengeserana vhoriyamu yeVISA neBitcoin.
![Avhareji kukosha kwekutengeserana kwekadhi rechikwereti pasi rose muna 2012, USD](zviwanikwa/_average-VISA-transaction.png) [^44]
![Average value yeimwe Bitcoin transaction](zviwanikwa/_average-transaction-value-bitcoin.png) [^45]
Avhareji bitcoin kutengeserana ukoshi aiva 258,766 USD musi Kubvumbi 21st, 2021, nepo avhareji VISA kutengeserana akanga 91 USD muna 2012. Bitcoin kutengeserana kutakura magnitudes kukosha zvikuru mukuenzanisa kubhadhara kadhi rechikwereti. Tichifunga kuti Bitcoin inowana kutorwa kwevanhu vakawanda saka rimwe zuva inogona kugadzirisa mamiriyoni emadhora anokosha seFedwire system pamari yakaderera zvikuru kana ichienzaniswa nebhangi system.
Avhareji yekutengeserana kukosha pakufambisa kweFedwire yaive 4.5 miriyoni USD muna Kukadzi 2021. [^46]
![Kugadziriswa kwebhanga maringe neBitcoin](zviwanikwa/_settlement-compared.png) [^^47]
Kutengeserana kweBitcoin kunogadziriswa maminetsi ega ega e10, maawa makumi maviri nemana pazuva, mazuva 365 pagore. Enzanisa izvi kune ACH kutengeserana izvo zvinogona kutora kusvika makore maviri kuti pakupedzisira agadziriswe. [^48] Tisingakanganwe: Kuitwa kweBitcoin neMheni hakuna mvumo uye hakuna kuvimbika ukuwo hurongwa hwekubhadhara hwechinyakare hunoshanda chete nekuti vapomeri vanochengeta hutsotsi uye kubhadharisa.
**Kufungidzira 4: Kuenzanisa Kushandiswa Kwesimba Nekusvibiswa** Vanhu vanoti, semuenzaniso, kuti " kutengeserana kwega kwega kunosvibisa" kana " kusvibiswa kwebitcoin kuri kuwedzera" kana " bitcoin inobudisa kusvibiswa semugumisiro wekushandisa kwayo simba - izvo hazvisi zvechokwadi. Iko hakuna kuwirirana kwakananga pakati pekushandiswa kwesimba uye kusvibiswa nekuti zvinoenderana zvachose nerudzi rwesimba riri kushandiswa. Kana iwe uri kugadzira simba nemarasha, izvo zvinokonzeresa kusvibiswa uye kukanganisa kwezvakatipoteredza. Kana iwe uri kugadzira simba nemadhamu ehydroelectric kana mhepo kana solar semuenzaniso, saka hausi kunyatso kusvibisa. Muchokwadi, uri kupa rubatsiro kune iwo magetsi emagetsi uye kukurudzira kugadzirwa kwezuva, mhepo, geothermal, off-gassing uye mamwe marudzi esimba kuburikidza nekushandiswa kwe bitcoin sechinhu chehupfumi mukugadzirwa kwesimba iroro. "
Bitcoin miners inofambiswa nepurofiti, saka ivo vachagara vachitsvaga iyo yakachipa simba, iyo inodzokororwa. Marasha neoiri zvichagara zvichidhura kupfuura hydroelectric, geothermal, stranded gasi, mhepo uye simba rezuva. Tisingakanganwe nyukireya, iri zvakare sarudzo iyo vazhinji vanoverenga segirini simba.
Pasina kupokana, Bitcoin miners vari kushandisa neimwe nzira kutambisa simba. Ndakataura na[Sébastien Gouspillou](https://anita.link/103) na[Philippe Bekhazi](https://anita.link/101) vashandi vaviri vemumigodhi vachishandisa hydropower, vakatsigira zvataurwa pamusoro apa.
**Energy Mix yeMagetsi Kugadzira ** Bitcoin miners yakagovaniswa zvakanaka pasi rose. Kunyange zviri nyore kuyera kudiwa kwemagetsi, zvinonyanya kuoma kuyera magetsi masosi sezvo indasitiri yemigodhi yeBitcoin inoramba iri yakavanzika uye isingazivikanwe indasitiri. Naizvozvo, tsvakiridzo pamagetsi anoshandiswa mumigodhi fungidziro yesimba rinogoneka kushandiswa inosiyana kubva pa39% (Cambridge Center, CBECI.org) kusvika 73% muCoinShares Mining Whitepaper, inopedzisa:
Tichishandisa musanganiswa wekufungidzira kwenzvimbo dzepasi rose dzemigodhi uye renewables renewables penetrations tinoverenga zvakare indasitiri yemigodhi yeBitcoin kuti ive inofambiswa zvakanyanya. Yedu yemazuva ano inofungidzirwa muzana yemagetsi ekugadzira muBitcoin yekumigodhi simba musanganiswa inomira pa73%, zvakapoteredza kana. Pakati pese, zvatakawana zvinosimbisa maonero edu ekuti kucherwa kweBitcoin kuri kuita semutengi wemagetsi wepasi rose wekupedzisira uye nekudaro kunenge kwave kuungana pamwe nekuenzaniswa nezvisingashandiswezve zvivakwa zvekuvandudza. sezvo indasitiri inokura uye ichigadzikana sechigarire mumeso eruzhinji - inogona kuita semutyairi wezvitsva zvinogoneka kuitika munzvimbo dzaimbove dzisina hupfumi.  [^49]
Mubvunzo hausi kuti simba rakawanda sei rinodiwa, asi magetsi anogadzirwa sei? Yakawanda sei CO2 inoburitswa? Kana tikasarudza senzanga kuti hatidi simba rinosvibisa, saka tinofanira kudzora kugadzirwa kwesimba uye kusabvumira kushandiswa kwemaitiro ekusvibisa. Izvi ndezvekugadzirisa kugadzirwa kwesimba uye kwete zvekugadzirisa kushandiswa kwesimba mune imwe chikamu chehupfumi chinoitika kuBitcoin.
Bitcoin inoshandisa yakakwira huwandu hwemagetsi kubva kune renewable pane grid muChina USA uye pasirese. ![Electricity Mix, Bitcoin vs. China vs. USA vs. The World, 2020](zviwanikwa/_Bitcoin-electricity-sources.jpg) [^50]
**Kabhoni Emissions ** Imwe tsvagiridzo yakaedza kuongorora kuyerera kwekabhoni uye kusimba kweBitcoin kuburikidza nekufungidzira kudiwa kweramangwana, zvichibva pafungidziro dzenhema. Rimwe bepa semuenzaniso ririkuti: "simba rekushandisa pagore reBitcoin blockchain muChina rinotarisirwa kukwira muna 2024 pa296.59 Twh uye kuburitsa 130.50 miriyoni metric matani ecarbon emission zvakafanana. [^ 51]"
Iyo mureza mutsvuku wekare kuti vanyori vazivise nechivimbo ramangwana reBitcoin kabhoni kunzvimbo mbiri dzegumi, apo chokwadi nhamba yacho inogona kungofungidzirwa mukati mekuraira kwehukuru., anodaro ** Nic Carter **. [^52]
Kubva pa[basa raHass McCook](https://bitcoinmagazine.com/business/bitcoin-vs-financial-sector-energy-use) Bitcoin inoburitsa isingasviki 2% yemauto-industrial complex uye isingasviki 5% yelegacy financial sector's carbon emissions. Kuburitswa kwepagore kwepasi rose kwegreenhouse gasi kwakada kusvika. 50,000 mamiriyoni ematoni carbon dioxide yakaenzana. Bitcoin inoburitsa chete 0.11% yeavo.
![Yegore Greenhouse Gas Emissions, Hass McCook, June 2021](zviwanikwa/_annual-GHG-emissions2021.png.png) [^53]
** Kufungidzira Kwekupedzisira: Bitcoin Haisi Kubatsira, Saka Chero Kushandisa Simba kweBitcoin Kunopambadza **
Kana ukafunga kuti Bitcoin haina basa, saka iyi ipfungwa yekuzvibata. Bitcoin inogona kunge isina musoro kwauri, asi inogona kuita zvine musoro kune vamwe vanhu vazhinji. Kana uri kuita nharo iyi, unofanira kubvuma kuti kune dzimwe nzira dzakawanda dzemashandisirwo esimba ayo ari prima facie asingabatsiri kana kutokuvadza mukushandisa kwawo, uye haagamuchire huwandu hwakafanana hwekuongororwa.
Tinogona kubatidza mabhiriyoni emwenje weKisimusi gore rega rega kuti tiratidze mweya weKisimusi, izvo zvingave zvisina maturo kumabhiriyoni ezvimwe zvitendero. Nhamba yekutanga kushandiswa kwesimba muUnited States, semuenzaniso, kunze kwemisika yevagari vemo iDhipatimendi reDziviriro. Hurumende yeUS inoshandisa masimba akawandisa uye ndiyo inonyanya kusvibisa munyika, pasina chikonzero chechokwadi kunze kwekutsvaga kutonga kwakanyanya.
![Mauto eUS anoburitsa CO2 yakawanda kupfuura nyika zhinji](zviwanikwa/_mauto-co2.png) [^54]
Izvi zvinodzokera kuchitsauko pamusoro pePetrodollar, kubatana pakati peUS dollar neOPEC, izvo zvinoita kuti USA ive ine simba guru pasi rose uye inochengetedzwa nemauto eUS nehondo mudunhu reGulf.
Muchina wehondo chinhu chinobatsira kuve nacho munharaunda yedu here? Usati wadanidzira "Whataboutism!", Taura kuti iri kuenzanisa zvinhu zviviri zvakasiyana uye zvinoda kuti tideredze kushandiswa kwehondo muchina pamwe chete nekushandiswa kwe bitcoin, usakanganwa kuti pane yakakosha link isipo. Muchina wehondo kutenderera pasirese unopihwa mari yakananga nechikwereti chefiat chinogadzirwa nekubhadharwa kuburikidza nekukwira kwemitengo kunogoneswa kuburikidza nemari isingadzoreki yebhangi repakati rekudhinda, iyo pakupedzisira iwe, muteresi, uri kumberi kwebhiri. Bitcoin haingori mhinduro yehupfumi hwakavhurika, imhinduro inomanikidza hurumende kugadzira mari nemitengo isingaite uye kushandisa inflation senzira yakavanzika yemutero kubhadhara muchina wehondo, unozopedzisira wasvibisa nekukuvadza kupfuura chero chinhu chiripo. . Bitcoin haisi kungotsiva chiitiko chehupfumi, zvakare kutonga kwakananga pamushini wehondo unosvibisa uye unoshandisa simba rakawanda kungouraya vanhu. Saka mukuona kwangu zvinhu zviviri izvozvo zvakasungwa zvakanyanya. Asi ndizvo chete Andreas M. Antonopoulos 'uye maonero angu pachangu.
** Mhedziso: Mabhenefiti eBitcoin **
Ndakataura nemumwe munhu akaponeswa kubva kunzara muVenezuela pakati pa2016 kusvika 2019 nekuda kweBitcoin. Bitcoin inoponesa hupenyu! Chii chinogona kubatsira kupfuura izvozvo?
Bitcoin haidzoreki, haiori, uye inobvumira mabhiriyoni evanhu kuti avhure kuwana mari yepasi rose, pasinei neruvara, murume kana mukadzi, upfumi, uye chimiro. Uyezve, ndiwo mukana wedu wega wekuchengetedza kuvanzika kwemari, kana kuti pseudonymity, munyika yekuongorora kwedhijitari.
Iyo Bitcoin network inochengetedza midziyo yevashandisi vangangosvika miriyoni zana pasi rose, inokosha inodarika mabhiriyoni mazana matanhatu emadhora (Chikumi 2021) pasina muganho wepamusoro uye haivimbe nesimba remauto kana hondo dzemari.
Heino mhedziso, sezvakataurwa neARK Invest: "Kupesana nekufunga kwekubvumirana, tinotenda kuti kukanganisa kwezvakatipoteredza kwe bitcoin mining is de minimis. Renewables, kunyanya magetsi emagetsi, anokonzera chikamu chikuru chekusanganiswa kwesimba re bitcoin. Sezvo Castle Island Ventures partner. , Nic Carter, akacherechedza, mukutsvaga kwavo mhando yemagetsi yakachipa, vashandi vemumigodhi vacharamba vachidirana kumatunhu anopa huwandu hwemagetsi anogona kudzokororwa, vachivhura midziyo yemagetsi yakavharika se 'mutengi wemagetsi ekupedzisira, vachigadzira iyo inonyanya kufambiswa. kune chero magetsi anokwanisa kubudisa pamitengo iri pasi pevagadziri vemazuva ano, pasinei nenzvimbo.' Nekuda kweizvozvo, kubva pakuona kwemamiriro ekunze, bitcoin mining inogona kuve yakanaka. " [^55]
[^35]: [Source Newsweek, 12/11/2017](https://www.newsweek.com/bitcoin-mining-track-consume-worlds-energy-2020-744036)   [^36]: [Source Cambridge Center for Alternative Finance, March 2021](https://cbeci.org/cbeci/comparisons/)   [^37]: [Cambridge Center for Alternative Finance](https://cbeci.org/cbeci/comparisons/)   [^38]: [Source Energy Flow Chart, Lawrence Livermore National Laboratory](https://flowcharts.llnl.gov/)   [^39]: [Conner Brown, Bitcoin: a bold american future](https://journal.bitcoinreserve.com/bitcoin-a-bold-american-future/)   [^40]: [Cambridge Center for Alternative Finance, March 2021](https://cbeci.org/cbeci/comparisons/)   [^41]: [Source, ARK Invest, Bitcoin myths](https://ark-invest.com/articles/analyst-research/bitcoin-myths/)   [^42]: [ARK Invest Bitcoin myths](https://ark-invest.com/articles/analyst-research/bitcoin-myths/)   [^43]: [Source Statista](https://www.statista.com/statistics/881541/bitcoin-energy-consumption-transaction-comparison-visa/)   [^44]: [Source Statista](https://www.statista.com/statistics/279308/average-credit-card-transaction-value-worldwide/)   [^45]: [Source BitInfoCharts](https://bitinfocharts.com/comparison/bitcoin-transactionvalue.html#1y)   [^46]: [Source The Federal Reserve Services](https://frbservices.org/resources/financial-services/wires/volume-value-stats/monthly-stats.html)   [^47]: Anita Posch   [^48]: [Caitlin Long](https://twitter.com/CaitlinLong\_/status/1384925713648734212?s=20)   [^49]:[CoinShares, Bitcoin Mining Whitepaper 2019](https://coinshares.com/research/bitcoin-mining-network-december-2019)   [^50]: [Source: Hass McCook](https://bitcoinmagazine.com/business/what-elon-musk-gets-wrong-about-bitcoin)   [^51]: [Nature communications](https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-021-22256-3)   [^52]: [Nic Carter, On Bitcoin, the Gray Lady Embraces Climate Lysenkoism](https://medium.com/@nic__carter/on-bitcoin-the-gray-lady-embraces-climate-lysenkoism-a2d31e465ec0)   [^53]: [Source Annual Greenhouse Gas Emissions, Hass McCook, June 2021](https://bitcoinmagazine.com/culture/bitcoin-vs-world-military-emissions)   [^54]: [Source Statista](https://www.statista.com/chart/18359/estimated-military-carbon-dioxide-emissions/)   [^55]: [ARK Invest Bitcoin myths](https://ark-invest.com/articles/analyst-research/bitcoin-myths/)

203-Arguments-for-Bitcoin

Nharo dzeBitcoin
Bitcoin isisitimu ine sarudzo. Iwe unosarudza kuishandisa. Iwe unosarudza kuti ndeapi mapurogiramu aunenge uchimhanya. Iwe unosarudza wauchazopindirana naye. Iwe unosarudza mitemo yemutambo wauri kuenda nawo. Kudyidzana. Ndosaka bitcoin ichizohwina. Inoburitsa hutsva hunodiwa nevatengi uye vanoda. - **Andreas M. Antonopoulos**
Shanduko
Ndiri chizvarwa chedhijitari mumuviri weGen X. Ndinogona kurangarira hupenyu husina internet, kunyangwe ndisina VCR. Takanga tine imwe nhepfenyuro yeTV muAustria, ndizvozvo. Vabereki vangu vakawana foni yedu yekutanga pandaiva nemakore gumi nemaviri. Pamakore gumi nemana ndakashandisa kombiyuta yangu yekutanga, muna 1997 ndakaisa internet yangu yekutanga uye email kumba. Gore iroro kwaingova nemiriyoni imwe chete yemawebhusaiti pasi rose uye Google neAmazon dzainge dzisipo pasi rese.
Vanhu vazhinji vakaramba internet senzira inoenda. Muna 1995, nyanzvi yenyeredzi uye munyori weUnited States Clifford Stoll akanyora chinyorwa cheNewsweek chakanzi "Internet? Bah!"
Kozoita kuita mabhizinesi pamhepo. Isu takavimbiswa kutenga ipapo ipapo kubva mukatalogu - kungonongedzera, kubaya nekutoita madhiri makuru. Isu tichahodha matikiti endege nepanetiweki, toita reservation rerestaurant uye totaurirana zvibvumirano zvekutengesa. Zvitoro zvichange zvisisashandi. Saka sei shopu yangu yemuno anoita bhizinesi rakawanda masikati kupfuura iyo Internet yese inobata mumwedzi? Kunyangwe dai pakanga paine nzira yakavimbika yekutumira mari paInternet - iyo isipo - netiweki inoshaya chinhu chakakosha che kapitalism: vatengesi. **Clifford Stoll** [^56]
Nekukurumidza kumberi ku2019 uye Amazon iri mumakambani makuru gumi epamusoro pasi rose, Google neYouTube ndidzo injini huru dzekutsvaga uye kune 1.8 bhiriyoni anoshanda mawebhusaiti. Kuonana kwangu kwekutanga neBitcoin uye blockchains kwaive muna Kubvumbi 2017 pandakanzwa hurukuro naShermin Voshmgir. Yakabva yangodzvanya ipapo. Makore makumi maviri mushure mekunge ndachinja basa rangu kubva pakuva murongi wemaguta kusvika pakuva mutengesi weinternet, ndakanzwisisa kuti Bitcoin yakakura sekutanga kweinternet muna 1997.
Kuwanikwa kweBitcoin kwaive kuuya kwehunyanzvi hutsva pamusoro peinternet hwatinoshandisa panhau nekutaurirana. Indaneti yemari, iyo inotibvumira kuchinjanisa kukosha pasi rose pasina miganhu. Kukurukurirana pamusoro peInternet kwakachinja nyika zvakanyanya mumakumi mashoma emakore apfuura. Iwe unofunga kuti kukanganisa kwekusununguka kwekufamba kwekukosha kuchave nei? Bitcoin uye zvimwe zvakavhurika, zveruzhinji midziyo yedhijitari inoshandura masimba emagetsi pakati penyika sezvo zvichingoerekana zvaita kufambisa mari yakawanda nekumhanya, pasina kupokana kana kubata iyo sisitimu iripo yemari.
Bitcoin I tekinoloji itsva. Tikaitarisa tichienzanisa kukura kwayo ne internet, tinoona tiri pakanga paine internet mugore ra 1977.
Kugonesa Shanduko Yemagariro
Vanhu vari munyika dzakasimukira vane hutongi hwejekerere vanowanzoramba Bitcoin sechombo chekufungidzira uye njodzi kune nyika-nyika. Naizvozvo, vamwe vanofunga kuti kushandiswa kwayo kwemagetsi hakuna basa nemhoteredzo. Vamwe vanototsigira kurambidzwa. Tarisira rudzi urwu rwekushoropodza kuwedzera mumakore anotevera.
Huwandu hwevanhu pasi rose i7.8 bhiriyoni. Chete 8,4% yeavo vanogara munyika dzegutsaruzhinji, 41% munyika dzegutsaruzhinji dzisina kukwana, 15% muhurumende dzakasanganiswa uye 35,6% muhurumende dzehudzvanyiriri.
Vanopfuura 50% yehuwandu hwepasirese vari kugara munyika dziri kure nemademocracy akasununguka uye akanaka! 1.7 bhiriyoni vanhu havana akaundi yebhangi uye havazombofi. Bitcoin ndeyavo. [^57]
Vanhu vari mumatunhu akaita seAfrica neSouth America vanozofambisa kutorwa kweBitcoin kumberi. Zvikuru zvekushandisa-kesi zviripo:
**Ruzhowa pakukwira kwemitengo** Tafura iyi neInternational Monetary Fund inoratidza shanduko yegore negore yemitengo yevatengi muzvikamu. ![Kukwira kwemitengo, avhareji yemitengo yevatengi, shanduko yegore negore mu%](zviwanikwa/_inflation-2021.png) [^58]
Venezuela yakaona mitengo ichikwira ne5,500%. Kutambura kwevanhu hakunzwisisike.
MuSudan mitengo yakawedzera 200% muna 2021 chete.
Zvizvarwa zveZimbabwe zvatarisana nekupeta kwemitengo yezvinhu nechikamu che100% kubva muna 2020 kusvika 2021.
IMF yanga isina data yeArgentina, asi ndakaziviswa nemumwe wangu wekuArgentina wekubvunzurudza, Franco Amati,  pagore zvakakwira ne 50%.
Nigeria yakaona kukwira kwemutengo ne16% muna 2020.
Turkey mugore ra2020  yakakwirirwa kusvika pa 13.6 %.
Kubva muna Chivabvu 2020 kusvika Kubvumbi 2021 huwandu hwekutengesa bitcoin muNigeria hwakawedzera ne40% kubva pamadhora mazana maviri nemakumi masere nenomwe kusvika pamadhora mazana matatu nemakumi mapfumbamwe nepfumbamwe. Ongororo ya2020 inoratidza kuti 32% yevaNigerian vakabvunzurudzwa vakashandisa kana kuve ne cryptocurrencies. Zvichakadaro, munyika dzakabudirira dzakaita seGermany neUSA, 5-6% chete vakashandisa kana vane cryptocurrencies.
![Huwandu hwekutengesa paP2P Bitcoin kuchinjana munyika dzeSub-Saharan kubva muna Chivabvu 2020 kusvika Kubvumbi 2021](zviwanikwa/_Nigeria-trading-volume-BTC.png) [^59]
Tichifunga izvi gore negore inflation rates, vanhu vanoziva kuti vanofanira kuchengetedza hupfumi hwavo mumari yakaoma seUSD, uye zviri nani zvakadaro, Bitcoin. Kana iwe ukatsanangura mutsauko weBitcoin kumari dzemuno munyika idzi, munhu wese anonzwisisa nekukurumidza kuti sei uye nei Bitcoin inogona kuvatsigira.
**Kune Kumwe Kuchinjana Kudzora **
Nyika dzine hupfumi husina kusimba uye dzine hutongi hwejekerere dzinoshandisa kudzora mari yekunze kudzikamisa - yavanodaidza - fungidziro pamusoro pemari yadzo isina simba. Sezvo vatungamiriri vehudzvanyiriri vachida kudzikamisa nekudzora mikana yevanhu yekunzvenga hurongwa hwavo hwekudzvanyirira, vanoshandisa mitemo yakaita seinotevera:
Kutonga kukuru kweArgentina kunongobvumira vanhu kuchinjanisa mari inodarika mazana maviri emadhora pamwedzi kubva kuArgentina Peso kuenda kuUSD.
Mitemo ine hukasha yakafanana inoshanda muZimbabwe. Kana iwe uchimhanyisa bhizinesi uye uchida kuunza zvinhu kunze kwenyika, unofanira kukumbira mvumo kuReserve Bank yekutumira USD kunze kwenyika. “Ngatitii ndiri mumagetsi ezuva ndinoda kutenga 20 panels kuti nditengese.Ndasarirwa nemazuva makumi matatu chete kuti ndipedze mari yandanga ndiinayo.Reserve Bank inogona kutora nguva yainoda kupa. Ndipe mvumo yekutomboenda kunotengazve. Ndicho chimwe chikonzero nei madhora ekuAmerica chaiwo, mari yacho ichikosha zvakanyanya muZimbabwe," mumwe mubvunzurudzo weZimbabwe akandiudza muna Kurume 2020.
**Sisitimu yemabhanga Haipo kana kuti yakatyoka **
Mabhizinesi emuZimbabwe anotenderwa kushandisa USD kubhadharisa mutengesi wemuno. Mutengesi uyu anofanira kubvisa madhora ekuAmerica mukati memazuva makumi matatu, kana kuti mari yacho yoshandurwa kuita RTGS akaundi nemutengo webhanga. RTGS izita redhora remuZimbabwe iro rinoratidza kukwira kwemitengo uku.
Kana iwe ukatenga mari yekunze kubhangi reArgentina mari yebhangi yepamutemo inoshandiswa (inofarirwa nebhangi, asi kwete mutengi) uye pamusoro pazvo mutero we65% unobviswa.
Kushandisa hurongwa hwebhangi kunogona kuzara nematepi matsvuku munyika dzekuMadokero zvakare, asi zvakanyanya kuipa munyika idzodzo.
**Kutumira mari **
Kana iwe ukagamuchira mari kubva kunze kwenyika kuburikidza neyakajairwa sisitimu yemabhanga inoshandurwa kuita yeArgentina pesos pamutengo webhangi wepamutemo. Izvi zvinomiririra kutorwa kwe30% yeukoshi.
Muna 2020 mari inosvika bhiriyoni imwe chete yemadhora yakatumirwa semari inotumirwa kuZimbabwe. Vanopfuura chikamu chimwe muzvitatu chevanhu vanovimba nemari inobva kuhama dziri kunze kwenyika. Zvizvarwa zveZimbabwe zvakawanda zvinogara muSouth Africa uye pamari yavanotumira, inosvika 20-30% inorasika kuburikidza nemari dzekubhanga uye nemitengo yekuchinja zviri pamutemo. [^60]
**Zvipingamupinyi kune Vakadzi** Kushandisa akaundi yebhangi hakukwanisi kusvikwa nevakadzi vanenge bhiriyoni pasi rose. Zviyero zvakasiyana-siyana zvekusaenzana kwevakadzi zvinotenderwa kana kurairwa nemutemo zvinorambidza vakadzi kutora chikamu mune zvemari zvizere munyika dzakawanda pasi rose. Zvichienderana nenyika, vakadzi vanosarurwa mumitemo yenhaka uye vanofanirwa kuwana mvumo yemurume wavo yekushanda zviri pamutemo, kuwana akaundi yekubhanga, kunyoresa bhizinesi kana kusaina chibvumirano; vakadzi vazhinji vanorambidzwa kupinda mamwe mabasa. Vanhukadzi vanogonawo kuomerwa nekuwana zvitupa zvemutemo nekuda kwemitemo iripo kana kuti zvinotemesa kunyoresa zvinodiwa, uye chitupa chakadaro chinowanzodiwa pakushandisa zvigadzirwa nemari.
Zvimwe zvimhingamupinyi zvinotadzisa madzimai kuwana rubatsiro rwemari kudiwa kwekufamba nzendo refu, njodzi yekubirwa vachiwana mari, uye kushaikwa kwekuvanzika kunoita kuti vachengetedze mari dzavo kubva kune vamwe.
“Zvinopfuura zvikamu makumi masere kubva muzana zvemabhizimisi madiki anoitwa muPacific nevakadzi ari mumisika midiki,” akadaro Dr. Sharman Stone, Ambassador weAustralia weMadzimai. "Pavaive nemari chete zvaive nengozi kuti vatore mari iyi kumba, uye nekuchengeta iyo mari kana vasvika kumba." [^61] NeBitcoin nemacryptocurrencies, akachengeteka panyama, anogona kunzvenga kukwira kwezvinhu uye kubata mari yavo.
Vakadzi ndivo vazhinji vevagari vemuKenya; vanoita 70% yebasa rekurima, asi ivo vane pasi pe1% yevhu uye vanodzora zvishoma kwazvo yemari inogadzirwa nevashandi vavo. [^62]
56% yevakuru vese vasina kubhengi pasi rose vakadzi. Vakadzi vanomiririrwa zvakanyanya pakati pevasina kubhengi muhupfumi hwakawanda. Izvi ndezvechokwadi kunyangwe mune hupfumi hwakabudirira kuwedzera muridzi weakaundi uye vane chikamu chidiki chevakuru vasina kubhengi. [^63] MuUnited States, Middle East neNorth Africa zvikamu zviviri muzvitatu zvevasina kubhengi vakadzi.[^64]
Ongororo yakaitwa muKenya yakaratidza kuti kuwanikwa kwesevhisi dzemari dzenharembozha kunopa mabhenefiti makuru, kunyanya kuvakadzi. Zvakaita kuti mhuri dzinotungamirirwa nemadzimai dziwedzere mari dzavanochengeta nezvikamu zvinopfuura chikamu chimwe muzvishanu, zvakabvumira madzimai 185 000 kusiya kurima nekusimudzira mabasa emabhizimisi kana ezvitoro uye zvakabatsira kuderedza urombo hwakanyanya pakati pemhuri dzinotungamirirwa nemadzimai nezvikamu makumi maviri nezviviri kubva muzana.
Masevhisi emari dzenharembozha akaita seM-Pesa kuKenya kana EcoCash muZimbabwe awedzera kuwaniswa kwekushandisa mari. Dambudziko: aya masevhisi nemakambani epakati, akazvimirira. Hurumende inogona kupindira, kutengeserana kunogona kuongororwa kana maakaundi anogona kuvharwa. Semuenzaniso, muna Chikunguru 2020 hurumende yeZimbabwe yakamisa mari kubva kumaakaundi eEcoCash emobile yemari kuenda kumabhanga kana mari.
Masevhisi emari anogonawo kubatsira vanhu kuti vaunganidze mari dzavanochengeta uye vawedzere mari yekushandisa pazvinhu zvinodiwa. Mushure mekupihwa maakaundi ekuchengetedza, vatengesi vemusika muKenya, kunyanya vakadzi, vakachengeta pamwero wepamusoro uye vakaisa makumi matanhatu muzana ekuwedzera mumabhizinesi avo. Mhuri dzinotungamirirwa nevakadzi muNepal dzakashandisa 15 muzana yakawanda pazvokudya zvinovaka muviri (nyama nehove) uye 20 muzana yakawanda padzidzo pashure pokunge yawana maakaundi okuchengetera mahara. Uyezve, varimi vokuMalawi vakaiswa mari dzavo mumaakaundi okuchengetera mari vakashandisa 13 muzana yakawanda pamidziyo yokurima uye vakawedzera zvirimwa zvavo ne15 muzana. [^65]
Bitcoin inogona kuderedza mutengo wekugamuchira mubhadharo, ichisiya vanhu vane mari yavo yakawanda. Nepo zvechinyakare zviridzwa zvemari zvinoda ID uye humbowo kero, kushandisa Bitcoin yakavhurika munhu wese. Nokudaro, Bitcoin inogona kutsigira vakadzi mukuwana rusununguko rwakawanda uye kuzvitonga.
Kuti uwane rumwe ruzivo nezve mararamiro evanhu muZimbabwe uye mashandisiro avanoita Bitcoin muVenezuela, Argentina, Afghanistan, Nigeria nezvimwe, [teerera kubvunzurudzo dzangu dzepodcast](https://anita.link/show). Nezve zvakanakira vakadzi vanoshandisa Bitcoin, tarisa kumusoro kwechikamu "Vakadzi muBitcoin".
Inononoka, Asi Yakachengeteka
Imwe kutsoropodza kweBitcoin ndeyekuti kukura kwayo kunononoka uye kwakaoma. Muchokwadi, chokwadi chinoratidza kuti Bitcoin ndiyo yakareba yakamira uye nehunyanzvi yakachengeteka blockchain. Haina kumbobvira yabiwa kana kuchinjwa. Chikonzero cheichi inharaunda yevakazvimiririra, vakavhurika-sosi vanogadzira vane kufarira kwekutanga kupa kune yakafara nzanga yakanaka. Teerera kuna [Adam Back](https://anita.link/12), [Gloria Zhao](https://anita.link/82), [Tim Akinbo](https://anita.link/63), [Amiti Uttawar](https://anita.link/62) kana [Matt Corrallo](https://anita.link/19) kuti vanzwisise kufunga uye nemafambisirwo avanoita basa ravo. Chechipiri, kumhanya kwebudiriro kunononoka nemaune. Iyo Silicon Valley mantra ye "Fambisa nekukurumidza uye pwanya zvinhu" inopesana nezvaunoda kune 600 bhiriyoni USD digital asset iri panguva imwe chete, mhenyu software.
Internet yezvinhu
Mari yepainternet senge bitcoin inogona kushandiswa nemichina zvakare. Mota dzemagetsi dzinozvityaira senge auto-matekisi dzinokwanisa kuzvichaja pazviteshi zvekuchaja uye kubhadhara otomatiki ne bitcoin. Iyi haisi ngano yesainzi, iyi inguva yemberi iri pedyo. Andy Schroder anobva kuKentucky [kurodha Tesla yake nemuchina-kune-muchina micropayments pamusoro peBitcoin Mheni Network](http://andyschroder.com/DistributedCharge/) nechekare. Izvi hazvizove izvo chete zvitsva zvinouya kubva kumharadzano yehunyanzvi hutsva, mari nekutaurirana.
Bitcoin, iyo Life-Boat
Sezvandakaronga muchitsauko 1, haisi nyaya yekuti hurongwa hwemari huripo huchadonha here, asi riini. Kunyangwe denda reCCIDID-19 risati rapararira pasi rose muchirimo 2020, nyika dzaive muchikwereti chakadzama; migumisiro inoparadza yakanga iri pachena mukukahadzika kwehupfumi hwepasi rose uye hwedunhu. Kwemakore akawanda nyanzvi dzakanyevera veruzhinji nezvazvo. Simon Dixon akanga atoshevedzera Kuderera Kukuru kwe2020s kare muna 2011. Nomi Prins akatsanangura kubatana kwebhangi repakati mubhuku rake re2018 rezita rimwe chete. Satoshi Nakamoto akataura nezve njodzi yehurongwa hwemari hwakavakirwa pachikwereti uye dambudziko remari mumapepa machena.
Bitcoin imari isina chikwereti. Munhu haangokwidziri zvinhu zvacho. Ndiyo yakanakira imwe nzira yekubuda muiyo fiat system. Kuitira kudzivirira dambudziko iri ririkuuya, zvine musoro kugovera mari pakati pezvinhu zvakasiyana uye nokudaro kuderedza systemic njodzi. Ndarama, equities, bond, real estate, mawachi uye mota dzekare zvinozivikanwa kukosha kwekuchengetedza zvinhu. Bitcoin idhijitari kukosha kuchengetedza asset.
Apo maCEO emakambani aitengeswa pachena akaita saElon Musk naMichael Saylor vakatanga kuchinjana USD nebitcoin, vakachengetedza nzvimbo yavo paBitcoin life-boat. Bitcoin yakagadzirirwa vanhu. Kune vanhu vakaita sewe neni. Iye zvino ndiwo mukana wako wekubuda muchikepe chinonyura chefiat currencies. Hazvina kunonoka, uchiri mangwanani.
Bitcoin Inowanikwa Zvakanaka
Iyo Bitcoin netiweki inzvimbo yeruzhinji; indaneti yakasarudzika yekutaurirana ichiri kuvakwa pamberi pemeso edu. Isu sevanhu takatadza kutora chikamu mune zvemari, zvakananga kubva pakuvaka kunze kweinternet. Vazhinji vedu takanga tisina migove yeApple, Google kana Facebook. Zvipingamupinyi zvakawanda hazvibatanidzi mabhiriyoni evanhu kubva pakudyara mukutanga-ups. Bitcoin yakavhurika kuti munhu wese aise mari muzvivakwa zvayo. Unogonawo kushandisa dzimba kufungidzira Bitcoin kuva digitaalinen pfuma; kune dzimba 21 miriyoni chete uye unogona kutenga chikamu cheimba, kusvika pamubato wegonhi.
Bitcoin Inokurudzira Kuchengetedza
Bitcoin yakanakira kuchengetedza kwenguva refu. Kana iwe uchitenda kuti kukosha kuchakwira mune ramangwana, unokurudzirwa kubata uye kusashandisa bitcoin yako pazvinhu zvisinganyanyi kukosha.
Unogona Kutenga Bitcoin
Haufanire kutenga bitcoin yese. Bitcoin inopatsanurwa kune zana remamiriyoni emayuniti. Iyo diki yuniti inonzi "Satoshi" - mushure memuvambi asinganzwisisike, Satoshi Nakamoto. Iwe unogona kutenga zvikamu zve bitcoin uye kutanga nediki se20 euros, semuenzaniso.
Bitcoin uye Mabasa eMari
Nyanzvi dzezvehupfumi dzakawanda dziri kusimbirira pakuti Bitcoin haisi mari nekuti haizadzise matanho matatu ekushanda ayo mari inofanira kuva nawo. Aya mabasa akatsanangurwa naWilliam Stanley Jevons[^66] muna 1875, ongororo yake ichive yakakurumbira mumabhuku ehupfumi hwemacroeconomic kubvira ipapo.
Sekureva kwaJevons, Bitcoin imari chete kana ichizadzisa mabasa aya:
Chitoro chemutengo - kukosha kunofanirwa kuramba kwakagadzikana nekufamba kwenguva
Pakati pekutsinhana - inogamuchirwa zvakanyanya mukutsinhana kwezvinhu uye masevhisi
Medium account - inoshandiswa seyero yemitengo, mari uye purofiti Kunobva: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Money
** 1. Chitoro cheKukosha ** Vatsoropodzi vanoti bitcoin haisi chitoro chekukosha nekuda kwekusagadzikana kwayo uye mukana wekurasikirwa kwenguva pfupi. Zvakanaka, sezvandakaronga muchitsauko 3.1, munguva refu izvo hazvisizvo chaizvo. Uyezve, ini ndinobvunza tsananguro ye " yakagadzikana nekufamba kwenguva. Ndeipi nguva yakatarwa? Inflation mumari yefiat muAustria yanga iri 20% mumakore gumi apfuura. Dzimwe mari dzese dzefiat dzakaita seEuro zvakafanana zvitoro zvisingavimbike zveukoshi nechikonzero ichi. "
** 2. Nzira yekuchinjana** Unogona kushandisa bitcoin senzira yekutsinhana kana uchida. Hongu, kune nhamba shoma yemakambani, masevhisi uye maresitorendi anobvuma bitcoin semubhadharo panguva yekunyora. Asi, kuti uite izvi, unogona kushandisa akasiyana maturusi nemasevhisi aunogona kuzadza ne bitcoin uye kushandisa mufiat. Pamusoro peizvozvo, kune makambani mazhinji mukati menzvimbo anotobvuma uye anobhadhara mubhadharo mu bitcoin futi. 
**3. Nzira yema akaundi** Fiat mari inodiwa kuti ive nzira yeakaunti nemutemo. Hatina zvokusarudza. Bitcoin inobva pakushandiswa kwekuzvidira, inosarudza-kupinda; kana tikafungidzira kuti kukosha kuri kukwira, isu hatizvishandise. Sezvo kusagadzikana kwe bitcoin kuchiderera nekufamba kwenguva, kukosha kwezuva rimwe kunorova nzvimbo uye vanhu vanozotanga kushandisa bitcoin. Kunyangwe izvi zvisati zvaitika, mabhizinesi mazhinji anozotanga kugamuchira bitcoin, sezvo vachivimba kuti haisi kurasikirwa nekukosha asi kuti inoonga. 
Imwe nzira nyowani yemari isingamanikidzwe patiri, asi isarudzo-mukati, inofanirwa kupinda mune mamwe matanho nenzira iyoyo: kutanga, inofanirwa kuve chitoro chekukosha, ipapo kuvimba kunofanira kuvakwa, ipapo vanhu vanozoita shandisa senzira yekutsinhana nayo. Ipapo chete ichashandiswa senzira yeakaunti.
Kudzinga Bitcoin nekuti haisati yazadzisa mabasa ese emari iko kupotsa poindi.
Kuenzanisa Maitiro Emari
Muna 2014 Ryan Walker akatora pfungwa dzedzidziso yaDarwin yekusarudzwa kwezvisikwa kuti aenzanise kushanduka kwemhando dzakasiyana dzemari. Tafura iri pazasi inoratidza dhigirii iro goridhe, fiat uye bitcoin zvinozadzisa hunhu hunozivikanwa hwemari (mutsara 1 - 8). Hurumende yakapihwa inoyera dhigirii repakati uye kutonga nezviremera (mutsara 9).
Kuuya kwekriptographic-based currencies kwakagonesa hunhu hutsva hwakakosha kare husingagoneke nemhando dzechinyakare dzemari. Uyezve, kuzadzikiswa kwehunhu hwakadaro kungangove nekukanganisa kukuru kune zvakatipoteredza umo mari idzi dzinokwikwidza. Row 10 ne11 inosanganisira iyo mhando ye cryptocurrency payakayerwa inopesana netsika uye ichangobva kuitika maitiro emari.  **Ryan Walker**
![Maitiro emari](zvishandiso/_tafura-maitiro-mari.PNG)[^67] Izvi zvinoratidza dhigirii iro goridhe, fiat, uye cryptographic currencies inozadzisa hunhu hunozivikanwa hwemari pamwe nehunhu hutsva hwakaitwa nekuwanikwa kweBitcoin. 
Sezvauri kuona, Bitcoin inopfuura kupfuura tsika yechinyakare yekuti mari chii. Irikusanduka kuita chidimbu chitsva chose chezvingaitwa nemari uye kubva pazvichazovakira maapplication mune ramangwana.
[^56]: [Clifford Stoll](https://www.newsweek.com/clifford-stoll-why-web-wont-be-nirvana-185306)   [^57]: [Wikipedia, Democracy Index](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Democracy_Index)   [^58]: [International Monetary Fund, Inflation rate](https://www.imf.org/external/datamapper/PCPIPCH@WEO/OEMDC/ADVEC/WEOWORLD), requested on April 26th, 2021   [^59]: [Trading volume on P2P Bitcoin exchanges in Sub-Saharan countries from May 2020 to April 2021](https://www.usefultulips.org/combined_Sub%20Saharan%20Africa_Page.html), requested on April 26th, 2021   [^60]: [World Bank, Sending money from South Africa to Zimbabwe](https://remittanceprices.worldbank.org/en/corridor/South-Africa/Zimbabwe), requested on April 26th, 2021   [^61]: [BNY Mellon Supports Global Push for Financial Gender Equality](https://www.bnymellon.com/us/en/about-us/newsroom/company-news/bny_mellon_supports_a_global_push_for_financial_gender_equality.html)   [^62]:[Georgetown Journal of International Law](https://www.law.georgetown.edu/international-law-journal/wp-content/uploads/sites/21/2018/08/4-Kenya-Report-508.pdf)   [^63]: [World Bank, Global ID Coverage, Barriers, and Use by the Numbers : An In-Depth Look at the 2017 ID4D-Findex Survey](https://globalfindex.worldbank.org/sites/globalfindex/files/chapters/2017%20Findex%20full%20report_chapter2.pdf)   [^64]: [World Bank, The Little Data Book on Financial Inclusion 2018](https://openknowledge.worldbank.org/bitstream/handle/10986/29654/LDB-FinInclusion2018.pdf)   [^65]: [World Bank, The Global Findex Database Measuring Financial Inclusion and the Fintech Revolution 2017](https://www.notion.so/Financial-Inclusion-feb3e3913cb042b9bc0ef525ad0f8272#f24c9e8d868e49fe9052c61ead55e080)   [^66]: [William Stanley Jevons](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_Stanley_Jevons)   [^67]: [Ryan Walker](https://www.coindesk.com/origins-money-darwin-evolution-cryptocurrency)

204-Strategic-notes

Manotsi esitirateji
Mashoko eYambiro
Usati watanga kutenga Bitcoin, ndapota verenga zvinyorwa izvi zvakakosha:
Iri gwaro rinovhara yekutanga Bitcoin blockchain, yakagadzirwa naSatoshi Nakamoto muna 2009, inoshanda pasi peiyo acronym BTC kana XBT pakuchinjana. Kuti uwane ruzivo nezve Bitcoin (BTC), ona [https://bitcoin.org](https://bitcoin.org/). PaBitcoin.com kune rumwe rutivi, unosvika pawebhusaiti yeBitcoin Cash (BCH), iyo yakakamurwa kubva ku2017.
Ziva kuti kune akawanda ma spin-offs eiyo yekutanga Bitcoin. Vane mazita akaita seBitcoin Cash (BCH), Bitcoin SV (BSV), Bitcoin Gold (BTG), Bitcoin Diamond (BCD) kana Bitcoin 2 (BTC2). Aya haasi "akachipa" bitcoin, asi akazvimirira, akasiyana pfuma. Vanoshandisa zita rimwechete seBitcoin kuti vabatsirwe kubva mukuzivikanwa kwayo, asi havachengetedze simba rakafanana kana mukurumbira seBitcoin chaiyo (BTC).
Bitcoin chinhu chakajairika, isina kodzero dzechiratidzo. Kana iwe waizotanga kambani nhasi woidaidza kuti "Apple Premium", waizogashira mhosva yekutyorwa kwechiratidzo kubva kuApple nekukurumidza. Izvi hazvishande kuBitcoin nekuti yakavhurika sosi, inosimudzira hunyanzvi uye kubatanidzwa. Munyaya yekutumidza spin-off chimwe chinhu chakadai seBitcoin Cash, inovhiringidza uye inofanira kudziviswa.
Kushandiswa kweBitcoin kuri pamutemo munyika zhinji dzepasi, asi kurambidzwa kwenyika kunogona kutanga kushanda chero nguva, zvichidzivirira kushandiswa kweBitcoin nevanhu. Chero zvazvingava, kurambidzwa kunogona kukonzera kurasikirwa kwekukosha uye kushandura bitcoin yako zvakare mufiat currencies kunogona kuoma. Sezvo musimboti weBitcoin nharaunda vari vashandisi vakazvipira zvakanyanya, kunyangwe nyika yako ikarambidza bitcoin, iwe uchagara uchiwana mumwe munhu achafara achitsinhana bitcoin yako yefiat.
Mutengo we bitcoin unotarwa nekupa uye kudiwa. Zvinogoneka chero nguva - uye zvakare zvakaitika kakawanda - kuti mutengo unodonha zvakanyanya munguva pfupi uye haugone kubvisa kana kuchinjanisa bitcoin yako nekukurumidza sezvaunoda.
Shandisa mari yakawanda chete sezvaunogona kurasikirwa pasina kupinda mumatambudziko emari. Iwe ndiwe une basa rekuchengetedza kuchengetedzwa kwemari yako. Muchiitiko chekurasikirwa kana kuba, hapana sarudzo yekudzorera.
Mukuwedzera kune bitcoin, kune zvinopfuura 4,000 zvimwe crypto assets kusvika nhasi, iyo yose ine zvinangwa zvakasiyana uye kushandiswa. Dzidza zvakawanda nezvezvinangwa, timu uye tekinoroji iri shure kwayo usati wadyara mari, kana zvachose.
Kubuda kwezvimwe zvinhu izvi zvinogona kukanganisa mutengo we bitcoin. Imwe mari inogona kuve inotungamira mari yedhijitari, kunyangwe parizvino yakawanda yekugamuchirwa uye kukura iri mukati meBitcoin (BTC).
Usatorerwe nekukwidziridzwa nekukurumidza nekuti mumwe munhu ari kukupa "kupfuma nekukurumidza" kupa uye anovimbisa kukutengera uye nekukuchengetera mari. Sezvineiwo, vanhu vazhinji vanotamba mitambo yakaipa uye nhanho yezvirongwa zvekushambadzira zvakasiyana-siyana, kana [Ponzi schemes](https://anita.link/ponzi).
Kana mumwe munhu akakukumbira kuti "ujoine" Bitcoin kana kunyora "BitCoin", ziva. Iwe haufanire kujoinha chero chinhu kushandisa Bitcoin, hapana chikonzero chekutenga pasuru yekupinda kana chero chinhu chakadaro - izvi zvingangove zvitsotsi.
Kana iwe wakamirira kutenga Bitcoin ETF, hausi wega bitcoin uye hauzoshandisa bitcoin. Iwe unozongoratidzwa chete kune mutengo chiito. Iwe chete ndiwe uye unodzora bitcoin yako kana iwe ukagadzirisa ako ega makiyi. Unogona kuwana kuti ungazviita sei pamapeji anotevera.

299-privacy-and-KYC

Kuvanzika muDigital Age
Bitcoin is pseudonymous. Izvi zvinoreva kuti chikwama chako nemakero eBitcoin hazvina kubatanidzwa nekuzivikanwa kwako sezvo zita rako, nzvimbo yaunogara kana IP kero inochengetwa.
Kunze kweizvi kugadzira mushandisi account pane yepakati Bitcoin exchange kana iwe uchichinjana fiat ye bitcoin. Pano, semabhangi echinyakare, humbowo hwekuzivikanwa uye kunyoreswa hunogona kudiwa. Mune mamwe mamiriro ezvinhu, mahofisi emitero uye masangano ehurumende anogona kumanikidza shanduko kuti ibudise yako yekuzivisa data uye ine hukama neBitcoin kero.
Kana iwe ukaburitsa kero yako yeBitcoin painternet kana kuizivisa kupi kumwe, munhu wese anogona kutarisa kuti mangani emari yaunayo mune block explorer. Ngwarira neizvi uye usashandise iyo yakafanana Bitcoin kero. Iwo wallet andichakupa kwauri gare gare anongogadzira akawanda akasiyana Bitcoin kero saka haufanirwe kunetsekana nazvo.
Bitcoin haina kuzivikanwa sezvainowanzo fungwa. Kuyerera kwese kwemari kunogona kuongororwa nekuedza kwakakwana. Makambani akadai seChainalysis anonyanya hunyanzvi mukuongororwa kwedata hombe uye vatengi, semabhangi, vanogona kubhadhara sevhisi iyi. Basa riri kuenderera mberi rekuvandudza kuvanzika kweBitcoin. Mumakore maviri anotevera, pachava nemitsva pano iyo isingakanganise kushandiswa kweBitcoin uye inopa mamwe kuchengetedzwa kwedata.
Iyo cryptocurrency Monero, iyo yave iripo kubva 2014, inopa yatove yakavakirwa-mukati kuchengetedzwa kwekuvanzika. Pano maadero haaonekwe pachena uye kuongorora kwe blockchain hakugoneke.

300-how-to-get-bitcoin

Ini Ndinowana Sei Bitcoin?
Unogona kuwana bitcoin nenzira nhatu:
munotsinhanisa fiat nokuda kwayo
unoiwana
unoirera wega
Sarudzo yekutanga ndiyo iyo vazhinji vedu tinosarudza. Iwe unogona kushandisa online exchange kana Bitcoin ATM uye kutengesa yako fiat mari ye bitcoin.
Kuiwana ndiyo sarudzo iri nani. Unogona kusunungura imba yako yepasi uye kutengesa zvinhu zve bitcoin, kana kushanda se freelancer uye kubhadharwa mu bitcoin et cetera.
Kuchera haisi sarudzo yedzimba zhinji dzakazvimirira zvakare. Mumazuva ekutanga eBitcoin, zvaigoneka kumigodhi pakombuta yako. Nhasi, hardware yakaoma - ASICs miners - inodiwa uye iwe unoda yakachipa yakanyanya sosi yemagetsi kuti urambe uine pundutso.
Muzvitsauko zvinotevera, tichapinda mune zvinodiwa kubata nekushandisa Bitcoin.

301-staircase

Iyo Staircase yeKutonga Kwemari
"Kwete makiyi ako, kwete mari yako." - **Andreas M. Antonopoulos**
Sezvawakaverenga muzvitsauko zvakapfuura, simba rekutanga reBitcoin kusarongeka kwayo, izvo zvinokupa hutongi hwemari. Ndiko - kunze kweiyo yakatarwa 21 miriyoni inopa - iyo huru yekusiyanisa kune ese mamwe marudzi emari. Iyo inokudzivirira kubva kubheyili-ins senge muCyprus muna 2014 uye kubva mukukwira kwemitengo inoderedza mari yako. Inopedza kusimbiswa kwemari yemari yako kuburikidza nemabhengi uye zvigadzirwa zvemari. Inokupa kutonga kwakazara pamusoro pemari yako, inoita kuti ufambe pasirese uchiuya nemari yako newe. Ndiyo imwe nzira, yekubuda mufiat system - zvese zvaunoda mazwi gumi nemaviri echiRungu: mutsara wemhodzi yako.
Bitcoin haigoneki uye haina-inflatable. Aya ndiwo maitiro ayo anonyanya kukosha. - **Anita Posch**
Kana iwe usina iwo mazwi emutsara wemhodzi, hauna ropafadzo uye rusununguko rwataurwa pamusoro apa.
Njodzi dzezvikwama zvekufamba nazvo
Zvakakosha kuziva kuti pane musiyano mukuru pakati pezvikwama zvekuchengeta uye zvisiri zvekuchengetedza wallet. Iwe unongowana kutonga kwemutsara wemhodzi kana iwe ukashandisa isiri-yekuchengeta (yega-yega) chikwama. Kuchinjana seCoinbase, Kraken, Binance, Bitpanda, nezvimwewo, hazvikupe makiyi akavanzika kune ako wallet. Kunyange zvingave zviri nyore kubata bitcoin muchikwama pane imwe nzvimbo yekutsinhana, hazvina kusiyana nebhangi. Iwe hausi wega bitcoin muakaundi yako yekutsinhana, inogona kuve dambudziko hombe kana shanduko ikabiwa, chimwe chinhu chakatoitika kakawanda. Semuenzaniso, ndinokuyeuchidza nezve Mt. Gox, hombe huru kusvika parizvino yakaitika muna 2014. Hapana zuva rinopfuura pasina nyaya dzeakaunzi akavharwa nechando, kana kucherechedzwa kwemari ine tsvina uye, dzimwe nguva, kumiswa kwekutengesa. Zvakare, izvo zvekutsinhana zvinoda kuti iwe unyore uye uzadzise zvese zvinodiwa zvekuzivikanwa zveKYC (ziva-wako-mutengi uye mutemo unopokana nekubira mari), inova chipingamupinyi kumabhiriyoni evanhu, vasingabatanidzi kubva kubhengi uye ikozvino kubva pakushandisa crypto exchanges. zvakare. Pamusoro peizvozvo, iyi mirairo yeKYC iri kupindira pakuvanzika kwako. Neraki, Bitcoin yakavakirwa munhu wese. Kuti uderedze njodzi dzekupikisa-bato dzekuchengetedza wallet unofanirwa kusvetuka kuchinjana uku uye kushandisa chikwama chisiri chekuchengetedza kubva pakutanga.
Inhema yekuti mari mubhangi yakachengeteka kupfuura mari pasi pematiresi inzvimbo yeropafadzo. - **Andreas M. Antonopoulos**
Kune vanhu vari kunze kwe "nyika dzekumadokero dzakasimukira", hakuna chinhu chakadai seakaundi yakachengeteka yekubhanga. Iyi iropafadzo. Iwe unogona kufunga kuti ungada kusiya mari yako pakutsinhana nekuti haudi kuve nekunetseka uye basa rekubata mari yako. Unogona kuzviita, asi hazvisi izvo zvaidiwa naSatoshi Nakamoto uye zvinokuita kuti uve panjodzi.
Kana uchinge wadzidza uye nekuita matanho ekusununguka kwemari, uchaona kuti hazvina kuoma sezvazvingangotanga kuita.
3 Matanho eKutonga Kwemari
Nekusununguka kukuru, kunouya mutoro mukuru. - **Dr. Stephanie Murphy**
Stephanie Murphy, mubatsiri we "Speaking of Bitcoin" podcast, anoronga modhi yerusununguko rwemari semasitepisi ane mazinga akasiyana ehuchangamire. Sezvo Bitcoin iri tekinoroji mukusimudzira, giredhi rerusununguko iro munhu anogona kusvika riri kuchinja nguva dzese. Iri bhuku rinokupa nhungamiro yekusvika padanho rechipiri: iyo "Makiyi ako, makoini ako" nhanho. Kusvika padanho re "Usavimbe, simbisa" kuchava nyore mumakore anotevera. Parizvino inoda tekinoroji kuziva-kuita uye kuyedza kukuru munguva uye zviwanikwa, asi musimboti, munhu wese anogona kuisvika.
![3 nzira dzekusununguka kwemari](resources/_staircase-sovereignty-3-steps.png) [^68]
**Groundfloor** Iwe uri mutsva paBitcoin, sezvo uri kuverenga bhuku rangu unofanirwa kufarira Bitcoin, asi iwe hauna chero.
**1st floor** Uri kusvika pakuziva BTC inogadzirisa nhau yekuchengeta zvikwama pane imwe centralized exchange, asi haudzore chero makiyi. Iwe une imwe rusununguko nekuti wakaiswa mari mucryptocurrency uye kwete chete fiat zvakare. Asi hakusi kuzvimirira kwakawanda nekuti unovimba nemunhu wechitatu, izvo zvinouya nenjodzi dzataurwa pamusoro apa. Iwe uri pachidanho che **"kwete makiyi ako, kwete mari yako"** .
Zvakanaka, iwe unosvetuka pasi pekutanga uye enda kune yechipiri pasi nekukurumidza sezvinobvira.
**2nd floor** Iwe tora kutonga kwemakiyi ako uye wozvichengeta zvakachengeteka pane isiri- chikwama chekufamba nacho inokupa mbeu yako. Iyi idanho repamusoro-soro rekutonga kwemari. Iwe unogona kuzviita nechikwama chenhare pane yako foni nemari diki kana - nzira yakanakisa uye inokurudzirwa zvakanyanya - nechikwama chekubata chemari yakakura. Iwe unosvika ku **"makiyi ako, mari yako"** nhanho. Wasvika padanho repamusoro-soro rekuzvimirira.
Kubva pano matanho ndeevashandisi vane ruzivo. Ivo vanokupa iwe kwakawedzera hutongi, kuvanzika uye kutonga pamusoro pe bitcoin yako.
**3rd floor** Iwe unowana hutongi hwakazara pamusoro pemari yako nekubatanidza chikwama chako chehardware neyako izere node. Nekuseta uku, haugone kungoona uye kugashira ruzivo nezve kutengeserana kwako asiwo simbisa zvivharo zvakacherwa uye kutengeserana pasina kuvimba nemapato matatu. Iwe haufanirwe kuvimba nemumwe munhu zvakare uye uve nepamusoro mwero wekuvanzika uye kutonga. **"Iwe ndiwe bhangi rako"** uye zvino wasvika pa chidanho che**"Usavimbe, nyatsotarisa"** .
Iwe unogona kutora aya ekuchengetedza uye ekuzvimirira matanho zvakatowedzera nemhinduro diki diki, maitiro akawanda uye nezvimwe.
Pamusoro pemasitepisi, zvigadziriso zvemari zvakatemerwa senge bitcoin kukwereta uye kukweretesa kuri kubuda.
Pakupedzisira, kana zvose zvaunoda kuita ndezvekudzivirira kukwira kwemitengo uye kushandisa Bitcoin sechitoro chekukosha, ** kusvika pauriri hwechipiri, "kiyi dzako, mari yako" ndicho chinangwa **. Ini ndichakuratidza kuti ungasvika sei padanho rehuchangamire muzvitsauko zvinotevera.

302-Securing-coins

Kuchengetedza Mari Yako
Sezvakataurwa muchitsauko chapfuura, chinangwa chedu ndechekusvika padanho re "Makiyi ako, makoini ako".
Kutenga, kushandisa uye kuchengeta bitcoin, iwe uchada:
Bitcoin wallet = bhokisi rako redhipoziti redhijitari. Enzaniso yakanyatsojeka idhijitari kiyi-cheni yemabhokisi ako emari.
Bitcoin kero = kero imwe chete kana anopfuura akasiyana emari yako pane blockchain, yako yekugamuchira kero (chaizvo chaizvo isina kushandiswa transaction yakabuda UTXO)
Mbeu = iyo yekudzoreredza zve chikwama chako che Bitcoin.
Chikwama cheBitcoin
Funga nezvechikwama sechivharo chevoruzhinji-bhokisi rine zvikamu zvakawanda. Chero ani zvake anogona kuisa mari mune chimwe nechimwe chezvikamu. Muridzi wemakiyi ega ega ndiye anogona kuvhura chikamu uye kufambisa mari yainayo. Chikwama chako cheBitcoin chine zvikamu zvese uye chinobata ese makiyi akavanzika kuti avhure. Private kiyi uye Bitcoin kero anogadzirwa kubva kumbeu. Mbeu ndiwo mudzi wemakiyi ese nemakero, wakafanana nebucket umo makiyi ako ese akavanzika anochengetwa.

Chikwama iapp pafoni yako kana pakombuta yako, inobata zvese zviri kumashure - makiyi ako ega, kero dzako, uye kutumira nekugamuchira bitcoin.
Chikwama cheBitcoin chine makiyi, kwete mari. Mushandisi wega wega ane chikwama chine makiyi. Chikwama angori makiyi-cheni ane mapeya eakavanzika / eruzhinji makiyi. Mari yako yakanyorwa paBitcoin blockchain.
Bitcoin Kero
Kuti ugamuchire bitcoin, unoda kero yeBitcoin uko mumwe munhu anogona kukutumira bitcoin. Kero yeBitcoin ine nhevedzano yakareba yemadijiti nemabhii.
Muenzaniso wekero yeBitcoin: 346n4apJCQPg2XAXU3bfNQTogz4PyTkrEf
Kunyora manhamba makumi matatu nemana hazvigoneke, saka maQR macode emakero anowanzo shandiswa uye anowanzo gadzirwa otomatiki nechikwama chako.
![BTC kero seQR kodhi](zvishandiso/_kero-bhuku.PNG)
Bitcoin is pseudonymous, zvichireva kuti hapana chinodiwa kuti ubatanidze email kero yako kana chitupa chako nechikwama. Nekudaro, iyo Bitcoin blockchain iri pachena, zvinoreva kuti yako Bitcoin kero inoonekwa pachena painternet. Semuenzaniso, unogona kuitsvaga kuBlockcypher uye kuona zvese zvazvino zvekutengesa uye kukosha. Heinoi muenzaniso link: [https://anita.link/explorer](https://anita.link/explorer)
Naizvozvo, nekuda kwezvikonzero zvekuvanzika, usagovane kero dzako dzeBitcoin zvine chekuita nekuzivikanwa kwako painternet. Kuvanzika ndichowo chikonzero nei usingafaniri kushandisa zvakare kero. Mazhinji maBitcoin wallet anokupa otomatiki kero nyowani pane yega yega yekutengesa.
Ngatisvike pachikamu chakakosha chekuchengetedza bitcoin yako: mhodzi.
Mbeu neMakiyi Akavanzika
Sezvo mbeu iri mudzi wemakiyi ese akavanzika, hapana mumwe munhu anofanira kuwana kwairi. Munhu anoziva mbeu ndiye ane simba guru pamari.
Mbeu (dzimwe nguva inonzi mnemonic mutsara kana mutsara wekuchengetedza) mutsara wemashoko gumi nemaviri kana makumi maviri nemana anokupa iwe kuwana makiyi epachivande emakero echikwama chako, uye nekudaro kuwana mari yako. Izvi zvinoreva kuti kurongeka kwemazwi uku kunofanira kuramba kwakavanzika. Chero ani anoziva mbeu anogona kuwana uye kutora mari yako. Sei?
Mari yako haisi mukati medhijitari wallet yako sezvo iri mukati muchikwama chako yenguva dzose. Pane kudaro, zvakanyorwa pa blockchain. Enzanisa izvi neemail netsamba. Iwe unogona kuwana yako email akaundi kubva chero kupi zvako pasirese nekuti maemail ako anochengetwa online, nepo tsamba yako yakamira. Izvi zvinoshanda zvakafanana kuBitcoin.
Kuwanikwa kwepasirese kumidziyo yako kunogoneka nembeu, zvisinei nemugadziri wako wechikwama. Pakusarudza chikwama chako, tarisa izwi rekuti "HD wallet" (Hierarchical Deterministic). HD chikwama inokutendera kuti uchinje kune mumwe mugadziri HD chikamu, tora mbeu uye udzorere mari yako.
Ngatitii foni yako yashatiswa, hauchakwanise kuwana yako Bitcoin wallet app uye unofanirwa kuchinjira kune imwe foni. Iwe unoisa vhezheni nyowani yechikwama chako cheBitcoin uye wounza mbeu kubva pachikwama chako chekutanga. Kuwana mari yako kwadzorerwa.
Mbeu inogadzirwa newallet app panguva yekutanga kuseta. Zvikwama zvizhinji zvinokutungamirira kuburikidza nekugadzirisa uye zvinokuraira kunyora pasi mazwi embeu pabepa. Kana chikwama chako chikasachipa ipapo, tsvaga iyo "Gadzira Backup" kana "Backup" chimiro uye tevera matanho. Kusikwa kwembeu kunoshanda nenzira inopesana nekugadzirwa kwepassword sezvaunowanzo kuzviziva pamawebhusaiti. Hausi iwe unosarudza password, asi wallet pachayo.
Kurongeka kwemazwi KWAKOSHA! Unofanira kunyora pasi mazwi acho chaizvo munhevedzano yaanoita.
Nyora mbeu neruoko pabepa woichengeta zvakachengeteka. Usatore skrini, usaichengete pafoni yako kana komputa yakabatana neinternet sezvo nzvimbo dzese idzi dzinogona kubiwa. Pane rumwe ruzivo nezve chengetedzo muchitsauko 5.
Sezvo mari yako isiri mukati mechikwama chako asi yakachengetwa pa blockchain, unogona kufamba pasi rose uye kutora mari yako bitcoin kwese kwaunoenda. Iwe unongoda kurangarira mazwi 12-24 mhodzi nenzira kwayo. Mushure mekupfuura tsika pasina nharembozha, unozvitsvagira chikwama chitsva uye unopinza mbeu. Mashiripiti.
[^69]: Anita Posch, inspired by Andreas M. Antonopoulos

400-Wallets

Mhando dzezvikwama
Kune marudzi akasiyana ewallet zvichienderana nemudziyo, kuchengetedza zvinodiwa uye inotsigirwa cryptocurrencies. Kuti usarudze kuti ndechipi chikwama chakakunakira iwe ini ndinokupa dzimwe pfungwa uye indasitiri zviyero sekutungamira. Pakupedzisira, iwe unofanirwa kusarudza kuti ndechipi chikwama chakakunakira iwe. Sezvo Bitcoin iri tekinoroji yakadaro, iri kuchinja nguva dzose. Iwe unofanirwa kufunga kuti iwe uchafanirwa kuita upgrades uye dzimwe nguva shandura chikwama chekugadzira nekuda kwekushanda kutsva, pane nguva dzose zvikwama zvitsva pamusika. Izvi hazvifanirwe kukudzima, ini ndinongoda kukuzivisa iwe nezvazvo. Mumakore mashoma apfuura, ndakashandisa wallet yakawanda kuti ndivayedze kana kukwanisa kushandisa mashandiro matsva. Naizvozvo ini ndichakurudzira mawallet andakashandisa ini uye ane mukurumbira wakanaka pakati penyanzvi dzeindasitiri.
Chengetedzo yezvikwama
Iyo yakachengetedzwa zvirinani mhando yechikwama inobva kunze kwekurwiswa pamusoro peinternet, iyo yakanyanya kuchengetedzwa. Naizvozvo, chikamu chakakosha chiri pakati pekupisa kwekuchengetedza uye kutonhora kwekuchengetedza mhinduro. Mawallet anopisa, senge nharembozha uye desktop wallet, maapplication anobatana neinternet uye nekudaro ari panjodzi kubva kune vanoba, mavhairasi kana kudzora uye kupikisa-bato njodzi. Chengetedza yemhinduro senge zvikwama zvinobatika hadzina kumbobvira dziri mumhepo uye nekudaro dzakachengetedzeka zvakanyanya.
Pamusoro pezvo, yako foni, ingave Android kana iOS, yakachengeteka kupfuura laptop yako kana PC. Desktop Windows masisitimu haana kuchengetedzeka zvishoma pane Apple zvishandiso panguva yekunyora. Mukati meakasiyana siyana anoshanda masisitimu e-foni, pane misiyano mishoma padanho rekuchengetedza.
Pamusoro pekufunga uku, unofanirwa kushandisa chikwama chinotsigira yako yaunofarira cryptocurrencies. Sezvo iri BTC gwara, ndinokurudzira kuti ushandise bitcoin-chete chikwama. Iyo yakawanda cryptocurrencies yakadai sechikwama chinofanirwa kubata, iyo yakanyanya kuoma kusimudzira uye kugadzirisa kwemhando kunobva kumagumo emugadziri. Kuwedzera kuomarara kunounza njodzi dzakakwirira dzezvimhingamupinyi uye kusasimba.
Mumakore kubva pakaburitswa Bitcoin, kushandisa chikwama chekubata kwakaratidza kuti ndiyo nzira yakanakisa yekuchengeta makiyi ako ega. Chikwama chekubata kamudziyo kadiki kanochengeta makiyi akavanzika pasina Indaneti, akafanana netsvimbo yeUSB.
Zvikwama zvemumhepo zvinoda kugadziriswa uye komputa kana smartphone. Kana iwe usingade kunetseka nezve magadzirirwo azvo, kana kuti usiri yako mudziyo wakadaro, unogona kushandisa Kadhi chikwama seimwe mhando yekuchengetedza imwe nzira. Icho chigadzirwa chekare neAustria bitcoin broker Coinfinity uye Austrian State Printing House.
Zvinodiwa mu industry
Muchiitiko chega chega, iwe unofanirwa kuvimba nevagadziri vehomwe kusvika padanho repamusoro kana diki. Iyo ** indasitiri inofarirwa uye inokurudzirwa inotonhora yekuchengetedza mhinduro zvikwama zvebitcoin **.
Zvichienderana nehuwandu hwechikwama chako chaunofanira kutarisira, zvakajairwa kushandisa musanganiswa we ** chikwama chemufoni nemari diki yaunoda kuva newe paunenge uchienda ** uye ** Chikwama che hadhiweya yemari yakawanda senge yakachengetedzwa mune yako. akaundi yebhanga**.
Kana mari yako yebitcoin ichisvika pamari yaungade kuchengetedza kusvika padanho repamusoro, saka iwe unofanirwa kutsvaga mhinduro dzakawanda-siginecha. Asi ziva: Multi-sig mhinduro hadzisi dzevanotanga **! Iwe unofanirwa chaizvo kuziva zvauri kuita.
Seimwe nzira, unogona kushandisa kambani inonzi Casa uye yavo indasitiri inotungamira akawanda-sig mhinduro. Kana kuti iwe unogona kuwana akati wandei mawallet ekutsemura mari yako kune mamwe maturusi, izvo zvinoderedza njodzi yechigadzirwa kana kukanganisa kwemugadziri.
Zvinokuridzirwa pazvikwama
Chengetedzo inopisa
**Zvikwama zvemufoni** Ye iOS ne Android
[Blockstream Green](https://blockstream.com/green/) (Bitcoin non-custodial, Liquid)
[Breez Wallet](https://breez.technology/) (Lightning non-custodial)
Kana iwe uchida kushandisa Bitcoin uye micro-kubhadhara paMheni Network:
[Muun Wallet](https://muun.com/) (Bitcoin and Lightning non-custodial)
[Blue Wallet](https://bluewallet.io/) (Bitcoin non-custodial and Lightning custodial)
[Electrum](https://electrum.org) (Bitcoin and Lightning non-custodial, for more tech-savvy users)
**Chikwama chepa dhesikitopu** Nekuda kwenjodzi dzekuchengetedza dzataurwa pamusoro, ini handishandise wallet yesoftware pakombuta yangu, kunze kwekunge ndaashandisa pamwe chete nechikwama che hadhiweya. Kune izvi, ini ndinoshandisa Electrum kana software yemugadziri wehardware.
[Blockstream Green](https://blockstream.com/green/) (Bitcoin non-custodial, Liquid)
[Blue Wallet](https://bluewallet.io/) (Bitcoin non-custodial and Lightning custodial)
[Electrum](https://electrum.org) (Bitcoin and Lightning non-custodial, for more tech-savvy users)
Chengetedzo Inotonhora
**Zvikwama zvehadhiweya**
Hardware wallet inobata mari yako, bitcoin kero uye akabatana makiyi akavanzika pasina ivo "vanobata" internet. Kunyangwe mudziyo wako uine hutachiona kana kuti wakabiwa, mari yako yakachengeteka uye unogona kutumira nekugamuchira mubhadharo. Iwe unofanirwa kusimbisa mashandisirwo ezvishandiso pazvishandiso izvi zvekunze - izvi zvinogonesa kuti hapana anopinda pakombuta yako anogona kutora mari yako.
Vanotevera vagadziri uye zvishandiso vachangobva kuzvisimbisa ivo pachavo mumusika wehardware wallet mumakore achangopfuura. SatoshiLabs kubva kuPrague yanga ichigadzira zvikwama zvehardware kubvira 2012. Kambani Ledger kubva kuParis yakavambwa muna 2014. SHIFT Cryptosecurity kubva kuZurich yanga iri pamusika kubva 2015 uye kambani yeCanada Coinkite yanga iri munzvimbo yeBitcoin kubvira 2012.
BitBox02 bitcoin-only edition https://anita.link/bitbox02 (my readers get 5 % off) - SHIFT Cryptosecurity
Trezor One, Model T https://anita.link/trezor - SatoshiLabs
Ledger Nano S, Nano X https://anita.link/ledger - Ledger
Coldcard (for tech-savvy users) https://anita.link/coldcard - Coinkite
Coldcard yakasiyana nemamwe mamodheru nekuti imudziyo wakavharwa nemhepo - inogona kushandiswa isina kumbobatanidzwa nekombuta. Ndosaka vamwe vanhu vachizvidaidza sekuchengetedza kutonhora-kutonhora, kuve yakachengeteka zvakanyanya. Kune vatsva, ini ndinokurudzira imwe yemidziyo mitatu yekutanga yekambani.
Usambofa watenga chikwama chehardware kubva kune vausingazive paBay kana Amazon, uye zvechokwadi, usachitenga chechipiri ruoko. Gara uchitenga zvakananga kubva kuwebhusaiti yemugadziri, peji remugadziri weAmazon kana mutengesi waunovimba naye. Ita shuwa kuti mudziyo wakavharwa sezvakataurwa pawebhusaiti yemugadziri. Zvizhinji zvezvishandiso zvinokurudzirwa pamusoro zvine tamper-inooneka kurongedza kuti ive nechokwadi chekuti mudziyo unoshandiswa kekutanga uye hauna kushandiswa. Ledger anosarudza nemaune kusashandisa anti-tamper seals pakurongedzerwa kwayo nekuti anogona kunge ari emanyepo. Genuine Ledger midziyo ine yakachengeteka chip inodzivirira kubata kwemuviri uye inobvumira vashandisi kuona iyo software uye hardware kutendeseka vachishandisa Ledger's madhiraivha. Chero zvazvingava: hapana mugadziri ari kutumira mbeu nemudziyo!
Pamusoro pemudziyo, mutengesi anopa wallet software yekutarisira mari yako. Nezvikonzero zvekuvanzika, vashandisi vazhinji vanotora chikwama chemutengesi chete kuti vaite kutanga uye kuchengetedza kwechishandiso (nyora pasi mhodzi) uye yekuvandudza firmware. Mushure meizvozvo, vanoshandisa chikwama seElectrum kubata mari.
**Zvikwama zvepasina indaneti** **Zvikwama zvemapepa** Paindaneti, iwe unowana kurudziro yekushandisa zvikwama zvemapepa. Iwo anozvigadzira ega bitcoin kero nemakiyi avo ega uye eruzhinji aunogona kudhinda pabepa. Sezvo iwe uchigadzira uye nekuadhinda iwe pachako, haufanirwe kushandisa mari pazviri. Asi, dzakaoma kugadzira zvakachengeteka. Matanho ekuchengetedza aunofanira kutora akanyanya kukwirira. **Ndinopa zano kusashandisa ivo **.
Chaizvoizvo, kana iwe usingade kubhadhara iyo 50 - 100 USD inodiwa kutenga chikwama chehardware kuchengetedza mari yakakwira kupfuura yaunotakura wakasununguka pafoni yako, saka unofanirwa kufunga zvakare kushandisa bitcoin sechitoro chekukosha kwekutanga.
Kana iwe usingakwanise kutenga chikwama chehardware, shandisa foni yako panguva ino. Paunenge uchinge wachengeta mari yakakwana, zvitore iwe hardware wallet.
**Chikwama chekadhi** Iyo chikwama chekadhi (chigadzirwa) iri musimboti chikwama chebepa, asi chinogadzirwa nenyanzvi dzine yakakwirira kuchengetedza zviyero. Nekudaro, iwe unofanirwa kuvimba nevagadziri kuti vasarekodha makiyi akavanzika kune kadhi. Unogona kushandisa Chikwama chekadhi seimwe nzira kana iwe usina komputa kana foni kana usiri kuda kutarisira kuchengetedza kwechikwama chako chehardware. https://cardwallet.com/anita (vaverengi vangu vanowana 20% kubva)
Iyo indasitiri inosarudzwa uye ** yakakurudzirwa kutonhora yekuchengetedza mhinduro zvikwama zvehadhiweya **.

500-security-measures

Kuchengeta Mari Yesimbi Zvakachengeteka
Matanho Okuchengetedza
Yese dhatabhesi inogona kubiwa. Tsvaga email yako pa https://haveibeenpwned.com/ - kana uine rombo rakanaka kuti hauna kubirwa, asi mabhiriyoni emamwe maakaundi. Naizvozvo, zvakakosha kutevedzera  kuchengetedzwa matanho anoshanda zvakanyanya paunenge uchishandisa Bitcoin.
Kugadzira hadhiweya nesofutiweya
Unogona kushandisa mabhurawuza ane mukurumbira akadai seFirefox, Opera, Brave kana Chrome. Mabrowser ekuwedzera anovhara Javascript uye Cookies anokurudzirwa. Ghostery, NoScript uye ScriptSafe ndiyo mhando yekuwedzera yaunogona kuwedzera kubrowser yako. "HTTPS kwese kupi" inomanikidza kubatana kweSSL kune ese mawebhusaiti, kusanganisira ayo asati apa SSL.
Ziva kuti zvimwe zvitoro zvepamhepo hazvishande nemazvo neaya ekuwedzera akabatidzwa, saka unofanirwa kudzima nemaoko.
Zvakakosha kuti uchengetedze midziyo yako.
Zviziviso
Zano iri rinoshanda kune ako ese maturusi: ita zvese zvinokurudzirwa sofutiweya zvigadziriso. Yekombuta yako yekushandisa sisitimu pamwe neyeyako foni. Gara uchishandisa yazvino vhezheni yechikwama chako uye femuweya sofutiweya pane chako chechikwama chehadhiweya.
Email Kero
Usashandise email kero pane zvese. Zviwanire kero dzeemail dzinoraswa dzaunoshandisa kamwe chete. Iwe unogona zvakare kutenga domain iyo iwe yaunoshandisa chete emanyepo email kero yaunotumira kune yako huru kero.
Chengetedza Mapassword
Shandisa mapassword akachengeteka kune ese masevhisi epamhepo. Zuva rako rekuzvarwa, kwaunogara, zita rekatsi yako kana 1234567 haasi mapassword akachengeteka. Mitsara yese ine manhamba, nzvimbo, mabhii makuru neadiki uye mavara akakosha mapassword akasimba.
Shandisa password yakasiyana kune yega yega webhusaiti yaunopinda mairi. Zvikasadaro, hacker ine password imwe chete inogona kupinda masevhisi ese awakanyoreswa nawo. Usachengete mapassword aya muIzwi faira kana chero chinhu chakadaro pakombuta yako. Gwaro reShoko riri nyore kuti matsotsi aba nekuverenga.
Unogona kushandisa sofutiweya senge 1Password, Bitwarden kana KeePass (yemahara uye yakavhurika sosi). Aya akavharidzirwa password dhatabhesi, kwaunogona kugadzira uye kuchengeta mapassword ako ese uye iwe unongoda kurangarira password imwe chete kuti uivhure.
PIN
Gadzira PIN yewallet software yako kuitira kuti pasave nemunhu anogona kuvhura chikwama chako zviri nyore pane chako kifaa.

Shandisa 2 factor authentication nzira kuchengetedza maakaundi ako. Usashandise SMS / zvinyorwa seyo 2 factor yekusimbisa nzira nekuda kweSIM swapping kurwiswa. Pane kudaro, isa app yechokwadi yakafanana neOTP kana TOTP pafoni yako.
Kuchinja kweSIM
Kuchinja kweSIM ndiko kana mumwe munhu akabira SIM yako uye nhamba yefoni. Ivo vanogona kuzoshandisa nhamba yako yefoni kupinda kune ese akabatana maakaundi kwawakamisa 2 chinhu chechokwadi nemavara/SMS. SIM swapping iko kurwiswa kuti upinde muakaundi yako yekutanga email. Kana vanorwisa vachikwanisa kuwana iyo yekutanga email account yakabatana ne2FA kunhamba yako yefoni, vanogona kuwana ese Bitcoin akaundi yekuchinja auri kushandisa ne2FA vodzima.
Kurwiswa kunowanzotangwa nekufonera vatengi masevhisi kune wako telecom mupi (Verizon, Vodafone, AT & T, Magenta,...). Vanotaura vachitevedza mitsara yekuti "Ndini muridzi wenhare, ndarasa foni yangu please transfer number dzangu kuSIM yangu itsva". Munhu webasa revatengi anokumbira chidimbu cheruzivo rwemunhu kuti aone chitupa chako. Vanorwisa vachabva vaedza mazano akawanda. Ivo vanobheja munhu werutsigiro kuti vawane zvidimbu zvidiki zveruzivo kubva kwavari, sungirira uye kufonera mumwe munhu uye kushandisa iyo snippet yeruzivo kuvaka kune inotevera nhanho. Ivo vanobva vawana rumwe ruzivo uye voramba vachivaka kusvika vawana ruzivo rwakakwana kunyengetedza munhu wekupedzisira kuti ndivo muridzi weakaundi uye kuti SIM itakurwe.
Ivo vanozoenda mushure mekuchinjana kwese kwe crypto kwaungave wakamisa akaundi ine email kero uye nhamba yefoni.
Kana vaziva email yako, vanoedza kushandura password yeakaundi yako ne "forgot password" mashandiro. Mawebhusaiti akanaka haavaudze kana iyo account iripo. Vanorwisa vanoedza kuita password reset kana kuyedza kuwana meseji yekuongorora.
Kana vaziva email yako, vanoedza kushandura password yeakaundi yako ne "forgot password" mashandiro. Mawebhusaiti akanaka haavaudze kana iyo account iripo. Vanorwisa vanoedza kuita password reset kana kuyedza kuwana meseji yekuongorora.
Phishing Attacks
Muna 2020, dhatabhesi yekushambadzira yeFrench hadhiweya inogadzira Ledger yakabiwa. Midziyo yacho yakachengeteka, asi zviuru zvekero dzeemail, nhamba dzenhare uye kunyange kero dzepamba dzevatengi dzakaburitswa uye dzinogona kuwanikwa nemunhu wese paindaneti. Iyi injodzi yakakwana nekuti pane mukana wakakura wekuti vanhu vanoodha chikwama chehardware yavo bitcoin futi. Mumamiriro ezvinhu akaipisisa, iwe ucha "shanyirwa" kumba. Kunyanya kutyisidzira kuburikidza neemail uye phishing kurwisa. Kuti udzivise izvi, ramba uchifunga kuti haungambodi kushandisa kero yako yepanyama kuendesa yeBitcoin ine chekuita nechigadzirwa senge hardware wallet. Unogona kuzvirongera bhokisi rekutumira. MuUS kune masevhisi anogona kukugamuchira tsamba (CMRAs). Kana zvichibvira, usatomboshandisa zita rako chairo pakuhodha. Zvitore iwe yechipiri nhamba yefoni uye shandisa iyi kana mutengesi akakumbira imwe. Vape kero yeemail inoraswa yaunoshandisa chete kune iyi chaiyo odha.
Phishing kurwiswa kuedza kukutyisa kana kukunyengera kuti uise mazwi embeu yako pawebhusaiti yeanorwisa. Semuenzaniso, unogona kugamuchira email ichiti: " Ledger mudziyo wako wakaora kana kudzima, shanyira iyi link uye uise yako 12 mashoko embeu kuti muchengetedze mari yenyu." kana "Taona kubviswa kukuru kubva muLedger yenyu. Une maawa makumi maviri nemana ekupindura kuti kutengeserana uku kushande. Tine hurombo, hatikwanise kusvika kuLedger yako inoita kunge yakaora. Isu tichakupa mvumo yekubvisa kunze kwekunge watanga hurongwa hwekudzoreredza, tipe mazwi ako makumi maviri nemana embeu." kana "watambira airdrop. Mari irikuuya muaccount mako, chatinoda chete kuongororwa, ndapota tanga kupora gadzirisa uye utipe mazwi ako makumi maviri nemana embeu.

Vanokurwisa vanoedza kuita kuti uite nekukurumidza usingafungi. Kana ukagamuchira tsamba yakadaro. Mira. Usaita chero chinhu. Nekuti hapana anogona kutora mari yako, hapana anogona kudzima chikwama chako chehardware kure. Ndiyo nzvimbo yese yemari yakadzikiswa senge bitcoin. "

Mabhurawuza akaita seOpera neChrome achakuyambira, asi Firefox haiite izvi nekukasira. Unogona kushandura izvozvo nekugonesa "punycode" muFirefox, ona [anita.link/puny](https://anita.link/puny).
3-2-1 Mutemo Wekuchengeta Mbeu Yako
Mbeu iyi ine mazwi gumi nemaviri - 24 echirungu. Mazuva ano, zvikwama zvakawanda zvinoshandisa mazwi gumi nemaviri panzvimbo ye24 nokuti anopa hutano hwakakwana hwekuchengeteka uye zviri nyore kuyeuka nekuchengetedza.
Nyora mbeu pabepa neruoko paunotanga kuvhura chikwama chako. Ita shuwa kuti kurongeka kwacho uye tarisa mazwi akanyorwa kakawanda. Ziva mutengesi, modhi uye chikwama software futi. Iwe unogona kuda ruzivo urwu kana iwe uchida kudzoreredza mari yako.
Kana iwe ukamisa chikwama chehardware unofanirwa kutumira zvishoma bitcoin kwairi kuti uve nechokwadi chekuti zvese zvinoshanda. Mushure mekugamuchira iyo shoma, bvisa software kubva pachigadzirwa uye udzorere nemashoko awakambonyora pasi. Iri inhanho yakakosha yausingafanire kusvetuka.
Mushure mezvo, zvinokurudzirwa kutora matanho anotevera ekuchengetedza kudzivirira kuti usarasikirwe nembeu yako. Kana vanhu vatadza kuwana mari yavo kazhinji kazhinji nekuti vanenge varasikirwa nembeu yavo kana kukanganisa kunyora pasi kwete nekuti michina yavo yakabiwa.
**3**: Nyora mbeu katatu
**2**: Pamusoro pemidhiya miviri yakasiyana (lamineti bepa, rakanyorwa kana kudhindwa pasimbi) woichengeta munzvimbo yakachengetedzeka kuitira dziviriro pamoto, kurasikirwa uye kuba.
** 1**: uyezve, chengetedza backup mune imwe nzvimbo, zviri nani ingangoita 100 makiromita kure.
Jameson Lopp, mumwe wevangu podcast vaenzi, ari kuyedza mahwendefa esimbi anogona kushandiswa kuchengetedza mbeu kwenguva refu. Anovafumura kumoto uye kudzvanywa kuti vatarise hupenyu hurefu. Hazvisi zvese zvigadzirwa zvakagadzirwa nesimbi kana titanium, ndosaka zvichinyungudika mumoto. Iwo maedzo anogona kuwanikwa pano: [anita.link/metalseed](https://anita.link/metalseed)
Usave nekugadzira! Kupatsanura mazwi muzvikamu zviviri kana kupfuura uye kuachengeta munzvimbo dzakasiyana kukanganisa kwakajairika. Iwe unongoda kurasikirwa chikamu chimwe chete uye hauchakwanisa kuwana makoini ako.
Usambopa mbeu kumunhu wausingavimbi nemari yako!
Usaise mbeu pane chero mawebhusaiti kana zvigadzirwa zvemagetsi!
Mbeu haifanirwe kutumira kana kugamuchira bitcoin.
Hapana munhu kana sangano rinovimbika ringakumbira mbeu yako.
Tarisa nzvimbo dzekuchengetera mazwi embeu yako nguva nenguva!
Gadzira hurongwa hwenhaka - zvakaipisisa zvinoitika uye kana ukasadzidzisa vako vanobatsirwa nemazvo, bitcoin yako inorasika. Ndinokurudzira bhuku raPamela Morgan pa "Cryptoasset Inheritance Planning".
Passphrase
Mutsara ndiyo imwe nzira yekuchengetedza mari yako pamusoro pembeu. Kana iwe ukawedzera passphrase, sofutiweya inogadzira imwe chikwama chaunogona kushandisa kuti uzvidzivirire kubva pakurwiswa kwepanyama. Kana mumwe munhu akabata mbeu yako, haakwanise kuwana mari yako nekuti haana chirevo chekupfuura.
Muenzaniso: Ungangoda kusiya mashoma emari yako mune yekutanga "isina-passphrase" chikwama uye fambisa yakawanda yemari yako kuchikwama-yakachengetedzwa-yakachengetedzwa. Pfungwa iri shure kweizvi ndeyekuti kana ukazozviwana uri mumamiriro ezvinhu apo mumwe munhu ari kuyedza kukutorera rudzikinuro kana kukuisa pasi pekumanikidzwa, unogona kuvhura chikwama chako zvakachengeteka uye wongopa anorwisa mukana kune yakajairika wallet (iyo ine chete. mari shoma).
Izvi zvinonzwika zvakanaka, asi panewo njodzi dzinobatanidzwa.
Nekuti iyo passphrase haina kuchengetwa chero kupi zvako otomatiki, iwe unofanirwa kutora **ese anodiwa ekuchengetedza ** kuitira kuti uve nechokwadi chekuti passphrase inogara yakachengeteka uye inowanikwa semuenzaniso. nekuita backup yemuviri.
Kana iyo passphrase yakarasika, iwe ** hauchakwanise kuwana icho chikwama ** uye chero mari yakachengetwa muchikwama ichocho ichave isingawanike.
Nechirevo chekupfuura, haungofanire kuchengeta mbeu yako chete asi chirevo chekupfuura zvakare. Zvino iwe unofanirwa kuwana chengetedzo yenguva refu yembeu UYE chirevo chekupfuura, chinoita kuti ive yakaoma maitiro. Ziva: Kuti udzorere chikwama cherudzi urwu, unenge uchida mbeu yako UYE chirevo chawashandisa pachikwama ichocho kuti udzorere kuwana mari.
Sezvo kurwiswa kwemuviri kuchiitika kashoma, kuchengeta mbeu ne3-2-1 nzira kunofanirwa kukwana.
Dzimwe nzira dzekudzoreredza
Zvimwe zvikwama zvinoshandisa nzira dzakasiyana dzekuchengetedza. Semuenzaniso, chikwama cheMuun chinoshandisa musanganiswa wekodhi yekudzoreredza - yaunoda kunyora pasi sembeu - uye kiti chekukurumidzira.
Kudzidza Nekuita
Zvinogona kutyisa kutanga kushandisa Bitcoin nekuti imari chaiyo. Ndosaka iri tsika yakanaka kutanga nemari shoma.
Pakuedza kwako kwekutanga, isa chikwama pafoni yako, tsvaga [Bitcoin ATM](https://anita.link/atm) iri pedyo newe kana kuenda kumusangano weBitcoin wemuno mochinjana kamari kadiki. Tora chikwama chekombuta yako uye utumire bitcoin pakati pemawallet ako maviri kumakero akasiyana.
Nguva yakanakisa yekuita izvi kazhinji pakupera kwevhiki apo Mempool haina kuzara nekutengesa uye mubhadharo wakaderera.
Shandisa akasiyana amwe mazvikwama esofutiweya, dzosera mhodzi yechikwama kubva pachikwama A kusvika B, shandisa mbeu pamidziyo yakasiyana. Iwe uchanzwa zvakanyanya uye zvakanyanya kuchengetedza kuchengetedza hunyanzvi.
Edza Gamuchira Kero
Usati watumira mari yakawanda kekutanga, ita shuwa kuti kero yacho iri kubva kune anogamuchira uye ita diki bvunzo kutengeserana. Gara uchitarisa kero yeBitcoin kaviri kana katatu usati watumira kutengeserana. Enzanisa manhamba ekutanga neekupedzisira ekero. Bitcoin yaunotumira kukero isiriyo inorasika.
Kuzama chikwama chako chehadhiweya
Usati wachengeta mari yakawanda pane chitsva chikwama chehadhiweya, unofanira kutarisa kushanda uye mbeu.
Paunomisikidza mudziyo pakutanga, inokugadzirira mhodzi yaunonyora pasi neruoko (kuwedzera mutengesi, modhi uye software shanduro). Mushure mezvo, iwe unoshandisa mutengesi software (kana imwe software yakadai seElectrum) uye gadzira kero yekutanga yeBitcoin muchikwama chako chehardware nekudzvanya pa "Gamuchira". Wobva watumira mari shoma kwairi kubva kune yako yakamboiswa smartphone wallet. Kana mari iri pachikwama che hardware yasvika -status "yakasimbiswa" - muedzo wekutanga wakabudirira.
Zvakare, edza kutumira kubva kune chako chikwama chehadhiweya kune chimwe chikwama. Semuenzaniso, unogona kutumira mari shoma kune yako chikwama chemufoni kana imwe kero yechikwama chako chehadhiweya. Hazvina basa zvakanyanya. Chinhu chikuru ndechekuti uri kuyedza kubhadhara kubva kune chikwama chehadhiweya futi. Kuti uite izvi unofanirwa kutarisa kero yekugamuchira pane hardware chikwama uye simbisa kutumira nekamwe kana kupfuura kudzvanya zvakananga pane chikwama chehadhiweya. Iri bhuku rekusimbisa pamudziyo rinoita kuti chikwama chehadhiweya achengetedzeke sezvo iwe chete uchikwanisa kudzvanya mabhatani uye hapana anogona kurova mabhatani pamusoro peindaneti.
**Dzorera chikwama chako ** Wobva waita shuwa kuti une backup/mbeu yako! Mushure mezvo, bvisa data rese pane yako chikwama chehadhiweya. Vamwe vatengesi vanozvidaidza kuti "factory reset", "pukuta" kana "reset the device". Chikwama chako hachina chinhu. Zvino dzosa mari yako nechikwama nembeu. Izvi zvinodaidzwa kuti "Dzosera kubva kudzorere izwi", "Dzosa chikwama", kana "Import mbeu". Wobva waisa mutsara wemhodzi pamudziyo wehardware. Kana zvese zviri izvo, chikwama chinodzoserwa uye unogona kuona kutengeserana kwako kwekare uye chiyero.
** Simudzira Firmware uye Software ** Usangokiya mudziyo kure. Iwe unofanirwa kutsvaga zvigadziriso kune software kana ye firmware upgrades ingangoita mwedzi mitanhatu yega yega. Iyo crypto nzvimbo iri kukurumidza kufamba uye zvitsva zvinosanganiswa muwallet software nguva nenguva. 
Smartphone Yakarasika? Kombiyuta Yakabiwa?
Kurasika, Kuba, kana Kusashanda Kwechishandiso Chako
Kana mudziyo wako ukabiwa, yeuka kuti bitcoin yako ichiri kunyorwa pa blockchain pasi pekiyi yako yakavanzika. Sezvo iwe uchiseta PIN yekuwana chikwama, mbavha haigone kuivhura. Nekudaro, ivo vachiri kuedza kutsvaga nzira yekutsemura PIN yako.
Iwe unofanirwa kuisa chikwama chitsva nekukasira kunze mbeu yawakachengeta yakachengeteka kuti uwanezve kuwana mari yako (ona "dzosa chikwama chako"). Zvadaro, fambisa mari kubva muchikwama chako chakabiwa kuenda kukero itsva yeBitcoin muchikwama chako chitsva nekukurumidza sezvaunokwanisa, uchidzokorora maitiro akafanana ekuchengetedza echikwama chitsva.
Kana mudziyo wako ukashatiswa, unotevera matanho mamwe chete, asi hapana chikonzero chekumhanya kufambisa mari yacho. Ingodzorera software chikwama uye wapedza.
