600-Bitcoin-price

Mutengo weBitcoin
Kudzorerera mutengo
Iko hakuna mutengo wepamutemo we bitcoin. Inotemerwa munguva chaiyo zvakasiyana pakutsinhana kwakafanana neKraken, Bitstamp, Coinbase, Binance etc. Kune masayiti akaita seCoinMarketCap, CoinGecko uye BitcoinAverage https://anita.link/average inokuratidza avhareji yepasi rose yemitengo yekutsinhana kwakati wandei. Kana kuti iwe unogona kuenda zvakananga kune webhusaiti yeimwe yekutsinhana uye tarisa iyo kumusoro.
Mutengo - unova mwero wekutsinhana - unotarwa nezviitiko zvevatengi uye vatengesi ve cryptocurrency vari kuitengesa munguva chaiyo. Kuwedzera kudiwa, mutengo wepamusoro. Kupa kushoma, mutengo wepamusoro. Ichi ndicho chikonzero kucheka kwehafu chiitiko chakakosha. Kunyangwe kudiwa kukaramba kwakafanana, iyo diki inopa inokwidza mutengo.
Bitcoin imusika wakavhurika. Basa remusika nderekutsvaga kuti chii chaicho kukosha kwe bitcoin. Mutengo wazvino wechinhu chero chipi zvacho mumusika wakavhurika ndiwo mutengo uchangoburwa uyo vanhu vakabvumirana uye vakatengeserana nawo. Hapana ari kuseta mwero wekuchinjana, mutengo we bitcoin unowanikwa.
Mutengo Wakasiyana Mudunhu
Kana iwe ukatarisa kumusoro kweyero yekutsinhana kwe bitcoin munyika dzakasiyana unowana misiyano pakati penyika. Semuyenzaniso, kutenga bitcoin muZimbabwe nemari yemuno kuchadhura kudarika neUSD. Hazvirevi nekuti bitcoin inodhura muZimbabwe, asi nekuti kudiwa kwemari yemuno kwakaderera. Haukwanise kufambisa Zimbabwe Dollar yako kunze kwenyika; even Zimbabweans vanoda USD. Saka, vanhu vanofanirwa kubhadhara mari yekutanga kutenga bitcoin kana vachishandisa mari yakaderera.
Yese-Nguva Yepamusoro Tracker
Peji yakanaka yekutarisa kuti uzive nguva kubva yekupedzisira Yese-Nguva Yepamusoro (ATH) iri Coingecko https://anita.link/ath
Bitcoin Calculator
Nezve kuomerwa kwekushandura satoshi kune dzimwe mari, semubvunzo "" Yakawanda sei 0.05 bitcoin kana 10,000 satoshi mumari yangu yefiat?":
Heino iri nyore kushandisa Calculator: https://anita.link/calc
Bitcoin mari inoshandura: http://preev.com"

700-Invest-in-Bitcoin

Maitiro ekuisa mari muBitcoin
Muchitsauko chino, tichaongorora nzira dzakasiyana dzaunogona kuwana bitcoin. Kazhinji, izvi zviri kuburikidza nekutenga bitcoin nekutsinhanisa iyo fiat mari kana nekuiwana. Nzira dzinosiyana padanho rekuzvitonga uye kuvanzika kwaunogona kuwana.
Kutenga Bitcoin - Kuiita yako
Muzviitiko zvakawanda, kudyidzana kwekutanga kwevanhu nekriptovalty kuri kuburikidza nekutsinhana kwekuchengetedza seKraken, Coinbase, Binance, Bitpanda uye Bitfinex kungotaura zvishoma.
Ivo vanonzi kuchengetedzwa nekuti vane makiyi e bitcoin yako. Iwe unowana chikwama pamapuratifomu aya, asi zvakaita seakaundi yebhangi, zvichitungamira kune njodzi dzebato senge kubira, kubvuta kana kutorwa nehurumende.
Kutengeserana pakuchinjana uku kunoitwa off-chain, zvichireva kuti kutengeserana hakuna kugadzikiswa pa blockchain asi kunongodzorwa mukati meiyo dhatabhesi yepuratifomu. Izvi zvinowedzera kukurumidza kwekutengesa, asi panguva imwe chete kunotungamirira kushayikwa kwekujeka uye kuchengeteka.
Kuti uwane bitcoin nenzira yekuchengetedza, unofanirwa kuvhura account, kutevedzera KYC uye AML kunyoresa maitiro uye wozoisa fiat mari muakaundi yepuratifomu. Mushure mekunge mari yako yasvika iwe unogona kuitengesa kune bitcoin kana mamwe makristptocurrencies.
Sezvakataurwa muchitsauko 4 "The Staircase of Financial Changamire", kuti uderedze njodzi dzinopikisa dzemawallet ekuchengetedza iwe unofanirwa kutumira mari yako kuchikwama chako wega kana kusvetuka kuchinjana uku uye kuenda kusiri kuchengetedzwa nekukurumidza.
Kutenga Bitcoin - isiri-yakachengetedzeka
Kubata bitcoin nenzira isiri-yekuchengeta (yega-yega) ndiyo mhedzisiro inodiwa. Inoita kuti kutengeserana kwako kusatarisike uye kunopa rusununguko rwakanyanya pamusoro pemari yako. Iwe unogona kuita izvi nekutenga bitcoin munzvimbo chaiyo yekutanga.
Mutengesi weBitcoin
Mutengesi ikambani inoita kuti iwe utenge isina- kuchengetedzeka bitcoin. Sezvo aya ari makambani akanyoreswa, anodzorwa zvizere uye iwe unofanirwa kuzivikanwa uye kuenda kuburikidza neAML/KYC maitiro. Bitcoin vatengesi vanotumira huwandu hwe bitcoin yawakatenga zvakananga kukero yako yeBitcoin (chikwama chako, kwaunobata mbeu).
Kungopa mienzaniso mishoma yemutengo Bitcoin:



[Coinnexus](https://coinnexus.ch/en) inoshanda isina kuongororwa kusvika CHF 1,000 pagore.
Shamwari ku Shamwari Kutenga Mumunhu
Iwe unogona kushanyira imwe yeakawanda Bitcoin kusangana-ups pasi rose, batanidza nevamwe Bitcoiners uye uvakumbire kuti vakutengese imwe bitcoin nemari. Munyika dzakawanda, vanhu vanosangana muTeregiramu kana Facebook mapoka kuti vawane vezera rekuchinjana ivo pachavo.
Peer-to-Peer Online Kutenga
Iyo inotungamira pasi rose P2P kuchinjanisa


Bitcoin ATMs
A Bitcoin ATM muchina wakafanana neATM, kwaunogona kutenga bitcoin uye mamwe cryptocurrencies nemari. Mukana weBitcoin ATMs ndewekuti iwe unowana yako bitcoin ipapo uye munzvimbo dzakawanda, kusvika kune imwe chikumbaridzo, pasina KYC/AML kuzivikanwa. Asi chenjera sezvo vazhinji vashandisi veATM vanochaja pamusoro peavhareji muripo.



Kadhi reBitcoin uye vhaucha
MuAustria semuenzaniso, zvinokwanisika kutenga 'Bitcoinbon' makadhi echipo pazviteshi zvepeturu pamwe nemumakiosks. Aya makadhi ezvipo anowanzo kuwanikwa munzvimbo dzekuratidzira panotengeswa makadhi echikwereti chenharembozha kana zvipo zveAmazon nezvimwewo. Unogona kutenga bitcoin makadhi echipo pasina kumisikidza chikwama uye pasina kunyoresa. Kana iwe uchida kushandura kukosha kwemakadhi kuita mari, iwe unogadzira chikwama uye udzikinure mari.







KYC uye AML inomiririra "Ziva Mutengi Wako" uye "Anti-Money Laundering" mitemo. Bhengi rega rega uye shanduko yakanyoreswa inofanirwa kutevedzera iyi mitemo yenyika nekurekodha ruzivo rwevatengi senge:
Zita
Kero
Nhamba dzefoni
Chitambi
Chitupa
Seufi akabata bepa rine zita rekuchinjana uye zuva
Kufona kwevhidhiyo nekuchinjana
Iye zvino, mumwe anogona kukakavara kuti tinoda kutsvaga matsotsi, magandanga, vatengesi vemari nezvimwewo uye naizvozvo mitemo iyi ine musoro. Dambudziko nderekuti mabhanga anowanzo gadzirisa zvakanyanya; vanoda data rakawanda kupfuura rinodiwa uye vanoteedzera kutengeserana kumwe chete uko, pamwe chete nemari yedhijitari, inoshanduka kuita muchina wekutarisa wakaipisisa kupfuura George Orwell akambofungidzira. Isu tichinongedza nekushoropodza mari yedhijitari yebhanga reChina uye chirongwa chavo chekukweretesa munharaunda, isu tiri kuvaka masisitimu akafanana anopinda zvakanyanya pakuvanzika kwevanhu.
KYC / AML haina kuchengetedza Deutsche Bank, HSBC nevamwe vakawanda vatambi vakuru kubva mukubira mari, asi inodzivirira mabhiriyoni evanhu vasina ID kuti vatore chikamu mumabasa ehupfumi. Zvinoda hukuru hukuru, mitengo yakakwira uye inoisa kuvanzika kwako panjodzi nekuda kwekudonha kwedata. Kuchinjana kunoziva kuti wakatenga marii, pawakaitenga, ruzivo rwako rwekubhengi nekero dzaunobvisa kwairi.
NeKYC/AML uye wakabata bitcoin yako pakuchinjana, iwe zvakare unotyora censorship kuramba kweBitcoin. Kutsinhana kwakawanda kunoshanda pamwe chete nemakambani ekutarisa blockchain, ayo anoshandira pamwe muzviitiko zvakawanda zvakananga nehurumende. Kuburikidza nekujeka kweBitcoin blockchain, chero kambani yekuongorora cheni inogona kutevera chiitiko chako. Iko kuchinjana kunogona kumisa account yako kana kuvharira kubvisa kwako.
Kunyange ndisingafungi kuti hurumende dzichakwanisa kurambidza kushandiswa kweBitcoin - zvinenge zvakafanana nekurambidza vanhu kufunga sezvo vachingorangarira mbeu yavo - vanogona kuedza kuitora, sezvakaitwa neUSA negoridhe. Kana chimwe chinhu chakadai chakaitika, uye iwe wakasiya mari yako pakutsinhana - saka zvakanaka sekuenda.
Executive order 6102, yakasainwa muna Kubvumbi 5 1933 neMutungamiriri weUnited States Franklin D. Roosevelt akarambidza kuchengetwa kwegoridhe. Muna 1975, maAmerica aikwanisa kuva negoridhe zvakare zviri pamutemo. Satoshi Nakamoto akaronga zuva ravo rekuzvarwa saApril 5, 1975. Ichokwadi kuti hazvina kuitika. Inoratidza zvinangwa zveSatoshi, kuti Bitcoin ndeyekusununguka kwemari.
Kuti uwane rumwe ruzivo nezvekuti hurongwa hwemari hwazvino hauna kunaka kumabhiriyoni evanhu pasirese, teerera [podcast kubvunzurudzwa naZachary Kelman,](https://anita.link/80) gweta rinonyanya zvematongerwo enyika, zvemutemo, uye. nyaya dzekutonga mukati nekutenderedza Bitcoin.
