[LocalCryptos](https://localcryptos.com/Bitcoin)
[Sovryn](https://live.sovryn.app)
Exchange sources: https://kycnot.me/, https://github.com/cointastical/P2P-Trading-Exchanges/, https://bitcoiner.guide/nokyconly/
Mari yekutenga Bitcoin
Paunotenga cryptocurrencies iwe unofanirwa kubhadhara mubhadharo weanopa sevhisi, sezvakangoita kana iwe uchichinjana kune imwe nyika mari kana iwe uchienda kune imwe nyika. Mutengo waunotsinhanisa nawo unotemwa nemupi webasa (ona chitsauko cheBitcoin mutengo). Kazhinji, uyu ndiwo mutengo wemusika pamwe nekuwedzera kwesevhisi. Sezvo imwe neimwe shanduko iine yayo bitcoin mutengo uye akasiyana mubhadharo zvimiro, pane misiyano mikuru mumitengo yekutengesa pakati pavo. Iwe unogona kuchengetedza mari nekuenzanisa mubhadharo wekutengesa paunosarudza chaiyo chikuva.
Pane mapoinzi matatu anosarudza mutengo wekutenga bitcoin, mupi wega wega webasa ane yake:
Bitcoin mutengo wemusika
Mari yekutengeserana yebasa ravo
Mari yekutengeserana, iyo inogona kuiswa mubhadharo yekutengeserana.

710-wallet-navigator

Kupindira pachikwama
Kune vakasiyana-siyana vanopa chikwama uye zvimwe zviri kuburitswa nekufamba kwenguva. Iwe unofanirwa kusarudza kana iwe uchida imwe ndeyeBitcoin chete kana imwe yemari yakawanda. Chikwama chega chega chinopa maitiro akasiyana, mazinga ekuchengetedza uye mazinga ekutsigira emaseti akasiyana emari. Iyi mibvunzo inotevera ichakubatsira iwe kusarudza rudzi rwekutanga rwechikwama ruchakodzera zvaunoda. Iwe uchazoda kutsvaga kuti ndeupi mugadziri anotsigira mari yepi.
Nhanho 1 - Sarudza Wallet
**Ungada here kukwanisa kubhadhara nechikwama nguva nenguva?** Kana iwe usingashandisi mbozhanhare kana komputa uye usingade kutumira mubhadharo, unogona kushandisa chikwama chekadhi. Unogona kutumira bitcoin kana ether kwairi uye wovachengeta. Paunenge uchinge wangoda kuibhadhara, iwe unozofanirwa kuisa chikwama. Kana iwe uchida kuita mubhadharo wenguva dzose, saka chikwama chesofutiweya, pamwe chakabatana nesimbisiro yehardware seTrezor kana BitBox02 inonyanya kukodzera.
**Unoda here kuchengetedza sofutiweya nemudziyo zviri maererano nemazuva?** Aihwa? Zvadaro, zvakare, iyo chikwama chekadhi ndiyo sarudzo chaiyo kwauri. Haufanirwe kunetseka nezve kuchengetedza mudziyo.
**Mari yauri kuronga kuva nayo pachikwama ichave....** * Zvakafanana nechikwama chenguva dzose muhomwe yako *: kazhinji chikwama chenhare chinokwana. Haibhadharwi uye inokwana mari shoma.
* Zvakafanana neakaundi yako yekubhangi *: shandisa chikwama chehadhiweya. Chikwama chehadhiweya inotsvakwa zvakanyanya muBitcoin nzombe inomhanya uye inowanzotengeswa kunze (chengeta izvi mupfungwa muhurongwa hwako).
Pane [mubatsiri akawedzerwa pawebhusaiti yeBitcoin.org](https://bitcoin.org/en/choose-your-wallet), yaunogona kushandisawo. Inokutungamira kuburikidza nesarudzo yakavakirwa pane yekushandisa sisitimu (nhare, desktop, hardware wallet) yaunosarudza.
Nhanho 2 - Gadzira Kudzoreredza Makiyi ako
Nyora pasi mhodzi yemnemonic - 12 kusvika 24 mazwi eChirungu, zita, mhando uye software shanduro yechikwama chako uye uzvichengete munzvimbo yakachengetedzeka (chitsauko 5.3).
Nhanho 3 - Tenga Bitcoin
Zvizhinji zvikwama anosanganisira kugona kutenga bitcoin zvakananga mukati meiyo interface. Vagadziri vezvikwam vari kushanda pamwe nekutsinhana, izvo zvinovabhadhara komisheni. Kana ndichida kushandisa shanduko ndinosarudza kusarudza imwe isati yatanga uye yekunze kubva pachikwama. Nenzira iyo ndinogara ndakazvimiririra yerudzi rwechikwama, ndinogona kushandisa iyi imwe kuchinjana kutumira bitcoin kune zvese zvikwama zvangu zvakasiyana, uye ndinongofanira kusiya data rangu reKYC mune imwe shanduko, kuderedza njodzi yekutyorwa kwedata. Kushandisa nzira dzisiri dzekuchengetedza, dzisiri dzeKYC (chitsauko 7.3) zvakatonyanya nani.
[How to get bitcoin](resources/_Buying-methods.png) [^72]
[^72]: Anita Posch

720-strategy

Zvekuita
Nzira yekudzivisa Kusagadzikana
Pane nzira yakanaka kwazvo yekudzivirira bitcoin volatility kana uchiishandisa sekubhadhara. Paunoshandisa bitcoin pane chimwe chinhu, unozadza chikwama chako nekukasira nekutenga iyo bitcoin nemari yefiat mushure mekutengesa. Nenzira iyo, iwe haurasikirwe chero mari nekuti mutengo we bitcoin unoramba wakangofanana munguva pfupi yakadaro yenguva.
Gadzira Chirongwa Chekuchengetedza
Tenga mari shoma ye bitcoin nguva nenguva - zuva rega rega / vhiki / mwedzi. Izvi zvinonziwo dhora mutengo avhareji (DCA) - kana fiat mutengo avhareji (FCA). Nekupatsanura kunze kwekutenga kwako unodzikamisa kushata kwemutengo weBitcoin kwenguva yakareba.
Pamawebhusaiti akaita se[Bitcoin Dollar Mutengo Wepakati](https://www.bitcoindollarcostaverage.com/) unogona kuverenga misiyano mukudzoka kwemaitiro akati wandei ekutenga.
**Bitcoin-chete FCA masevhisi**
Austria, Germany: [Coinfinity](https://coinfinity.co/sparplan/?ref=6716) France: [StackinSat](https://www.stackinsat.com/) Europe: [Relai](https://relai.ch/) UK: [Coinfloor](https://coinfloor.co.uk/hodl/), [xsats](https://xsats.com/) Australia: [Bitaroo](https://support.bitaroo.com.au/hc/en-au/articles/360042838874-Recurring-Buy-DCA-), [Amber App](https://amber.app/) Canada: [Bull Bitcoin](https://bullbitcoin.com/) Nigeria: [Bitnob](https://bitnob.com/) USA: [Swan Bitcoin](https://www.swanbitcoin.com/), [River](https://river.com/)
Kuchinjana
Kune vasingaverengeki vekutengesa nyanzvi pamhepo vanoudza vanotanga kuti "nguva yemusika" uye kufanotaura mafambiro emutengo we bitcoin. Vanoedza kukutengesa iwe yekutengesa software nemasemina. Mira. Usapedze nguva yako nemari pakuedza kuita izvozvo. Iwe haugone kuronga nguva yemusika. Vatambi vakuru vanokuwana iwe "rekt." Pamusoro peizvozvo, iwe unobhadhara mari yakawanda yekutengesa uye ramba uchifunga kuti iwe unogona kuteedzera mafambiro ese ekutengesa nekuda kwezvikonzero zvemutero. Mune dzimwe nyika mari yako yebitcoin haina mutero kana ukasachinjanisa mari yacho kwemwedzi gumi nemiviri. Kutengeserana kwega kwega kunogona kuve chiitiko chitsva chemutero.
Altcoins
Altcoins ndiyo chidimbu cheimwe mari. Aya ese ese ma zvichengetedzo zve crypto akagadzirwa mushure meBitcoin. Vazhinji vanotanga vanotevera zano re "kusiyanisa portfolio yavo" uye votanga kutengesa bitcoin yavo neAltcoins. Zviuru zvemaAltcoins zvakanyorwa pa[Coinmarketcap](https://coinmarketcap.com/). Iwe haugone kuferefeta ese uye mazhinji haasisiri kuvandudzwa uye haana maturo. Bitcoin ndiyo yekutanga-mufambisi uye izvo zvichengetedzo zvine yakakura network maitiro. Maonero angu ndeekuti, kana iwe uchida kusiyanisa, ita neruzivo rwako. Enda zvakadzika mukati meBitcoin rabbit gomba, dzidza kuzvichengeta, dzidza nzira yekumisikidza node, dzidza nezvezvitsva zvakaita seDeFi paBitcoin kana dzidza maitiro ekuwana bitcoin.
Dai Ndakangoita...Ndakanonoka
Dai wakangotenga Bitcoin muna 2011, ungadai wakapfuma zvakanyanya parizvino. Icho ichokwadi uye ndaizokorokotedza pasina godo, nekuti iwe waive mumwe wevashoma vanhu vaitenda muBitcoin uye wanga wakagadzirira kuisa mari yako yakawana zvakaoma mukuedza kune njodzi. Hapana wevatangi vekutanga aiziva kuti Bitcoin yaizosimuka sezvayakaita. Zvakanga zvakaoma kuchengetedza makiyi ako kumashure uye akawanda bitcoin akarasika kana kubiwa. Dai waipedza uye wakachengetedza mari yako, ungadai wakaitengesa yese muna 2014, pamwe 2017? Hazvina maturo kufungisisa nezve "ko kana". Tichiri mumazuva ekutanga. Kana iwe uri kutanga kuzvidzidzisa uye kushandisa Bitcoin izvozvi, uchiri maligi pamberi peruzhinji. Hazvina kumbononoka kudzidza nezve Bitcoin.
![Heuno munhu ari kufunga kunonoka muna 2013](zvishandiso/_too-late.png) [^73]
Mitero
Ini handisi chipangamazano wemitero asi zvandinogona kutaura ndezvekuti, dzidza nezvemitemo uye zvinodiwa mutero munzvimbo yako. Iyo Bitcoin blockchain iri pachena uye yakawanda uye yakawanda zviremera zvemitero zvinoda kuchinjanisa kuti vavape data ravo rekutengesa. Chengetedza humbowo hwekutenga kwako kuitira kuti zviremera zvitange kuferefeta.
[^73]: [Source BitcoinTalk](https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=170725.0)

800-Using-Bitcoin

Kushandisa bitcoin
Transaction Fees
Mari yemugodhi inofanirwa kubhadharwa kune yega bitcoin transaction uye mari iyi inodiwa kuti kushanda kweBitcoin network kuenderere mberi. Basa revashandi vemigodhi rinopihwa mibairo iyi uye ichangoburwa bitcoin (ona chitsauko 2.3). Kuchera chinhu chakakosha muBitcoin protocol. Mushure mekunge bhuroka rekutengeserana rakacherwa, rinosungirirwa kune blockchain. Iyi ndiyo nzira yekuvimbisa kuchengetedzwa kwetiweki. Sezvo Bitcoin ine yakatarwa muganhu wemari mamiriyoni 21 emari, vashandi vemumigodhi havaizogamuchira chero mubairo wekuita kwavo mushure mekunge vasvika pahuwandu hwehuwandu huno, uye havachafariri kugadzirisa kutengeserana uye nokudaro kuchengetedza blockchain. Naizvozvo, Satoshi Nakamoto akaunza mari yekutengeserana. Sekureva kwebepa jena, chinangwa ndechekuita kuti mari idzi dzive dzakaderera pane inofananidzwa mubhadharo uye mutengo weiyo yechinyakare banking system. Nekudaro, haisi iyo nyaya yekuti kutamiswa hakuna muripo nekuti, muchirevo, hapana chikonzero chevamiriri kana mabhangi.
Paunenge uchitenga bitcoin kuburikidza nekuchinjana, mari yekutengeserana (mubhadharo wemigodhi) kazhinji haigadzirike uye inogadziriswa nemupi.
Muchikwama chako cheBitcoin chisiri chekuchengetedza, unogona kusarudza mari yekutengeserana yekubhadhara kunobuda wega. Iyo yakakwirira iwe yauisa mubhadharo, kukurumidza kutengeserana kwako kuchagadziriswa nevanochera migodhi nekuti vanotora kutengeserana nemari yepamusoro pekutanga. Kana kutamisa kwako kusingatarisi nguva, unogona kusarudza muripo wakaderera.
Kuti uwedzere kudzora unogona kufungidzira muripo uye kumhanya kwekusimbisa pamapeji akaita se[Mempool.space](https://mempool.space/) kana [Johoe's Bitcoin Mempool](https://jochen-hoenicke.de/queue/) . Aya mawebhusaiti anoratidza huwandu uye saizi yezvese zvisina kusimbiswa kutengeserana. Ivo vanopa chaiyo-nguva yekuona uye vanoratidza kuti iyo Mempool inoshanduka sei. Iko kutengeserana kunopendwa nehuwandu hwemari yavanobhadhara pa (virtual) byte.
![Chaiyo-nguva maonero ezvisina kusimbiswa](zviwanikwa/_Mempool-space-white-back.png) [^74]
Pazasi iwe unogona kuona marongero muEdge wallet. Iwe unogona kusarudza imwe yemhando dzeiyo default muripo wekutengesa kana kukosha kwetsika.
![Magadziriso emuripo wekutenga muEdge wallet](zvishandiso/_transaction-fee-setting.png) [^75]
**Pending Transaction** Sezvo zvidhinha zvitsva zvichicherwa maminetsi ega ega e10, zvinotora avhareji yemaminetsi angangoita gumi kusvika kutengeserana kwako kwasimbiswa. Kana ukaseta mari yekutengeserana yakaderera saka kutengeserana kwako kunogona kunge kwakamirira kwenguva yakareba sezvo Mempool inocheneswa uye vacheri vemigodhi vanotanga zvakare kubatanidza matranseksheni ane mari shoma. Pano iwe unoona imwe yekutengeserana kwangu yave yakavharirwa muMempool kwemwedzi. ![Pending transaction](zvishandiso/_Pending-transaction-edge.png) [^76] Unogona kutarisa mamiriro ekutengeserana kwako mu [Blockchain muongorori](https://blockchair.com). Sezvauri kuona pazasi transaction yangu ndeye 4,717 nhanho kubva pakucherwa neiyo yakazara ye41,610 kutengeserana muMempool. Ndakasarudza muripo we5 sat per vbyte. ![Mamiriro ekutengeserana sezvinoratidzwa mublockexplorer](zviwanikwa/_Pending-transaction-explorer.png) [^77]
Haufanire kutevedzera ari pazasi matanho kuti kutengeserana kwako kwepakutanga kusimbiswe. Zvizhinji zvekutengesa-mubhadharo wakaderera zvinoramba zviripo kwemazuva uye zvinozopedzisira zvasimbisa. Nekudaro, kune nzira mbiri dzekugadzirisa dambudziko reiyo yakanamatira kutengeserana uye kuita kuti isimbiswe nekukurumidza.
**Kutumirwa Kwekutengeserana Kwakamira **
Kutsiva-ne-mubhadharo (RBF): mamwe wallet anobvumidza iwe kuseta iyi sarudzo kuti hongu usati watumira kutengeserana. Muchiitiko ichi, kana kutengeserana kwepakutanga kukamira, unogona kuseta mari yepamusoro uye wotumirazve kutengeserana.
**Chiitiko Chinouya Chakamira **
Mwana anobhadharira mubereki (CPFP): unogona kufunga nezvazvo semubereki asina mari yakakwana yekushandisa, saka mwana wavo anobhadhara mutsauko panzvimbo yemubereki. CPFP inzira yaunokwanisa kubhuya nayo zvishoma nezvishoma kutengeserana kuri kuuya nekuita kutengeserana kutsva nemari yakakwira (yemwana) uchishandisa zvakabuda (mari) kubva mukutengeserana kwekare (transaction yemubereki) yaramba.
Ndokumbira utarise zvinyorwa zvewallet yauri kushandisa kuti uwane mirairo yakazara.
Tenga Chimwe Chinhu NeBitcoin
Heano mamwe madhairekitori ane zvitoro kwaunogona kushandisa bitcoin.
[Accepted here](https://www.acceptedhere.io)
[B2B services accepting BTC](https://cryptwerk.com/companies/b2b/btc/)
[Coinmap](https://coinmap.org/view/) masitoro anotora Bitcoin
[Spending Bitcoin](https://spending-bitcoin.com/) directory
[UseBitcoins](https://usebitcoins.info/) directory
Makadzi eBitcoin
Unogona kushandisa Bitcoin debit kadhi kutenga chinhu sezvakangoita chero imwe yebhangi debit kadhi. Musiyano ndewekuti inotakurwa ne bitcoin kana altcoins. Vatengesi vanobhadharwa nemari yavo nekambani yekubhengi uye mutero unozobviswa kubva pamari yako bitcoin, izvo zvinokutendera kuti urarame chete kuburikidza ne bitcoin.
Iwe unozofanirwa kuisa bitcoin yako kukambani yekadhi rechikwereti, zvinoreva kuti iwe unopa kutonga pamusoro pemari yako kune wechitatu bato. Deposit chete sezvaunoda pakadhi uye tarisa muripo unochajwa nemakambani aya emakadhi.
Rondedzero pfupi yemakadhi aripo panguva ino: Cryptocom Visa, Binance, Bitpanda Visa, Coinbase Visa, Wirex Visa, BlockCard, Cryptopay, Nexo, Bitwala Visa, BitPay Visa, Cash App
Kushandisa uye Kugamuchira
Izvi zvinotevera zvishandiso uye masevhisi anogonesa iwe kushandisa uye kugamuchira BTC muhupenyu hwako hwezuva nezuva.
[Bity](https://bity.com/products/crypto-online-bill-pay/) bhadhara mabhiri pamhepo ne bitcoin
[Cash App](https://cash.app/bitcoin) tenga uye tengesa BTC kubva kuCash App yako yasara
[Ramwai](https://global.strike.me/) tumira uye ugamuchire ipapo mari dzepasi rese, mari dzekunze nekukasika uye nekuwana kuzere kuBitcoin network.
[Piixpay](https://www.piixpay.com/?lang=en) bhadhara chero munhu muEURO uchishandisa crypto yako
[Piixpay](https://www.piixpay.com/?lang=en) bhadhara chero munhu muEURO uchishandisa crypto yako
