810-earn-bitcoin

Tora Bitcoin
Kuwana Bitcoin ndiyo nzira yakanakisa yekuiwana: yakaganhurirwa kana isina kunyoreswa, yakaganhurirwa kana isina KYC cheki yekuzivikanwa uye hapana mubhadharo wekutengesa. Mamwe eaya masevhisi anongowanikwa muUS kana mamwe matunhu epasi. Sezvo nzvimbo yeBitcoin iri mukukura nekukurumidza, chitsauko ichi chinogona kungove chitarisiko chezvichauya.
Mabhodhi emabasa eBitcoin
Tsvaga basa kana mutengi kuti uwane Bitcoin yebasa rako.
[BitGigs](https://bitgigs.com/)
[Coinality](https://coinality.com/)
[CanWork](https://www.canwork.io/)
[Freelance For Coins](https://freelanceforcoins.com/projects)
[Kushandira Bitcoin](https://workingforbitcoins.com/)
Mabasa emumhepo
Wana satoshis kuburikidza nekupedzisa mabasa madiki.
[Stakwork](https://stakwork.com)
[Microlancer](https://microlancer.io/)
[Sats 4 Likes](https://kriptode.com/satsforlikes/index.html
Chinja zviwanikwa zvako
[Bitwage](https://www.bitwage.com/) semushandi kana freelancer, unokwanisa kuwana mubairo wako mu bitcoin pane fiat. Vashandirwi vanogona kushandisa sevhisi iyi kubhadhara timu yavo mu bitcoin futi. [Bvunzurudzo nemuvambi Jonathan Chester](https://anita.link/106).
Kugamuchira Mipiro kana Kubhadhara
Sesangano risingabatsiri, blogger kana podcaster, unogona kugamuchira matipi mu bitcoin/satoshis nemasevhisi aya:
[Tippin.me](https://tippin.me/) inoita kuti ugamuchire matipi emheni bitcoin pane webhusaiti yako uye Twitter pasina muripo.
[Tallyco.in](https://tallyco.in/) ipuratifomu inopa vanhu mari yakawanda yakavakwa pamusoro peBitcoin blockchain. Unogona kugamuchira mubhadharo muBTC uye micro-kubhadhara kuburikidza nemheni pazero muripo
[Zvipo zveMheni](https://lightning.gifts/) gadzira mavhocha echipo e-bitcoin kuti ugovane neshamwari nemhuri, uye nevateereri vako.
Vagadziri vezvekuverenga uye Podcasting 2.0
Nekuuya kwemheni Netiweki, nzira itsva yechokwadi yekutumira kukosha uye kubhadhara kune zvirimo painternet yakagadzirwa. Kutepfenyura mari, izwi rakagadzirwa naAndreas M. Antonopoulos, rinogonesa vaimbi, vagadziri vemavhidhiyo uye mapodcasters kuti vawane mari munguva chaiyo, pasina vamiriri. Iwe unongoda chikwama chine podcasts akabatanidzwa, zvishoma bitcoin uye unogona kutanga kuteerera uchibhadhara neminiti. Chinangwa chePodcasting 2.0 uye yekutepfenyura mari ndeyekusunungura vanogadzira zvemukati uye vateereri kubva kushambadziro, kuongoroorwa uye kuongorora. Kubhadhara ndekwekuzvidira, pasina mari yekunyoresa uye hapana prepayment. Ziva kuti panguva yekunyora aya ese masevhisi ari mukuvandudza nguva dzose. Zvimwe nezve [kumashure kwepodcasting 2.0 mubvunzurudzo](https://anita.link/pod2) neni.
![](resources/_breez-podcast.png) ![](resources/_breez-podcast-boost.png) [^78]
[Breez](https://breez.technology/) Chikwama chemheni chisiri chekuchengetedza kuti uteerere mapodcasts
[PodFriend](https://web.podfriend.com/) Panorira mapodcats
[Podstation](https://podstation.github.io/) bhurawuza rema podcats
[Sphinx Chat](https://sphinx.chat/) Nzvimbo dzine machatsi nemapodcasting evatereri nemapodcasters vane manodzi avo.
[Satoshis.stream](https://satoshis.stream/) nzira dziri nyore dzema podcasters asina manodzi avo vega.
[LN Cast](https://lncast.com/) Mapodcast enetiweki yelightning, bhadhara masatoshi mashoma uye nekupa kuti uterere podcast raunofarira.
[LN Pay](https://lnpay.co/) Gadzirisa kuti zvinhu zvako zvibhadharwe, zvichibhadharika ne lightning
[WordPress Lightning Paywall](https://lightning-paywall.coincharge.io/)
[Scarce.City](https://scarce.city/) Panotengeswa zvinhu zveBitcoin - [Interview with founder Chris Tramount](https://anita.link/91)
[Sparkshot](https://sparkshot.io/) Maatisiti vanokwanisa kutengesa zvinhu zvavo for Bitcoin.
Komesi
[Breez](https://breez.technology/#business) iri nyore kushandisa Point-of-Sale app kune vatengesi, maresitorendi, maresitorendi... kutanga kubvuma kubhadhara bitcoin.
[BTC Pay Server](https://btcpayserver.org/) inozvimiririra yega, yakavhurika-sosi yekubhadhara cryptocurrency processor ye e-commerce. Yakachengeteka, yakavanzika, inodzivirira censorship uye yemahara. Unogona kuibatanidza nechitoro chako chepamhepo, gadzira ma invoice e accounting yako uye uwane bitcoin kuburikidza nemheni. Nekubatanidzwa kweWooCommerce, Shopify, Drupal, Magento, PrestaShop, Shopware.
[Confirmo](https://confirmo.net/) bvuma kubhadhara nemaplugins ezvitoro zvine mukurumbira zvepamhepo.
[Globe](https://globee.com/) gamuchira bitcoin neGloBee, vanopa ma-plugins akavhurika kune ese makuru e-commerce mapuratifomu ekomisheni (yekuchengetedza).
[OpenNode](https://www.opennode.com/) bitcoin kubhadhara uye kubhadharwa kwemabhizinesi, e-commerce plugins, mapeji ekubhadhara anogarwa (kuchengetedza).
Cashback uye Faucets
[Peta](https://foldapp.com/) wana bitcoin pakutenga kwese neVISA kadhi rako
[Lolli](https://www.lolli.com/) wana bitcoin kana uchitenga muzvitoro zvinopfuura chiuru
[Pei](https://getpei.com/) link ingangoita chero debit kana kadhi rechikwereti
[Satsback](https://satsback.com/en) tambira kubva kuzvitoro zvepamhepo
[LN Pay](https://lnpay.co/faucets/) gadzira yako yega pombi yemheni uye dzorera vateereri vako mu bitcoin.
[Chikwama](https://purse.io) shandisa bitcoin kutenga paAmazon uye uwane mutero
[Satsy](https://satsy.com/) wana mari paunenge uchitenga pamhepo, tora ongororo uye tamba mitambo

[Thndr Games](https://thndr.games/games) kuhwina bitcoin mibairo uchitamba
[Zebhedhi](https://zebedee.io/) neZEBEDEE Wallet unogona kutamba mitambo nebitcoin, kutumira mubhadharo mukati memeseji mameseji, kuunganidza zvipo parukova rwako rwunorarama nezvimwe zvakawanda.
[Bitcoin Bounty Hunt](https://bitcoinbountyhunt.com/) mutambo wekupfura, kwaunogona kuwana satoshis
[Mitambo yeSatoshis](https://satoshis.games/) mapuratifomu emitambo uye musika weNFT wevatambi
Wana kuburikidza neKuisa mari
[SunExchange](https://thesunexchange.com/) gadzirisa kabhoni tsoka yako, tenga maseru ezuva uye uwane bitcoin - [Kubvunzurudza nemuvambi Abe Cambridge](https://anita.link/104)
[Blockstream Mining Note, STOKR](https://blockstream.com/finance/bmn/) kutora chikamu mukucherwa kweBitcoin kuburikidza nekutenga chiratidzo chekuchengetedza STOKR
Kuchera
Ziva, kune akawanda matsotsi ekuchera kunze uko. Kunyange ini ndakadonha kwemamwe makore apfuura. Ndosaka ndisina kuzobata mukana iwoyo zvakare. Iye zvino mamwe mabhizinesi ari pamutemo ari kutanga munzvimbo iyoyo.
[Compass](https://compassmining.io/) Sevhisi inobatsira kutenga, kuisa uye kubata zvicherwa zvemigodhi.
[Blockstream Mining](https://blockstream.com/mining/) tambira zvicherwa zvako neBlockstream's bhizinesi-kirasi migodhi zvivakwa uye manejimendi.
Kukweretesa & Kukwereta
[DeFi Rate](https://defirate.com/) Mhedziso yemitengo yekukweretesa uye yekukwereta
