820-The-future

Ramangwana Rave Iko Zvino
"Ramangwana inzvimbo yekuvaka." - Anita Posch
Iye zvino zvawava nekunzwisisa kwakadzama kweBitcoin uye mashandisiro ayo, tinogona kunyudza zvigunwe zvedu muzviitiko zveramangwana zvandinofunga kuti zvichave nemhedzisiro yakakura. Ichi chikamu chakanyorwa pamwe chete naMark Kersley nezvikamu zvakatorwa kubva: [Andreas M. Antonopoulos 'hurukuro pamusoro peBitcoin, Layer 2 Solutions, uye Wild West yeCrypto](https://youtu.be/TsbIMg-YHQk)
Decentralized Finance - DeFi
Chimwe chikamu chinonakidza chezvishandiso zvitsva chinonzi decentralized finance, kana DeFi. Decentralized zvemari ine chinangwa chekuwedzera pamusoro pekusununguka kwemari kunopihwa uye nekufemerwa neBitcoin, uye kusuma aya maficha kune yese nharaunda yecrypto. Zvose zvakanaka uye zvakanaka kuva ne bitcoin kana zvimwe zvinhu zvakasarudzwa, asi kana vanhu vazhinji vachienda kunotenga, kutengesa kana kunyange kubata zvinhu zvavo kwenguva refu, vanoshandisa sangano repakati rakadai sekuchinjana.
Nekushandisa masangano epakati vanhu ava vari kuzviisa pangozi dzakaita seKYC, maturakiti akachengeterwa, hacks uye mukati manipulation. DeFi inopa imwe nzira isingavimbike kuburikidza nekushandisa programmable smart zvibvumirano. Crypto-assets ndeye mumhepo uye, saizvozvowo, inorongwa. DeFi mapuratifomu anoshandisa pre-yakarongwa zvibvumirano kuita mabasa aimbove achingowanikwa chete kuburikidza nepakati masangano akadai swaps, margin kutengesa, kukweretesa, staking nezvimwe. Nekubvisa iyo yepakati 'yepakati' uye pachinzvimbo kushandisa zvibvumirano zvinoonekwa pachena, DeFi inopa yakaringana zvemari layer kune crypto ecosystem. Mikana yeDeFi ichiri kuwanikwa uye kuvakwa. Rimwe zuva, hurongwa hwese hwemari hwepasi rose hunogona kuderedzwa.
Zvizhinji zveDeFi zvinoshandiswa zvinogadzirwa uye zvinomhanya paEthereum (ETH) network - yechipiri yakakura crypto-asset nemusika cap panguva yekunyora. Ethereum ine hushamwari hwakanyanya uye inotarisa mukuvandudza kondirakiti kuburikidza nemitauro yakaita seSolidity. Naizvozvo, yanga iri iyo yakakwana incubation pasi yeDeFi mapuratifomu mumakore achangopfuura. Makesi ekushandisa akakurumbira eDeFi paEthereum ndiwo madhizaini ekutsinhana (DEXs), mapuratifomu ekukweretesa uye mapegged akatsiga-makoini seUSDT.
DeFi mapuratifomu anogona kushandisa tokeni kubva kune mamwe maketani kuburikidza nemaitiro anonzi kuputira. Izvi zvinosanganisira kutumira asset kubva kune imwe blockchain kune smart contract peg. Ngatishandisei 1 bitcoin semuenzaniso. Iyi mbambo ichabata (kukiya) iyo bitcoin yakatumirwa kwairi uye gadzira iyo yakaenzana vhezheni yeiyo bitcoin paEthereum network. Mienzaniso yeizvi yakaputirwa bitcoin (WBTC) uye Ren bitcoin (renBTC). Aya mapegged tokens anogona kushandiswa paDeFi application panzvimbo yeasethi yepakutanga uye nekuti smart contract inobata yepakutanga asset, hapagone kuve nenyaya ye 'double-pend'. Kana mushandisi achida kubvisa zvinhu zvake kucheni yake yekuzvarwa, kondirakiti yakangwara ichapisa chiratidzo chayakagadzirwa uye kutumira mushandisi midziyo yavo yepakutanga pacheni yemuno. Izvi zvinoita kuti DeFi ishande kune chero chiratidzo chedhijitari.
Kubudirira kweBitcoin kunononoka uye kune nzira inochengetedza kupfuura mamwe akawanda blockchains seEthereum. Izvi nechikonzero chakanaka: kuchengeteka. Asi vanogadzira munzvimbo yeBitcoin vanga vasina kurara, kunze kweMheni Network yakawanda yeBitcoin-yekuzvarwa mapuratifomu uye maapplication akagadzirwa.
Mitemo nepakatanga nezveBitcoin
Rootstock
Rootstock (RSK) itiweki inotarisa kuunza smart contract kugona kuBitcoin. Inocherwa neBitcoin, zvichireva kuti pakati pe40 ne75% yeBitcoin miners vanonyatso gadzirisa kutengeserana kweRSK network. Izvi zvinoreva kuti RSK inochengetedzwa neakawanda hashi simba kune chero imwe blockchain munyika, kunze kweBitcoin hongu. Zvakafanana neEthereum mhinduro, RSK inoshandisa nzira yekuputira kusuma bitcoin kune network. Nekudaro, sezvo iyo network pachayo yakasanganiswa-yakacherwa neBitcoin miners inogona kunzi ndiyo yakachengeteka uye isingavimbike network yekuvaka DeFi pane parizvino. Iyo inonyanya kukwezva kuBitcoiners uye avo vanoshuvira DeFi mhinduro dzeBitcoin, asi vasingade kurasikirwa nedecentralization, kusavimbika uye kuchengetedzeka kunopihwa neBitcoin network.
Rootstock yave mukuvandudzwa kubva 2014 uye yakatanga mainnet yayo muna 2018. RSK network ine fast block nguva, kugadzirisa imwe neimwe block mu 15-30 masekonzi. Zvikumbiro zvinogona kuvakwa pamusoro peRSK uchishandisa hunyanzvi hwakafanana seEthereum senge nemutauro wekusimudzira weSolidity. Mari yegesi yeRSK yakanyanya kuderera pane yeEthereum; panguva yekunyora, kutengeserana kweEthereum kunodhura avhareji yemadhora makumi matanhatu nepo RSK kutengeserana kunodhura avhareji yemadhora 0.50. Nekuda kwekumhanya kwayo uye kugona kugadzirisa, marollups anogona kuunzwa kune maapurikesheni akavakirwa paRootstock kuti awedzere kudzikisira kukurumidza kwekutengesa uye mutengo, ungangove wakadzikira pasi pemadhora 0.01 pakutengeserana.
Sovryn
Sovryn muenzaniso weimwe chikuva chakadaro chiri kuvakwa paRootstock network. Sovryn iri kugadzira DeFi nzvimbo ye bitcoin pamwe chete nezvimwe zvinhu zvakawanda kuburikidza nemabhiriji kune mamwe maketani anosanganisira Ethereum uye Binance Smart Chain (BSC). Iyo isiri-yekuchengetedza uye isina mvumo chibvumirano-yakavakirwa sisitimu inonyanya kushandiswa kukweretesa bitcoin, kukwereta uye kutengesa margin. Iko hakuna KYC yeSovryn uye haimboda kuti uchengete mari yako, *kwete makiyi ako, kwete mari yako! fungible token (NFT) kushanda. Inoshandisa fastBTC relay kukurumidza kushandura bitcoin kuRootstock smart bitcoin (rBTC) kuti ishandiswe paSovryn. Zvichaitika mune ramangwana zvichaunza zvinhu zvakawanda kubva kumaketani akawanda kuenda kuSovryn, pamwe nenzvimbo yemusika yeNFT, token launchpad, perpetual swaps uye overcollateralized bitcoin-backed stable-coins. Chiratidzo cheSovryn hachifaniri kunge chiri chimwe chikuva cheDeFi, asi hurongwa hwemari hwekushanda kwenyika.
Sovryn haisi kambani kana nzvimbo iripakati pevanhu nehurumende. Iyo ine vazhinji vanopa vane chinangwa chekugadzira iyo isingavimbike mari musara iyo yaifanira kunge yakagadzirwa pamusoro peBitcoin kare kare. Sovryn anovimbisa hutongi hwakasarudzika hwekutedzera nzira kuburikidza nemhando yesisitimu yekuzvitonga inonzi Bitocracy, shanduro yakagadziridzwa yevetocracy. Izvi zvinosanganisira kuiswa kwematokeni eSOV mukudzorera simba rekuvhota uye mibairo yemubhadharo. Sarudzo dzese dzezvinoda kuita dzinofanirwa kupasa kuvhota muBitocracy kuti iitwe. Iyo nzira iyi yesiteking inovimbisa kuti vavhoti vanokurudzirwa kuti vape mavhoti akadzidza vachitsigira zvikumbiro zvingabatsira Sovryn nharaunda uye zvinopesana nezvikumbiro zvinokuvadza. Panguva yekunyora, Sovryn ichangotanga kutengeserana kwayo uye iri kutarisa kuburitsa mabhiriji akawanda uye zvitsva. Zvichave zvinonakidza kuona purojekiti ichikura.
Ndakabvunzurudza muvambi Edan Yago, kwaanoongorora akawanda emisoro iyi - teerera pa anita.link/105
Thorchain
Zvakafanana naSovryn, Thorchain yakavambwa pakuziva kuti nzira dzepakati dzekutamisa muridzi we zvinhu zvecrpto zvakakanganisika. Akazvarwa muna 2018, Thorchain yakagadzirwa kuti ishande sechinotsiva kune yepakati (CEX), uye panzvimbo pacho inofambisa muchinjika-cheni decentralized crypto exchange (DEX). Thorchain inobatanidza pakati pemaketani akasiyana kuburikidza neayo emuchinjiko bhiriji, iro rine zita rekuti Bifröst Protocol. Iyo Bifröst inobvumira echinyakare token swaps pamaketani akasiyana, zvichireva kuti hapana chikonzero chekugadzira kana kuputirwa shanduro dzematokeni. Zvine hutsinye, Thorchain haina-kuchengeta uye iri 100% yakaderedzwa.
Thorchain inoshanda zvakanyanya zvakafanana nemamwe maDEX akadai saSovryn; inoshandisa otomatiki yekugadzira musika modhi (AMM) kugadzirisa uye kuchengetedza shanduko. Nekudaro, Thorchain haimhanyi pane imwe blockchain, saSovryn inomhanya paRSK semuenzaniso. Thorchain iri panzvimbo yayo yakazvimirira blockchain iyo yakavakwa uchishandisa iyo Cosmos SDK. Izvi zvakabvumira Thorchain kumanikidzira yayo RUNE tokeni sechigadziko chekuchinjana zviwanikwa, zvichireva kuti imwe neimwe shanduko pair iRUNE-x pair. Naizvozvo vashandisi vanokwanisa kuchinjanisa, semuenzaniso, BTC yeETH kuburikidza neRUNE tokeni yepakati basa. Izvi zvaizoita sekuchinjana kweBTC kuenda kuRUNE, wozochinjana neRUNE kuenda kuETH. Izvi zvakabvumira iyo RUNE chiratidzo chekushandisa kuraira kukosha: RUNE inogona kushandiswa kupa liquidity kumadziva eAMM mukudzoka kwechikamu chemubhadharo uye inogona kutengeswa nekufungidzirwa kuburikidza nemusika wakavhurika.
Babelfish Mari
Mukati me crypto, kune akawanda pegged tokens ayo anonzi zvakanyanya se ' makoini akagadzikana'. Aya ane mukurumbira zvikuru uye anowanzo shandiswa kuchengeta, kutamisa uye kushandisa hupfumi nekushomeka kwenguva pfupi kushanduka. Kune akawanda makoini akagadzikana akarovererwa kuUS Dollar akadai seTether (USDT), US Dollar Coin (USDC), Binance USD (BUSD) neDAI, ese akagadzirirwa kuchengetedza kukosha kwe1.00 pachiratidzo. Nepo  makoini akagadzikana aya achigadzira chinhu chinobatsira checrypto nharaunda, kuve nema  makoini akagadzikana akasiyana pamanetiweki akasiyana kwakonzera zvipingamupinyi kumvura yemvura pamapuratifomu.
Yakatumidzwa zita remudziyo weshanduro muDouglas Adams' 'The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy', Babelfish ine chinangwa chekuita semuchinjiko-cheni aggregator kune ese stablecoins. Chiratidzo ndechekuti chero munhu achakwanisa kushandisa Babelfish kushandura chero  makoini akagadzikana kune imwe, zvese zvinotsigirwa neBitcoin.
Maitiro acho achatevera nhanho dzakafanana neye pamusoro fiat- makoini akagadzikana tokeni kuburitswa: mushandisi achatumira imwe mhando ye  koini rakagadzikana uye iyo nzira ichave ne makoini akagadzikana emindi (XUSD) kumushandisi. Iyo nzira inodyara iyo yekutanga stablecoins mhiri kweDeFi mapuratifomu kuti iwane goho, izvo zvinozoita mari yekutonga uye bitcoin layer 2 inishuwarenzi dziva; goho richadzorerwazve vhiki nevhiki mune dziva remunharaunda ye bitcoin - zvekupedzisira zvinobatika zve insuarance.
Kutonga kwemutemo kunotongwa nenharaunda. Pese apo mumwe munhu anoshandisa mutemo uye achigashira maXUSD aka mintwa, ivo vanogashirawo FISH tokeni. HOVE chiratidzo chekutonga icho chinoratidza simba rekuvhota. Naizvozvo, vashandisi vanogona kuvhota munzira yemutemo vachishandisa aya maFISH tokens.
Babelfish ichave ichiparura kutengeswa kwayo kwekutanga paSovryn's Origin papuratifomu - yakasarudzika yekumisikidza inotongwa neSovryn Bitocracy.
Mari paNgetani
Mari paNgetani (MoC) iDeFi protocol inobata mana akakosha tokeni mukati mayo. Pfungwa ndeyekupa dzimwe sarudzo kuBitcoiners, kuvandudza pakuita kwavo bitcoin uye kushandisa makesi uchivabvumira kutonga kuzere kwemakiyi avo ega. Mari paNgetani inoshandawo paRSK network, ichichengetedza iyo Bitcoin inotarisisa.
Yekutanga tokeni MoC inopa iDollar paNgetani (DoC). Iyi ndiyo yekutanga 100% bitcoin-collateralized token, pegged 1: 1 kune US dollar.
Inotevera iBPRO, chiratidzo chinodzoreredza mari yaunowana kuburikidza nekugovaniswa kwekugovana purofiti nedzimwe nzira. Vabati veBPRO vanogona kubatsirwa nemahara emahara marefu, neruremekedzo rweDoC token holders. Vabati veBPRO vanowanawo kubva mumigodhi yemvura uye chikamu chemari inogadzirwa neMoC protocol. Chaizvoizvo, kubata BPRO kwakafanana nekubata bitcoin, pane imwe nhanho yakareba kwenguva refu, uchiwana mari yekungoita kubva kune yako bitcoin.
Chiratidzo chechitatu chinopihwa neMoC iBTC/USD chiridzwa chinonzi BTCx. BTCx ndiyo inomiririra inomiririra ye bitcoin yakarebesa chinzvimbo chakareba. Aya ma tokens anogadzirwa kana mushandisi anotumira BTC kune makontrakiti akachena uye ouya nemutengo unosiyana wemhindu (iyo inotarwa pakugadzirwa kwekondirakiti). Mari yekubhadhara inoenda kune vane ₿PRO.
Chekupedzisira, iyo MoC mitemo inosanganisirawo chiratidzo chekutonga, chiri nyore kunzi Money on Chain tokeni (MOC). Izvi zvinobvumira vane MOC kuti vatore chikamu mukudzoka kwesimba rekuvhota / veto uye mibairo yakatemerwa, zvese kubva mumari inobhadharwa papuratifomu uye yekuchera migodhi. Vashandisi vane kodzero yekuderedzwa pamubhadharo wepuratifomu pavanobhadhara vachishandisa chiratidzo cheMOC.
Kupedzisa, Mari paChain ndeye inozvimiririra yeBitcoin nharaunda, paRSK, iyo inotarisa kupa akawanda isiripakati uye asiri- muhusungwa kushandiswa nyaya zvakanangana Bitcoiners.
Liquid Network
Iyo Liquid Network inodyidzana nesidechain-based settlement network kune vanhu uye nekutsinhana, ichigonesa kukurumidza, kwakavanzika kuchinjana mari paBitcoin uye kuburitswa kwezvinhu zvedhijitari. Iyo yakaparadzana blockchain inowedzera mashandiro e bitcoin neakaturikidzana matekinoroji. Liquid haishandise humbowo-hwe-basa, zvidhinha zvinosainwa pane imwe miniti base nevashandi gumi nevashanu. Inosimudzira kuvanzika kuburikidza nekutengeserana zvakavanzika uye midziyo, uko huwandu uye rudzi rwezviwanikwa iri kutumirwa yakavanzwa, nepo ichiri cryptographically inovimbiswa kuti hapana imwe mari inogona kushandiswa kupfuura iripo.
Kune akasiyana makesi ekushandisa eLiquid:
kukurumidza kutengeserana pakati pekuchinjana
vanhu vanogona kushandisa L-BTC kuburikidza neBlockstream Green, Aqua, Elements, kana Sideswap chikwam
Kuchinjana pahushamwari HodlHodl inoshandisa L-BTC sevhisi yayo yekukweretesa
iko kuchinjana zvisina ari pakati Bisq ichabatanidza L-BTC sehwaro hwayo
chero munhu anogona kubudisa zvinhu zvitsva, kusanganisira makoini akagadzikana seTether USDt (yatove yakatsigirwa neLiquid) uye zviratidzo zvekuchengetedza, zvinogona kutengeswa zvakasununguka mukati metiweki.
Liquid inoratidza kuti unogona kuita chero chinhu neBitcoin. Iwe haudi blockchain nyowani kana chiratidzo chitsva. Mari yekuzvarwa yeLiquid iL-BTC, kwaunokiya bitcoin yako wowana yakaenzana L-BTC yayo. Naizvozvo pachava ne21 miriyoni L-BTC zvachose. Liquid transactions yakachipa, inokurumidza uye yakavanzika kupfuura bitcoin transaction. Kunyangwe iri iyo yakasanganiswa nesidechain transaction haigone kuongororwa. Iwo anoshanda mabhokisi matema, anogona kungodzimwa nevashandisi. Chinokubvisa pakuchunjana ndechokuti Bitcoin panomiswa kuchinjana kweBitcoin panofanira kuitwa kuburikidza neLiquid nhengo.
RGB
RGB isisitimu yemsakondirakiti akachena, inoshanda paLayer 2 uye 3 pamusoro peBitcoin uye Lightning Netiweki. Yakagadzirwa nekuvanzika uye scalability mupfungwa.
Zviitiko zvekushandisa zvinokwanisika ndezvi:
Bvisa dhijitari zviwanikwa zvinochinjika, senge sitoku, mabhondi uye mamwe mafomu ekuchengetedzeka
Gadzira akasiyana mafomu ekuunganidzwa (asiri-fungible assets)
Gadzira uye maneja kuzvitonga kuzere / kwakasarudzika
Dhizaina uye mhanyisa mamwe mafomu eanopokana-akaoma akangwara makondirakiti
Nekugona kwavo RGB zvakachena zvibvumirano zvinopfuura izvo zvinogoneka neEthereum-senge smart kontrakiti masisitimu, ichipa yakawanda yakaturikidzana, inoiswa pachikero, yakavanzika uye yakachengeteka nzira, uko muridzi weiyo smart kontrakiti yenyika inoparadzaniswa kubva kune yakangwara chibvumirano kugadzira.
NFTs
Chimwe chikamu chandinofunga kuti chinonyanya kufadza ndecheNFTs, kana kwete-matokeni anochinjika. Aya ma tokens ayo, pachinzvimbo chekumiririra mayuniti emari, anomiririra akasiyana zvinhu, zvinhu, kana zvivakwa muchimiro chinosiyaniswa kubva kune chimwe uye saka hazvifungidzike. Saka ngatifunge nezve chidimbu cheunyanzvi chinomiririrwa negwaro remabasa. Gwaro iroro rinogona kunge riri chiratidzo chedhijitari chinogona kutengeswa senge bitcoin, kana gwaro reimba yako, kana mota yako, kana chero chinhu chaicho kana chidimbu chevhu. Kuri kutotora zvinhu zviripo munyika chaiyo kana kutora dhijitari pfuma yehungwaru - serwiyo kana mhando - nekuiisa chiratidzo kuti ive chinhu chinogona kutengeswa nedhijitari. Hatisati tambokwenya pamusoro penzvimbo iyoyo kusvika parizvino.
Nhanho yekutanga yeNFT pamusoro peBitcoin yaiva imwebato, yakavambwa kunyange pamberi peEthereum muna 2014. Mumwedzi ichangopfuura mamwe Bitcoin based NFT platforms ari kubuda. Raretoshi, uye Azool.art mapuratifomu eNFT akavakirwa paLiquid Network. PaWatafan makadhi ekutengesa ane kukosha kwakabatana anotsigirwa neRootstock smart zvibvumirano. Sovryn neRGB vari kugadzira mapuratifomu eNFT panguva yekunyora bhuku rino.
Utongi
Pakupedzisira, chikamu chechitatu chinondifadza kune ramangwana ndiyo mukana wekushandisa izvi kune nzvimbo dzekuzivikanwa uye kutonga kwevanhu. Iko kugona kuve nechiratidzo chehunhu hwevanhu, kwausingafanirwe kuratidza kuti ndiwe ani asi unogona kusarudza kuratidza akasiyana siyana panguva. Ini ndinogona kuratidza kuti ndine dhigirii kubva kuYunivhesiti ndichishandisa isiri-matokeni anochinjika ndisina kukuudza zita rangu. Ndinogona kuratidza kuti ndine rezinesi rekutyaira ndisina kukupa nhoroondo yangu yese. Ndinogona kuratidza kuti ndakavimbika, kana ndakavimbika, ndakabaiwa kana chero humwe hunhu hwaungafunga nezvahwo. Aya ma tokenzi akasiyana aunogona kupa kune vanhu anokutendera iwe kuti utonge zvinhu izvi, hapana chikonzero chekuti hurumende kana mubatanidzwa seFacebook uite izvozvo. Ipapo iwe unogona kutora izvo zviratidzo uye wozvishandisa kune zvinangwa zvekutonga. Kugona kuvhota mumubatanidzwa wevaridzi vemba, mumubatanidzwa wangu wevabereki nevadzidzisi, munharaunda yangu, uye kusvika pakuvhota kuUnited Nations semumwe wevagari vepasi rino vane 7 uye 1/2 bhiriyoni vane chiratidzo chekuvhota. Shanduko huru yakananga kudemokrasi yakananga inogoneka nematekinoroji aya.
Izvi zvinhu zvatiri kutaura pamusoro pemakore gumi, gumi nemashanu, makumi maviri, makumi maviri nemashanu mune ramangwana. Asi ukanzwisisa kuti tekinoroji iyi inoshanda sei, uye ukaona mbeu dzatiri kudyara nhasi, unogona kuona semagadzirirwo echisikigo anobuda muhunyanzvi uhu.

900-glossary

Tsanangudzo yemashoko
**Cantillon Effect ** Nyanzvi yezvehupfumi yeFrance Richard Cantillon yakaratidza kuti kukwira kwemitengo inoitika zvishoma nezvishoma uye kuti kutsva kwemari kunowanikwa kune imwe nzvimbo kune kukwira kwemitengo zvinobudirira kutanga pfungwa yekusarerekera mari. Uyezve, akataura kuti avo vakagamuchira mari itsva vanonakidzwa nemararamiro akakwirira vachirasikirwa nevanozogamuchira gare gare.[^79]
**Central bank** Bhanga repakati, bhangi rekuchengetedza, kana masimba emari inzvimbo inobata mari uye mutemo wemari wehurumende kana mubatanidzwa wemari, uye inotarisira hurongwa hwavo hwekubhanga. [^80]
**Mari** Mari ndiyo hurongwa hwemari inoshandiswa zvakafanana inotsanangurwa nehurumende. Matunhu mazhinji anotsanangura mari yavo yenyika sematenda epamutemo, imari inoziviswa nemutemo kuti inoshanda pakubhadharwa kwezvikwereti uye haigone kurambwa sekubhadhara.
**Fiat money** Mari (a medium of exchange) yakagadzwa semari, kazhinji nemutemo wehurumende. Fiat mari haina kukosha kwemukati uye haina kukosha kwekushandisa (inherent utility, senge mhou kana beaver pelt inogona kuve nayo). Hune kukosha chete nekuti hurumende inochengetedza kukosha kwayo, kana nekuti mapato ari mukuchinjana anobvumirana pakukosha kwayo.[^81] Yese nyika yenyika mari ndeye fiat currencies. Kubva 1971 fiat mari haina kutsigirwa negoridhe. Izwi rokuti fiat" ndereLatin uye rinoreva kuti "ngazviitwe".
**Fractional-reserve banking ** Kubhanga kweFractional-reserve banking, kunoitwa nemabhanga ekutengeserana pasi rose, kunosanganisira mabhanga kugamuchira mari kubva kuvatengi uye kuita zvikwereti kune vanokwereta asi vachichengeta mari yakaenzana nechidimbu chezvikwereti zvebhangi. Mari dzebhanga dzinochengetwa semari mubhanga kana semasaramusi muakaundi yebhanga kubhanga guru renyika. Bhanga guru renyika rinotara mari shoma iyo mabhanga anofanira kubata mumidziyo yemvura, inodaidzwa kuti " reserve requirement" kana " reserve ratio". Mwero uyu unosiyana munyika nenyika. Muna Kurume 2020 iyo FED yakabvisa ichi chidimbu chekuchengetedza chinodiwa nekuda kwedenda. Kanadha, UK, New Zealand, Australia, Sweden neHong Kong havana zvavanoda.
**Full node ** Node yakazara ipurogiramu yepurogiramu inosimbisa zvizere zvekutengeserana uye zvivharo. Iwe unogona kumhanya yakazara node pakombuta yako yekumba kana paRasperry Pi. Anenge ese akazara node anobatsira network nekugamuchira kutengeserana uye zvivharo kubva kune dzimwe node dzakazara, kusimbisa izvo zvekutengesa uye zvivharo, uye zvino kuendesa kune mamwe azere node. Ivo chikamu chenetiweki yehushamwari. 
**Hasha** Muchina wekombuta wakasarudzika, unonzi ASIC unoshandiswa chete kumigodhi yeBitcoin.
**International Monetary Fund** IMF isangano rezvemari repasi rose, rine muzinda muWashington, DC, rine nyika zana nemakumi mapfumbamwe dziri kushanda kusimudzira kudyidzana kwemari yepasi rose, kuchengetedza kugadzikana kwemari, kufambisa kutengeserana nedzimwe nyika, kusimudzira mabasa epamusoro nekusimudzira hupfumi hwenyika, uye kuderedza urombo pasi rose nepo nguva nenguva zvichienderana. paWorld Bank nokuda kwezviwanikwa zvayo. Yakagadzirwa muna Chikunguru 1944, paBretton Woods Musangano zvakanyanya nepfungwa dzaHarry Dexter White naJohn Maynard Keynes, yakavepo zviri pamutemo muna 1945 nenyika makumi maviri nepfumbamwe uye chinangwa chekuvakazve hurongwa hwemari hwenyika. Ikozvino yava kuita basa repakati mukutarisira kuenzana kwematambudziko ekubhadhara uye matambudziko emari epasi rose. Nyika dzinopa mari kune imwe nzvimbo kuburikidza nehurongwa hwemakota umo nyika dzine matambudziko ekubhadhara dzinogona kukwereta mari. [^82]
**Mukweretesi wekupedzisira kuita ** Mukweretesi wekupedzisira sarudzo (LOLR) inzvimbo iri muhurongwa hwemari inoshanda semupi wemari kusangano rezvemari iro rinozviwana richitadza kuwana mari yakakwana mumusika wekukweretesa wemabhangi uye zvimwe zvivakwa kana masosi zvapera. Icho, chokwadi, vimbiso yehurumende yekupa mari kumasangano ezvemari. [^83]
**M0 Monetary Base** Huwandu hwemari (M0) ndiyo huwandu hwemari iri mubepa chairo uye coin iri kutenderera mumaoko everuzhinji kana muchimiro chemari yekubhanga yekutengeserana inochengetwa mumatura ebhanga guru renyika. [^84]
**M1 Mari Stock ** M1 chiyero chakamanikana chekupihwa kwemari kunosanganisira mari yepanyama, madipoziti anodiwa, cheki dzevafambi, uye mamwe madhipoziti anotarisika. M1 haisanganisire zvinhu zvemari, zvakaita seakaundi ekuchengeta nemabhondi.[^85]
**M2 Mari Stock ** M2 chiyero chekupihwa kwemari kunosanganisira mari, yekutarisa madhipoziti, uye nyore kuchinjika padyo nemari semasaving deposits, chengetedzo yemusika wemari uye mutual funds. Iyi midziyo haina mvura shoma pane M1 uye haina kukodzera semasvikiro ekuchinjana, asi inogona kukurumidza kushandurwa kuita mari kana kutarisa madhipoziti. M2 inotariswa zvakanyanya sechiratidzo chekupihwa kwemari uye kukwira kwemitengo mune ramangwana, uye sechinangwa chemutemo wezvemari webhanga guru. [^86]
**Panopticon** Iyo panopticon imhando yezvivakwa zvemasangano uye hurongwa hwekutonga hwakagadzirwa nemuzivi wechiRungu uye muongorori wemagariro Jeremy Bentham muzana ramakore rechi 18. Pfungwa yekugadzira ndeyekubvumidza vasungwa vese vepachikoro kuti vacherechedzwe nemuchengeti mumwe chete, pasina vasungwa vanokwanisa kuziva kuti vari kutariswa here.[^87]
** Peer-to-Peer Network ** Sisitimu yevane ropafadzo yakaenzana, vatori vechikamu vane hunyanzvi vasina hutongi hwemambure. Iyo Bitcoin netiweki yevakaenzana idhizaini yakasarudzika yemakomputa anomhanyisa Bitcoin software inosimbisa uye kugovera kutengeserana.
**Rehypothecation ** Rehypothecation itsika iyo mabhanga nemabroker vanoshandisa, nekuda kwezvinangwa zvavo, midziyo yakatumirwa sechibatiso nevatengi vavo. 
**Mbeu** 12-24 mazwi ayo mune mazhinji ezvikwama anowanikwa mumusika (HD wallets), gadzira ese akavanzika / eruzhinji makiyi ayo anozodzora mari yako pa blockchain. Chero ani ane mbeu ane simba pamusoro pemakiyi aya uye nekudaro, pamusoro pemari pamakero akabatana.
**Surveillance capitalism** Izwi rakagadzirwa naShoshana Zuboff. Inotsanangura kurongeka kwekugadzirwa kwedata remunhu nemakambani epakati emonopolistic aine chinangwa chekuita purofiti. 
**Wallet** Software kana Hardware inobata ako ese bitcoin kero uye zvakavanzika makiyi. Ishandise kutumira, kugamuchira, uye kuchengeta bitcoin yako.
[^79]: [Cantillon Effect on Wikipedia](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_Cantillon)   [^80]: [Central bank on Wikipedia](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Central_bank)   [^81]: [Fiat money on Wikipedia](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fiat_money)   [^82]: [IMF on Wikipedia](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Monetary_Fund)   [^83]: [Lender of last resort on Wikipedia](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lender_of_last_resort)   [^84]: [Monetary Base](https://www.investopedia.com/terms/m/monetarybase.asp)   [^85]: [M1 Money](https://www.investopedia.com/terms/m/m1.asp)   [^86]: [M2 Money](https://www.investopedia.com/terms/m/m2.asp)   [^87]: [Panopticon on Wikipedia](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Panopticon)

920-disclaimer

Tarisiro
Zviri mukati mebhuku rino hazviunze zvemari, mutero kana zano remutemo, asi ndezvezvinangwa zveruzivo chete. Ruzivo rwunoitirwa kuzivisa seti yezvakanakisa maitiro. Iyo inogona kusagadzirisa njodzi dzakananga kumamiriro ako ezvinhu, uye kana ikasadaro, iwe unofanirwa kugadzirisa nenzira kwayo. Nepo ruzivo urwu ruchigona kuzivisa maitiro akanakisa, hapana vimbiso yekuti kutevera iri zano kuchave nechokwadi zvakakwana kuchengetedzwa kwezvinhu zvako zvedhijitari. Mukuwedzera, ruzivo urwu iwindo rekuita zvakanaka pane imwe nguva munguva. Ziva kuti iyo Bitcoin & blockchain nharaunda inogona kunge yakashanduka uye kuongororwa kwenjodzi yezvimwe zvigadzirwa zvinogona kunge zvachinja kubva pakaburitswa bhuku rino. Mune mamwe mazwi: chenjera, chenjera, uye ziva nezve yazvino Bitcoin & blockchain nzvimbo usati washandisa ruzivo urwu.

930-author

Munyori
Anita Posch mumiriri weBitcoin, munyori, solopreneur uye mutsigiri weAnita Posch show. Ndiye muvambi weBitcoin for Fairness - chirongwa chekudzidzisa chisingabatsiri.
Chinangwa chaAnita ndechekuunza Bitcoin kumabhiriyoni kuburikidza nebasa rake rekudzidzisa. Akagadzira Bitcoin podcast, chiteshi cheYouTube uye akanyora bhuku (L) kuwana Bitcoin. Vakabvunzurudzawo vanhu vanobva pasirese pasi rose kusanganisira vamwe vanobva kunyika dziri kusimukira dzakaita seNigeria, South Africa, Venezuela, neAfghanistan nezve mhedzisiro yeBitcoin parusununguko rwevanhu.
Mukutanga kwa2020 ndiye aive wekutanga Bitcoiner kushanyira Zimbabwe kuti atsvage mamiriro emari munyika pamwe nekutorwa kweBitcoin uye kutaura zvakabuda mupodcast yake. Chinangwa chaive, kuburikidza nekubvunzurudza, kuvaka bhiriji pakati pevanhu vanogara pasi pehutongi hwehutongi hwehutongi kana hutongi hwehutongi kune dzimwe nyika uye kuratidza kuti Bitcoin ingavandudza sei mararamiro avo uye rusununguko rwemari.
Bitcoin imari kubva kuvanhu, kuvanhu. Mitemo yaro yemasvomhu haigone kushatiswa - kwete nehurumende kana nemabhirioni. Izvi zvinovimbisa mwero weruvengo usingakwanisi kuwanikwa mumagamuchidzanwa anotungamirwa nevanhu. Inopa vanhu vanoshaya, sevanhu vanobva kunyika dzichiri kusimukira, vakadzi, nemapoka madiki akadzvinyirirwa, mukana wekutora chikamu pasi rose zvakasununguka uye zvakavanzika nemumwe nemumwe. Rusununguko urwu rwekuchinjana kukosha, kusunungura hunyanzvi hwevanhu uye hunyanzvi, ndihwo hunofambisa Anita Posch.
Bitcoin inogona kunge iri chishandiso chedu chega chekuchengetedza kodzero dzevanhu dzekuvanzika uye rusununguko rwekutengeserana. Inzira yekusunungura mabhiriyoni evanhu uye nzira yekudzivirira yekuvanzika muhupenyu hwedu hwemadhijitari. - **Anita Posch**
Asati atanga basa rake rekudzidzisa reBitcoin muna 2017, Anita akawana anopfuura makore makumi maviri eruzivo rwekuvandudza webhu, e-commerce, uye bhizinesi repamhepo. Aodzwa mwoyo nechimiro chepakati cheinternet, kushandiswa kwevatengi uye kuongorora capitalism yaakapedza 2016 muBerlin pachinangwa chekuchinja.
Mukutanga kwa2017 akaenda kuhurukuro yeBitcoin uye yakavhurika blockchain tekinoroji uye nemhedzisiro yakanaka yaigona kuve nayo munharaunda. Akaona kuti tekinoroji isingabvumidzwe, kuburitsa kukwira kwemitengo uye mari yepasirese yepainternet yaigona kusunungura mabhiriyoni evanhu, vasina kusununguka nemasimba emari aripo. Bitcoin imari isingamisiki inogona kushandiswa nemunhu wese zvisinei nekuti ndiani. Haina kwayakarerekera, haina kudzorwa nekambani chero ipi zvayo kana hurumende, nepo panguva imwe chete iri internet protocol, njanji dzemari dzakavakwa kuti dziite zvakanaka.
Anita akashandura mavhoriyamu maviri e "Internet of Money" naAndreas M. Antonopoulos muchiGerman. Tsvagiridzo yake uye zviitiko zvakatenderedza Bitcoin zvinokurukurwa munhau pasi rese: Bitcoin Magazine, CoinDesk, Zvakaitwa neBitcoin, Bayern2, Deutschlandfunk, Radio FM4, uye terevhizheni yeARD, pakati pevamwe.
Anita Posch anogara achinyora pa [https://twitter.com/anitaposch](https://twitter.com/anitaposch).
Unogona kuwana zvimwe nezvaAnita pawebhusaiti yake pa [https://anitaposch.com](https://anitaposch.com), iyo Anita Posch show pa[https://anita.link/show](https:// anita.link/show), Anita's YouTube chiteshi pa [https://www.youtube.com/anitaposch](https://www.youtube.com/anitaposch), uye ruzivo nezve bhuku rino pa [https://learnbitcoin .link](https://learnbitcoin.link).

950-back-cover

Chii chinonzi Bitcoin? Kutotanga kupindura mubvunzo uyu, munhu anofanira kutanga abvunza "chii chinonzi mari?" Anita anotora muverengi kuburikidza nerwendo urwu rwekudzidza pamusoro pemari kuitira kuti vanzwisise kuti sei Bitcoin ndiyo inotevera kusvetukira mberi mune tekinoroji yemari. Ukangoziva "nei?" zvino pane nyaya yekuti "sei?" Nekutonga kukuru kunouya mutoro mukuru; kuti ufambe nenzira yakachengeteka iyi system itsva uchada ruzivo nezvishandiso zvinopihwa nebhuku rino." - **Jameson Lopp, Co-founder & CTO, Casa**
Anita akaita basa guru munharaunda yeBitcoin, kusanganisira uye kunyanya izvo zvaakaburitsa pamusoro pekushandiswa kweBitcoin munzvimbo dzisina rombo pasi rose. kuti nditange. - **Lyn Alden, Investment Strategist **
Vadzidzisi vepamusoro vadzidzi. Kubva pazuva rekutanga Anita akabuda pa radar yangu, anga ari muongorori ane ruzivo uye ane njere uye mutsigiri weBitcoin's revolutionary technology. Kunhonga gorosi kubva muhundi, anonyora zviri nyore, zvakajeka, uye nemazvo zvinodikanwa. yenyaya yakaoma inoda hunyanzvi muzvidzidzo zvakawanda. Sovryn inodada nekutsigira kuburitswa kwe (L) kuwana Bitcoin sechikamu chechinangwa chedu chekuita kuti Bitcoin isamire. - ** akadzingwa surfer, Muvambi, Parallele Polis, Comms Inotungamira kuSovrynBTC **
Anita Posch ndeimwe yeanonyanya kubereka uye anonzwisisa manzwi echiGerman munzvimbo yeBitcoin. Basa rake rinoita kuti Bitcoin isvike, inonzwisisika uye inomanikidza kune avo vari vatsva kuBitcoin uye inovabatsira parwendo rwavo rwekuva nyanzvi. Munzvimbo yakazadzwa neruzha. , basa rake rakajeka uye rakatendeseka. - **Andreas M. Antonopoulos, Munyori Mastering Bitcoin" uye "Internet yemari"**
