Nhanganyaya
Kunyora tsananguro yechinhu ichi kune vateereri vese kune ropa rakaoma. Hapana chekuita nazvo. - Satoshi Nakamoto
(L) earn Bitcoin ndiyo gwara rakanakisa rekusarudza kuti sei uye sei uchifanira kupinda munyika yeBitcoin. Inopa Bitcoin mumativi ayo ese kubva kune zvehunyanzvi, zvehupfumi, zvematongerwo enyika uye zvemagariro zvine chekuita nemamiriro emari aripo. Inopa nhanho-ne-nhanho nzira yekufambisa ino nyika itsva yezvemari uye inomisa iwe nekongiri kurudziro yekuti ungawana sei zvakachengeteka, kuwana uye kuchengeta bitcoin. Kukwira masitepisi ehutongi hwemari kuchakupa rusununguko uye kutonga pamusoro pemari yako.
Mubhuku rino iwe uchawana mhinduro dzemibvunzo yekuti chii mari, kwainobva, kuvandudzwa kwayo kwenhoroondo, blockchain tekinoroji uye Bitcoin chaizvo. Inopa mhinduro kune nei uye sei kushandisa Bitcoin panguva imwe chete debunking ngano dzakakurumbira uye kusanzwisisa kwakapoteredza cryptocurrencies. Ini ndinonyura zvakadzama mukusimukira kweBitcoin kubva payakavambwa muna 2008 uye ndinopa tarisiro yemangwana mashandisirwo emari anoenderana neBitcoin.
Nepo vezvenhau uye vezvehupfumi pundits munyika dzekuMadokero vachifunga kuti chingori chishandiso chekufungidzira, chinangwa changu ndechekuparadzira shoko nezveBitcoin semugonesi werusarura zvemari uye shanduko yemagariro. Izvo zvisingataurwi ndizvo zvakanaka zvepasirese zvinorehwa kuti zvechokwadi isingabvumirwe, isingaverengeki, isina kwayakarerekera yedhijitari asset ine yakagadziriswa inopihwa inopa.
Gare gare mubhuku ini ndichatarisa pane zvakanyanya kushanda zveBitcoin (BTC) uye maitiro aungaita zvakachengeteka nekuichengeta. Iwe unozodzidza nzira yekuwana chivimbo nekutanga nemari shoma, maitiro ekudzikisa njodzi dziripo uye kuenderera zvine hungwaru uye nemazvo mukuchengetedza hupfumi hwako kwenguva refu.
Iri harisi zano rezvemari, kana gwara rekutengesa kune zviuru zveAltcoins zviripo. Kana iwe uchingofarira kuwana kwenguva pfupi, kubata mari sekunge uri kubhejera mukhasino, bhuku rino harisi rako. Izvo ndezvevanhu vanoda (l) earn uye kunzwisisa zvakakosha zveBitcoin uye kudzora mari yavo nenzira yekuzvimiririra.
Yakakurudzirwa na
[Anita Posch](https://anitaposch.com/) mumiriri weBitcoin, munyori, [podcaster](https://bitcoinundco.com/en/) uye ega. Ndiye muvambi weBitcoin for Fairness - chirongwa chekudzidzisa chisingabatsiri. Bitcoin imari kubva kuvanhu, kuvanhu. Mitemo yaro yemasvomhu haigone kushatiswa - kwete nehurumende kana nemabhirioni. Izvi zvinovimbisa mwero weruvengo usingagoni kuwanikwa muhurongwa hwechinyakare hunotungamirwa nevanhu. Inopa vanhu vanoshaya, sevanhu vanobva kunyika dzichiri kusimukira, vakadzi, nemapoka madiki akadzvinyirirwa, mukana wekutora chikamu pasi rose zvakasununguka uye zvakavanzika nemumwe nemumwe. Rusununguko urwu rwekuchinjana kukosha, kusunungura hunyanzvi hwevanhu uye hunyanzvi, ndihwo hunofambisa Anita Posch.
